Description: Jang Cheol-min is a former boxer who finds work as a parking space attendant. His life turns upside down when he meets Jung-hwa, a blind girl, and they begin to fall in love.

Title: Battlestar Galactica: The Plan
Description: When the initial Cylon attack against the Twelve Colonies fails to achieve complete extermination of human life as planned, twin Number Ones (Cavils) embedded on Galactica and Caprica must improvise to destroy the human survivors.

Title: Checkered Ninja
Description: A possessed Ninja doll teams up with a teenage boy to avenge the murder of a poor child factory worker.

Title: Alexander Nevsky
Description: The story of how a great Russian prince led a ragtag army to battle an invading force of Teutonic Knights.

Title: The Holcroft Covenant
Description: The son of a German General becomes part of a mysterious conspiracy to gain hidden Nazi funds.

Title: Furious
Description: In the 13th century, an amnesiac soldier vows to get his revenge on the Mongol army that ransacked his village.

Title: Constantine: City of Demons - The Movie
Description: A decade after a tragic mistake, Chas Chandler and occult investigator John Constantine set out to cure Chas's daughter, Trish, from a demonically induced coma.

Title: The Last Train to New York
Description: Remake of the 2016 Korean film Train to Busan about a father traveling with his daughter on a train during a zombie outbreak.

Title: A Breath Away
Description: A family fights to survive as the streets of Paris fill with a deadly gas.

Title: Bubble
Description: After bubbles that broke the laws of gravity rained down upon the world. Cut off from the outside world, Tokyo has become a playground for a group of young people who have lost their families.

Title: Terminal Velocity
Description: A maverick skydiver and a former KGB agent team up to stop the Russian mafia from stealing gold.

Title: Batman: Gotham by Gaslight
Description: In an alternative Victorian Age Gotham City, Batman begins his war on crime while he investigates a new series of murders by Jack the Ripper.

Title: The Best Man
Description: Mercenaries seize control of a remote resort hotel during a wedding and it's up to the best man, the groom and their drunken best friend to stop the terrorists and save the hostages.

Title: Showtime
Description: A spoof of buddy cop movies where two very different cops are forced to team up on a new reality based television cop show, while tracking down the manufacturer and distributor of an illegally made semi-automatic firearm.

Title: Two-Minute Warning
Description: A crazed sniper is set to kill spectators at an L.A. Coliseum football championship game and the police race against time to eliminate him.

Title: Miss Bala
Description: After entering a beauty contest in Tijuana, a young woman witnesses drug-related murders and is forced to do the gang's bidding.

Title: Outlaw
Description: A group of people who feel betrayed by their government and let down by their Police force form a modern-day outlaw posse in order to right what they see as the wrongs of society.

Title: War
Description: Kabir, a secret agent, goes rogue after a mission to catch a terrorist goes awry. However, his boss sends Khalid, another agent and his student, to track him down.

Title: The Prince
Description: When his daughter is kidnapped, a retired assassin is drawn back into the life he gave up. To rescue her, he must confront his former rival.

Title: White Tiger
Description: Great Patriotic War, early 1940s. After barely surviving a battle with a mysterious, ghostly-white Tiger tank, Red Army Sergeant Ivan Naydenov becomes obsessed with its destruction.

Title: Ryan's World the Movie: Titan Universe Adventure
Description: Ryan's twin sisters Emma and Kate get trapped in a comic book world. Ryan enters this realm to rescue them, facing adventures, battles, and mishaps while attempting to bring them back before his parents discover their disappearance.

Title: Believer
Description: A police detective determined to catch the unseen boss of Asia's biggest drug cartel joins hands with a revenge-thirsty member of the gang.

Title: Halo
Description: Justin Harp lost his mother in a car accident that crippled his father, and now his little sister has run away. When he finds out she has been caught up in the underground club scene, his fire is rekindled.

Title: Viduthalai Part 2
Description: An unassuming school teacher faces extreme circumstances, forcing him to take up arms and lead a fiery rebellion against oppression, becoming an unlikely leader.

Title: Marry My Dead Body
Description: One day a police officer finds a red wedding envelope, only to find out that the owner is in fact a ghost asking for the officer's hand in marriage before reincarnation. What will happen when a human and a ghost form a special bond?

Title: Speed Zone
Description: Despite the police's preemptive strike, the illegal coast-to-coast car race is still on with new drivers. It's a race where fair play, red lights, stop signs, police roadblocks and traffic rules in general have no validity.

Title: Hell's Trap
Description: Two rivaling groups of friends intend to hunt a bear on a forest, but soon they are stalked by a masked madman Vietnam veteran.

Title: Flight World War II
Description: After Flight 42 travels through a storm they find themselves in France, 1940, during World war II.

Title: The Divine Fury
Description: A world-champion MMA fighter suddenly discovers stigmata on his palms. His visit to a church leads to an unexpected exorcism with a priest. Together, they face a final showdown with Jisin, a sinister agent of evil.

Title: GTMax
Description: When a notorious gang of bikers recruits her brother for a heist, a former motocross champion must face her deepest fears to keep her family safe.

Title: White Snake
Description: A love story between a snake spirit and a snake hunter.

Title: Mesrine: Killer Instinct
Description: The story of the notorious French gangster Jacques Mesrine, with the focus on his life before the early 1970s and the events that led to him being declared Public Enemy No. 1 in France.

Title: Cruel Jaws
Description: A huge shark terrorizes a beach in Florida, and the locals try everything to kill it.

Title: Ala Vaikunthapurramuloo
Description: After growing up enduring criticism from his father, a young man finds his world shaken upon learning he was switched at birth with a millionaire's son.

Title: RoboCop Returns
Description: RoboCop returns to fight crime in Detroit.

Title: The Thinning
Description: In a future, overcrowded, dystopian society, students with the lowest test scores are culled. Two students discover errors with the test.

Title: Money Plane
Description: A professional thief with $40 million in debt and his family's life on the line must commit one final heist - rob a futuristic airborne casino filled with the world's most dangerous criminals.

Title: Rosewood
Description: A dramatization of a 1923 horrific racist lynch mob attack on an African-American community.

Title: Outrage
Description: The boss of a major crime syndicate orders his lieutenant to bring a rogue gang of drug traffickers in line, a job that gets passed on to his long-suffering subordinate.

Title: Yodha
Description: After terrorists hijack a passenger plane, an off-duty soldier aboard devises a strategy to defeat the hijackers and ensure the passengers' survival when the engine fails.

Title: Naked Vengeance
Description: A beautiful woman seeks revenge for tragedy forced upon her family.

Title: The Last Front
Description: Amidst World War I's chaos, a grieving father turns hero, leading villagers to safety while evading a relentless enemy driven by vengeance.

Title: Trigger Point
Description: Follows Nicolas Shaw, a retired U.S. special operative who becomes part of an elite "invisible" team that quietly takes out the worst villains around the world.

Title: Rumble Through the Dark
Description: In the dark landscape of the Mississippi Delta, a bare knuckle cage fighter seeks to repay his debts in a final, desperate attempt to salvage the family home of his dying foster mother.

Title: Dobermann
Description: Dobermann is the world's most ruthless bank robber and with his gang rob bank after bank, now in Paris. What can the police do but to let the mad, morally bankrupt police commissioner loose on him?

Title: The Red Ghost
Description: A detachment of Soviet soldiers, including a dangerous half-man, half-ghost, come up against an elite death squad within the Wehrmacht.

Title: Certain Prey
Description: Minneapolis Deputy Police Chief, Lucas Davenport, has to face off against a duo unlike any he's ever encountered; a lethal hit woman and a ferociously cunning killer determined to hunt him down.

Title: Brothers by Blood
Description: A tale of family, friendships and betrayal in the violent world of the Philadelphia mob.

Title: Rage
Description: When the daughter of a reformed criminal is kidnapped, he rounds up his old crew and seeks his own brand of justice.

Title: The Lesser Evil
Description: A woman is approached by a man who has kidnapped her daughter.

Title: Space Battleship Yamato
Description: In 2199, the crew of the space battleship Yamato embark on a dangerous journey to the planet Iskandar to acquire a device that will rejuvenate the war-ravaged Earth.

Title: Night Train
Description: A single mom struggling to make ends meet as a Hollywood teamster evades capture by a ruthless FBI Agent while running black market medical supplies in her legendary souped-up pickup truck.

Title: Lucky Day
Description: Red, a safe cracker who has just been released from prison, is trying to hold his family together as his past catches up with him in the form of Luc, a psychopathic contract killer who's seeking revenge for the death of his brother.

Title: The Scorpion King 4: Quest for Power
Description: When he is betrayed by a trusted friend, Mathayus (Victor Webster) must marshal all his strength and cunning to outwit a formidable opponent who will stop at nothing to unlock a supreme ancient power.

Title: The Trust
Description: A pair of cops investigating a drug invasion stumble upon a mysterious bank vault.

Title: The Angel
Description: As his country prepares for war, top Egyptian official Ashraf Marwan makes contact with Israel and wades into a shadowy game of high-stakes espionage.

Title: Invincible
Description: Plot unknown. Feature length adaptation of the comic books.

Title: Digimon: The Movie
Description: Throughout three different stories, Kari Kamiya and her friends take on explosive adventures involving digital creatures.

Title: Mura
Description: Four friends from a humble background plan a heist, but past secrets and hidden motives emerge, testing their loyalties. As ambition collides with friendship, they face tough choices in their quest for revenge.

Title: The Sea Wolves
Description: During World War II, British Intelligence brings a crew of ex-soldiers out of retirement, using their age as cover, to take to the seas and pull off an unlikely undercover mission in neutral Goa.

Title: The Last Ronin
Description: In a post-apocalyptic world ravaged by nuclear war and climate disaster, survivors navigate scorched lands and ruined cities. With technology failing and fuel useless, ammunition becomes the new currency of a desperate civilization.
Five people find themselves trapped in an elevator during the September 11 attacks. They soon work together, never giving up hope, to try to escape before the unthinkable happens.

Title: The Toxic Avenger Part II
Description: The Toxic Avenger is tricked into traveling to Tokyo to search for his estranged father, leaving Tromaville open to complete domination by an evil corporation.

Title: Messenger of Death
Description: A Denver reporter investigates the mass murder of a family of Mormons in rural Colorado.

Title: The Spine of Night
Description: Ultra-violent, epic fantasy set in a land of magic follows heroes from different eras and cultures battling against a malevolent force.

Title: Welcome to the Punch
Description: When a notorious criminal is forced to return to London, it gives a detective one last chance to take down the man he's always been after.

Title: Danger: Diabolik
Description: A master thief and his sensual lover pull off heist after heist, all while an envious coalition of cops and gangsters is gunning for them.

Title: Chhota Bheem Master of Shaolin
Description: Bheem and his friends accompany Ming, a monk, to the Shaolin temple to fight against a dangerous Kaifu who wants to take control of the Shaolin temple.

Title: Mythica: A Quest for Heroes
Description: The young magician Marek dreams of exciting adventures. When she meets the help-seeking priestess Teela she offers her assistance and provides a motley troupe. Together they go in search of Teela's sister, who was kidnapped by a wild ogre.

Title: Secret Society of Second Born Royals
Description: Follows Sam's adventures at a top-secret training program for a new class of second-born royals tasked with saving the world.

Title: One Way
Description: Freddy, a petty criminal, is on the run with a bag full of cash and coke. He's way over his head and hurt bad. With a bullet in his guts he's running out of time.

Title: Quantum Apocalypse
Description: A group of talented but rebellious 'rock-star scientists' find themselves in a race against time to save Earth when a comet makes an unexpected turn towards our blue planet where all life may cease to exist within days if our small town heroes fail to find a solution.

Title: Rise of the Footsoldier: The Heist
Description: Fresh out of prison, Pat Tate steps right back into his Essex nightclub business. Since he can't stop brooding about the man who had him put away, it's not long before he's off to Marbella to find Frank Harris and seek his revenge.

Title: MR-9: Do or Die
Description: An elite Bangladeshi spy teams up with a CIA operative to bring down an international criminal organization headed by a ruthless businessman.

Title: Guns
Description: After a failed assassination attempt on her partner, DEA agent Donna Hamilton discovers that the crime lord responsible for her father's death is coming after her and her associates.

Title: Batman: Year One
Description: A wealthy playboy and a Chicago cop both return to Gotham City where their lives will intersect in unexpected ways.

Title: Flash Gordon
Description: Flash Gordon, Dale Arden and Dr. Alexis Zarkov visit the planet Mongo to thwart the evil schemes of Emperor Ming the Merciless, who has set his planet on a collision course with Earth.

Title: Starchaser: The Legend of Orin
Description: Set on the subterranean Mine-World, a band of human worker are treated like slaves under the power of the evil overlord Zygon until one, Orin, unearths the hilt of a mythical sword that only he can master. Escaping the planet, he runs into the rogue smuggler Dagg and a pair of helpful droids and the princess, who all team up to return to the Mine-World with a plan to defeat Zygon and free Orin's enslaved people.

Title: The Operative
Description: A woman is recruited by the Mossad to work undercover in Tehran.

Title: The Protector
Description: A young fighter named Kham must go to Australia to retrieve his stolen elephant. With the help of a Thai-born Australian detective, Kham must take on all comers, including a gang led by an evil woman and her two deadly bodyguards.

Title: Control
Description: A troubled doctor wakes up one morning to the sound of a mysterious voice in his head. With his reality now in question, the voice makes a series of escalating demands he must follow or devastating consequences will unfold.

Title: Crows Zero
Description: A transfer student attempts to take over the most violent high school in the country, whose students form factions and battle each other for power.

Title: Vanvaas
Description: Delves into the dynamics between an elderly father grappling with dementia and his family.

Title: Emperor of the North
Description: In 1933, during the Depression, Shack the brutal conductor of the number 19 train has a personal vendetta against the best train hopping hobo tramp in the Northwest, A No. 1.

Title: Naya Legend of the Golden Dolphin
Description: This is an action film following the adventures of Naya The Golden Dolphin Princess and her mission to save the Earth.

Title: Detective Chinatown
Description: After being rejected from the police academy, a mild-mannered young man travels to Bangkok where he and an energetic distant relative must solve a murder case.

Title: Cat Run 2
Description: Two quirky NYC PIs head to New Orleans for a cooking contest and to clear a cousin's name in a shootout on a military base. Who are the strippers/spies/assassins?

Title: Aqua Teen Hunger Force Colon Movie Film for Theaters
Description: An action epic that explores the origins of Master Shake, Frylock, and Meatwad, better known as the Aqua Teen Hunger Force, who somehow become pitted in a battle over an immortal piece of exercise equipment.

Title: Resident Evil: Damnation
Description: Special Agent Leon S.Kennedy goes against his superior's orders and works to destroy a series of biological weapons being used in a war zone in Europe.

Title: The Locksmith
Description: A thief fresh out of prison, tries to work his way back into the life of his daughter and ex-fiancé. Determined, he is forced to use the skills he has as a gifted locksmith. Things take a tumultuous turn after an unexpected disappearance.

Title: The Octagon
Description: A martial artist must defeat a plan by ninjas to create a worldwide training camp for terrorists.

Title: Cotton Comes to Harlem
Description: Two Harlem cops investigate a robbery, believing that a reverend has staged it in order to steal the money he's collected for a local fundraiser.

Title: Lazer Team
Description: Four losers are thrust into the position of saving the world when they stumble upon a UFO crash site and become genetically equipped to the battle suit on board.

Title: Nice Girls
Description: When Léo's brother Ludo is killed in Hamburg, despite orders she partners with German cop Mélanie to investigate. Unbeknownst to them, Nice faces a threat and they share an unknown connection.

Title: Raid on Entebbe
Description: True story of a daring Israeli commando assault on the Entebbe Airport in Uganda to free hostages of a terrorist hijacking.

Title: Tentacles
Description: A mutated giant octopus wreaks havoc on a California seaside community.

Title: Fighting
Description: In New York City, a young counterfeiter is introduced to the world of underground street fighting by a seasoned scam artist, who becomes his manager on the bare-knuckling brawling circuit.

Title: The Majorettes
Description: A high school majorettes are being methodically killed by a mysterious masked figure. Meanwhile, a local gang are involved in suspicious activities around the school.

Title: Justice League of America
Description: An evil Weather Man intent on destroying New Metro City with a series of malevolent meteorological mishaps? Can the super-powered (and semi-employed) Justice League of America save the day? Or will New Metro be drowned in a humongous tidal wave?

Title: Angel of H.E.A.T.
Description: A mad scientist uses an army of androids and a device that can disintegrate metal to try to steal microchips containing top secret information. The government dispatches a beautiful female agent to stop him.

Title: Riot

Title: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Re;Surrection

Title: The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring - Special Extended Edition Scenes

In an inexplicable situation, a family finds themselves confined within their home, unable to leave. As supplies dwindle, they must learn resourcefulness to survive and unravel the mysterious force trapping them.

Title: Chandu Champion

Description: Several groups of people try to survive a zombie pandemic that unleashes itself in downtown Seoul.

Description: Three problem teens sent to jail are offered a deal to work with an undercover cop, uncover an intricate drug ring and are caught in a deadly set-up. With cops on their trail, they have little time to solve the case and clear their names.

Description: A standalone film featuring Suriya's character Rolex, introduced in Vikram, follows the Lokesh Cinematic Universe after Kaithi, Vikram, Leo, Benz and Kaithi 2

Title: Dragon Ball Z: Broly - The Legendary Super Saiyan
Description: Goku, Vegeta, and the rest of the Dragon Team search for the fabled Legendary Super Saiyan, a destructive, all-powerful warrior.

Title: Godzilla vs. Destoroyah
Description: The aftermath of the Oxygen Destroyer brings forth Destoroyah, a beast intent on killing Godzilla, who is on the verge of a nuclear meltdown.

Title: Trespass

Title: Fatal Justice

Title: Batman and Harley Quinn

Description: Connor Connolly has one day to pay reparations to Tyrone Pettis. He is forced to ask his old military ops crew, led by Brice Mason, to come together to get him two million dollars before he loses everyone he loves in the process.

Title: Parasyte: Part 1
Description: The humanity is suffering from murders all over the globe, called "Mincemeat murders". High school student, Izumi Shinichi has a parasite living off him, having replaced his right hand, and he might be the discoverer of truth.

Title: The Good Thief

Title: Batman: Bad Blood

Title: Ultimate Avengers: The Movie

Title: Rangasthalam

Title: Naruto Shippûden: The Movie

Title: Road House 2: Last Call
Description: While he's deep undercover in New York, DEA agent Shane Tanner, the son of a legendary cooler named Dalton, learns that his uncle Nate Tanner got beat up by a group of men because he doesn't want to sell the Black Pelican, his bar in Tyree, Louisiana. Shane takes off for Louisiana to find out who attacked Nate. Shane decides to stay in Nate's house for the time being, and run the Black Pelican in Nate's absence, much to the dismay of former Black Pelican cooler Bill "Wild Bill" Decarie. Wild Bill wants to buy the Black Pelican since it's located in a prime location for running drugs. The Black Pelican is close to the border, it's between Florida and Texas, and it's in an area where drugs can be smuggled pretty much undetected. But Shane doesn't want to sell, and damages the numerous thugs that Bill sends his way. Also, Dalton was murdered years ago, and Shane still wonders who killed Dalton. When Shane was a rookie state trooper in Tyree, Shane had come home from work one night, and found Dalton fatally shot. After that, Shane left town and became a DEA agent. Now, Wild Bill's boss, Miami crime syndicate kingpin Victor Crost, decides that it's time to handle matters personally, because Wild Bill's men are not doing a good job of it. Shane is soon faced with impossible odds and a low number of staff members at the Black Pelican. To rid Louisiana of Victor, Wild Bill, and their organization, Shane teams up with local school teacher Beau Hampton, who is a regular at the Black Pelican.

Title: Malone

Title: Yor: The Hunter from the Future

Title: Canyon of the Dead

Title: Samurai Cop 2: Deadly Vengeance

Title: K-Pop: Demon Hunters

Description: After a botched assignment, a rice-fetishizing hitman finds himself in conflict with his organization, and one mysterious, dangerous fellow-hitman in particular.

Title: Humanoids from the Deep
Description: While a town is in a state of alert, the monster of the sea keeps mutating the townspeople at an alarming rate. A researcher finds a genetic disorder that has been caused by a chemical that has been dumped into the water that has caused the creature to have an alarming appetite.

Title: The Unthinkable
Description: Sweden faces a mysterious attack while Alex tries to reunite with his youth love, Anna.

Title: Steel Dawn
Description: In a post-apocalyptic world, a warrior wandering through the desert comes upon a group of settlers who are being menaced by the leader of a murderous gang who's after the water they control.

Title: By Dawn's Early Light
Description: A non-NATO nuclear missile is fired from Turkey at USSR, where it detonates. Soviet response is automatic as it's seen as a NATO missile. Can continued escalation be avoided? We follow the US president and a bomber crew.

Title: Jackson County Jail
Description: A wrongfully imprisoned young woman accused of murdering the guard who assaulted her escapes from jail and becomes a fugitive.

Title: Redux Redux
Description: Irene Kelly travels through parallel universes, repeatedly killing her daughter's murderer. As she becomes consumed by vengeance, her humanity hangs in the balance.

Title: The Loot
Description: Henry and Angel Henderson discover a treasure with a letter promising millions from dealer Mary. Billy attempts to steal it, leading the brothers on a quest to protect their newfound fortune.

Title: Smokin' Aces 2: Assassins' Ball
Description: Hords of insane assassins (2 cute) gather in or near a bar waiting to kill an insignificant FBI pencil pusher at 3AM and collect $3M. He's kept in a safe house/bunker nearby surrounded by FBI agents. Action awaits.

Title: Overdose
Description: Follows Sara, head of the Toulouse police narcotics squad, who is forced to collaborate with Richard, the head of the local criminal police, to stop a go-fast between Spain and France and find the murderer linked to the case.

Title: Je Jatt Vigarh Gya
Description: Follows the story of Daler (Jayy Randhawa), a straightforward and a fierce individual whose life takes a drastic turn due to unforeseen personal circumstances. Faced with injustice and unnatural behavior, Guri's transformation from a law-abiding kid to a relentless avenger forms the crux of the narrative.

Title: Beyond the Reach
Description: In the Mojave Desert, an unarmed hunting guide runs from a wealthy hunter who wants to ensure his silence in the death of an old man.

Title: Police Story 2
Description: The Hong Kong supercop must stop a group of blackmailing bombers, while the villains of Police Story (1985) are out for revenge.

Title: Fist of the North Star
Description: In a post-nuclear hellscape, a master of the deadly martial art "Hokuto Shinken" allies with two kids and an expert in "Nanto Suicho-Ken" to battle the tyrants who kidnapped his lover.

Title: Ben 10: Secret of the Omnitrix
Description: When the Omnitrix begins a countdown to self-destruction, Ben and Gwen team up with Tetrax to find the watch's creator before it's too late.

Title: Hunt Club
Description: Follows a group of male hunters who regularly lure women to their island with the chance to win 100K in a hunt, only to discover that they are the hunted, but this time they mess with the wrong girls and must deal with the consequences.

Title: Terminator II
Description: In a polluted future Venice researchers work to improve the situation. One day, unknown forces start killing them. A team of soldiers and a couple of civilians is sent to investigate. Soon, they encounter strange murderous creatures.

Title: Rurouni Kenshin Part II: Kyoto Inferno
Description: Kenshin Himura goes up against pure evil Makoto Shishio who is attempting to overthrow the Meiji government. The fate of the country hangs in the balance as Kenshin Himura takes up the sword that he vowed to never draw again.

Title: The Dukes of Hazzard: Reunion!
Description: The Good Ole Boys return to try to save Hazzard Swamp and Uncle Jesse's farm from being destroyed by a crooked developer's (Mama Josephine Max) plans to build a theme park. To do so, they have to dust off the General Lee and win a cross-country moonshine race. The plot thickens when Mama Max stops at nothing to prevent Bo and Luke from running in the race, including kidnapping Daisy.

Title: WrestleMania XL
Description: The Undisputed WWE Universal Championship will be on the line when Roman Reigns defends his title against the winner of the 2024 Royal Rumble, Cody Rhodes. The Scottish Warrior Drew McIntyre will finally get his chance to win a world title in front of the masses as he faces World Heavyweight Champion Seth "Freakin" Rollins at The Showcase of the Immortals. Plus a big tag team match on night 1 where Cody Rhodes and World Heavyweight Champion Seth "Freakin" Rollins will go head to head with Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson and Undisputed WWE Universal Champion Roman Reigns in a match with huge WrestleMania implications. Bayley is hellbent on seizing the WWE Women's Champion when she goes to war against her former ally IYO SKY at WrestleMania. 'Mami' Rhea Ripley defends her Women's World Title against 'The Man' Becky Lynch in what should be a legendary championship fight and many more.

Title: Outcast
Description: A mysterious warrior teams up with the daughter and son of a deposed Chinese Emperor to defeat their cruel brother, who seeks their deaths.

Title: Missing in Action 2: The Beginning
Description: Prequel to the first Missing In Action, set in the early 1980s it shows the capture of Colonel Braddock during the Vietnam war in the 1970s, and his captivity with other American POWs in a brutal prison camp, and his plans to escape.

Title: Code Name: Geronimo
Description: A group of Navy SEALs comes to learn the identity of their target: Osama bin Laden.

Title: Gallowwalkers
Description: A cursed gunman (Snipes) whose victims come back from the dead recruits a young warrior to help in the fight against a gang of zombies.

Title: The Warrant
Description: After fighting in the Civil War, two Union Army buddies find themselves on opposite sides of the law with the post-war peace at risk.

Title: Never Too Young to Die
Description: After a top-secret agent is murdered, his estranged son, a high-school gymnast, teams up with his dad's attractive female partner to stop the psychopathic hermaphroditic gang leader who killed him and now plans a major terrorist attack.

Title: Raging Fire
Description: Bong is a hardline cop with a long history of success, but his past comes back to haunt him when a sting is attacked by a group led by his former protégé, a man set on destroying everyone who ever wronged him.

Title: Certain Fury
Description: During a courtroom shootout, a teenage sex worker and small-time crook wind up on the run to fight their way together through the drug underworld.

Title: Sniper: Special Ops
Description: When the mission to rescue a U.S. Congressman who has been kidnapped by the Taliban goes sideways, Army sniper and his partner are left behind. Now, they must survive in enemy territory and wait for their unit to come back for them.

Title: The Sea Hawk
Description: Geoffrey Thorpe, a buccaneer, is hired by Queen Elizabeth I to nag the Spanish Armada. The Armada is waiting for an attack on England and Thorpe surprises them with attacks on their galleons where he shows his skills with the sword.

Title: Warriors of Future
Description: A meteorite brings an extraterrestrial life to the earth. When powerful alien creatures threaten humanity, Commander Sing Lee's elite forces are almost wiped out, and the surviving soldier Tai Loi discovers an even bigger conspiracy.

Title: 100 Yards
Description: Follows two bitter rivals as they duel for stewardship of a wushu academy.

Title: Ghost in the Shell 2.0
Description: A hacker known as the Puppet Master is hunted by a female cyborg cop and her partner. This film is a revised version of Ghost in the Shell (1995).

Title: Night of the Twisters
Description: The residents of a small town come face to face with a deadly and unpredictable series of tornadoes. Among them is one boy struggling to keep his family safe in the dangerous weather.

Title: No Tears for the Dead
Description: A hit man traumatized from accidentally killing a young girl during a job is given the mission to eliminate her mother, and begins the ultimate fight to save her life.

Title: The Heir Apparent: Largo Winch
Description: After a powerful billionaire is murdered, his secret adoptive son must race to prove his legitimacy, find his father's killers, and stop them from taking over his financial empire.

Title: Daughter of the Wolf
Description: A military veteran hunts the men who kidnapped her son.

Title: Young Ones
Description: Set in the future when water is hard to find, a teenage boy sets out to protect his family and survive.

Title: Guntur Kaaram
Description: Years after his mother abandons him and remarries, a man demands answers when he's asked to sign a document denying he is her son as she runs for office.

Title: Black Friday
Description: A film about the investigations following the 1993 serial Bombay bomb blasts, told through the different stories of the people involved --police, conspirators, victims, middlemen.

Title: Batman: Death in the Family
Description: An anthology series of 5 DC showcase: Death in the Family, Sgt. Rock, Adam Strange, The Phantom Stranger and Death.

Title: The Negotiation
Description: An ace crisis negotiator faces off against a cold-blooded hostage taker. Over the course of 21 hours, she attempts to crack his unusually calm demeanor and force him to reveal his motivations.

Title: Code Name Banshee
Description: Caleb, a former government assassin in hiding, who resurfaces when his protégé, the equally deadly killer known as Banshee, discovers a bounty has been placed on Caleb's head.

Title: A Breed Apart
Description: A conservationist and a widow meet a mountain climber hired to steal bald-eagle eggs.

Title: Phineas and Ferb the Movie: Across the 2nd Dimension
Description: Phineas and Ferb discover that Perry is a secret agent, and they all get stuck in an alternate dimension where Doofenschmirtz is the ruler of the tri-state area.

Title: The Hunters
Description: In 1952, during the Korean War, two American pilots become bitter enemies over the same woman but must shelve their personal feud when confronted by deadly Chinese MIG fighter jets in battle.

Title: Swindle
Description: When a boy named Ben finds an old baseball card in his house, his friend Griffin tells him to sell it. However when he does he is swindled out of $1.2 million, and Griffin decides to assemble a team in order to get the card back.

Title: Resident Evil: Degeneration
Description: Leon S. Kennedy and Claire Redfield must battle a rogue warrior seeking revenge after unleashing the deadly G-Virus, whilst a mutated monster goes on a rampage.

Title: Conquest
Description: A young man, armed with a magical bow and arrows, embarks on a mystical journey through a mystical land to rid it of all evil and joins forces with an outlaw to take down an evil witch bent on claiming the magic bow for evil.

Title: Gumraah
Description: The murder investigation of a young man takes an unexpected turn when the cops discover that the prime suspect has a lookalike.

Title: Regular Show: The Movie
Description: To save the universe, and their friendship, Mordecai and Rigby must defeat an evil volleyball coach.

Title: Population Purge
Description: A government program poisons millions. An immune grandfather-granddaughter duo survive, hunted by ruthless scalpers and an official determined to save his son, leading to a fight for survival amidst the chaos.

Title: The Recall
Description: When five friends vacation at a remote lake house they expect nothing less than a good time, unaware that planet Earth is under an alien invasion and mass-abduction.

Title: Getaway
Description: To save his kidnapped wife, Brent Magna must drive at the orders of a mysterious man.

Title: The Pirates: The Last Royal Treasure
Description: In the Joseon era, a brave crew of pirates and bandits brave the rough waters and try to decipher the clues to find the lost royal gold before their rivals do.

Title: 1990: The Bronx Warriors
Description: In a post-apocalyptic New York City, a policeman infiltrates the Bronx, which has become a battleground for several murderous street gangs.

Title: Lake Placid: Legacy
Description: A group of urban explorers venture to a quiet lake in upstate Maine that is home to a deadly and forgotten secret. Unfortunately for them, they quickly discover they're not alone and encounter a deadly threat that can kill them all.

Title: Our Girl
Description: Our Girl is the story of Molly Dawes, born and raised in the London Borough of Newham. Molly is the eldest of seven kids with little future, an abusive father, and a mother who always wanted more for her. Leaving school with no qualifications, Molly has a part-time job in a local nail bar. Drunk and despondent on the evening of her 18th birthday, she throws up in the doorway of an Army Recruitment Office. She doesn't know it then, but it's an action that will change her life forever...

Title: Deadlock
Description: An ex-military man working at a Georgia power plant has to spring into action to prevent disaster when a group of rogue soldiers gain control of the plant and take the employees hostage.

Title: Berserk: The Golden Age Arc II - The Battle for Doldrey
Description: For three years, Guts believed his mission was to pursue Griffith's dream together with him. But in order to become Griffith's equal and truly be called his friend, Guts realizes he will have to leave the Band of the Hawk.

Title: Stolen Girl
Description: An American woman spends more than ten years tracking down her daughter who was abducted and taken to the Middle East by the child's father.

Title: A.R.M
Description: Set in the Northern Kerala in 1900, 1950 and 1990, three generations of heroes, Maniyan, Kunjikelu and Ajayan, try to protect the most important treasure of the land.

Title: Hell Up in Harlem
Description: A gangster in Harlem must rescue his ex-wife, who has been kidnapped by the Mafia.

Title: Taxi 3
Description: Out to stop a new gang disguised as Santa Claus, Emilien and Daniel must also handle major changes in their personal relationships.

Title: Close Range
Description: A rogue soldier turned outlaw is thrust into a fight with a dirty sheriff and the cartel he works for to protect his niece and sister.

Title: The Organization
Description: In San Francisco, Police Lieutenant Virgil Tibbs helps a group of idealistic vigilantes expose a drug ring controlled by powerful businessmen.

Title: Essex Boys
Description: The 1995 Rettendon triple murder: three drug dealers, Patrick Tate, Craig Rolfe, and Tony Tucker, lured under pretext of a deal, shot execution-style in their Range Rover. Depicts the case's events objectively.

Title: Puppet Princess
Description: A family who builds special karakuri puppets is slain by an evil warlord. But one member, the princess, survives, and uses her skill with puppets to go on a quest for vengeance.

Title: Well
Description: Laci comes to live at a run-down gas station with his long-lost father. A van arrives with four prostitutes and their handlers, and we learn that that Laci's father has something to hide. The gang resolves to wait... for what? AKA Primal.

Title: Appleseed
Description: In a utopian society created at the end of the third world war, a female warrior who has been plucked from the badlands begins to see cracks in this new facade. And what does this community have planned for the rest of humankind?

Title: Raazi
Description: A Kashmiri woman agrees to marry a Pakistani army officer in order to spy on Pakistan during the Indo-Pakistan War of 1971.

Title: Ghajini
Description: Sanjay Ramaswamy, who is suffering from short-term memory loss, sets out on a quest to find and eliminate the people responsible for his ladylove Kalpana's murder.

Title: Godzilla: King of the Monsters!
Description: An American reporter visiting Tokyo becomes a witness to the city's destruction by a dinosaur-like beast awoken from undersea hibernation by atom bomb testing.

Title: Myth of Man
Description: Ella embarks on a whimsical odyssey between life and death, convinced she has received a message from her creator.

Title: Collide
Description: An American backpacker gets involved with a ring of drug smugglers as their driver, though he winds up on the run from his employers across Cologne high-speed Autobahn.

Title: Ratchet & Clank
Description: When the galaxy comes under the threat of a nefarious space captain, a mechanic and his newfound robot ally join an elite squad of combatants to save the universe.

Title: Real Men
Description: A womanizing CIA agent and an insecure insurance agent are paired together to make sure a deal goes through with aliens for the future of mankind.

Title: Vedaa
Description: The journey of a young woman, who faces and resists a repressive system against portrayal of an antagonist.

Title: SAGA: Curse of the Shadow
Description: A secret cabal, The Shadow, works to bring about the return of Goth Azul - the Undead God - in the rich world of SAGA, populated by elves, orcs, dwarves and dragons.

Title: The Dirty South
Description: When the small town big shot goes after the deed to her family's bar, a heartbreaking bartender takes extreme measures to keep it.

Title: Nekrotronic
Description: A man discovers that he is part of a secret sect of magical beings who hunt down and destroy demons in the Internet.

Title: Tiger 3
Description: Tiger and Zoya are back - to save the country and their family. This time it's personal.

Title: Range 15
Description: Veterans wake up after a night of partying to find out that the zombie apocalypse has spread across the United States.

Title: Deathstalker IV: Match of Titans
Description: Deathstalker must defend his remaining comrades, his life, and his newfound love in the battle against an evil army of stone warriors and the wicked queen who created them.

Title: Pursuit of the Graf Spee
Description: In the first major naval battle of World War II, the British Navy must find and destroy a powerful German warship.

Title: Freebie and the Bean
Description: Two reckless San Francisco police detectives finally obtain evidence against a local crime boss, and while waiting for a witness to arrive before making an arrest, they have to discreetly guard his life against an assassination attempt.

Title: Stewardess School
Description: The zany "stewdents" at a wacky flight attendants' school have all sorts of wild and crazy high-flying adventures in this '80s comedy.

Title: Eliminators
Description: Thomas, widower and ex federal agent, hides in London with his daughter. 3 men break in. Thomas kills them. His photo ends on TV. A US crime boss sends a killer to London.

Title: The Seven Magnificent Gladiators
Description: A bandit leader endowed with supernatural powers by his sorceress mother makes yearly raids on a peasant village. However, the women of the village come into possession of a magic sword, and go in search of a hero who is able to wield it and save their village from the evil bandit.

Title: Farewell, Friend
Description: After an overseas deployment, two former French Foreign Legion members plan to break into the vault of a French corporation.

Title: Devaki Nandana Vasudeva
Description: Driven by fears of astrological prophecy, Kamsaraja torments his sister's family, convinced her child will cause his downfall. When imprisoned, Krishna shields the family from Kamsaraja's sinister schemes.

Title: Wheelman
Description: A getaway driver for a bank robbery realizes he has been double crossed and races to find out who betrayed him.

Title: White Elephant
Description: An ex-marine enforcer must battle his conscience and code of honor when he is forced to do things for the mob.

Title: Moon 44
Description: An unconventional corporate agent is given the task of shaping a group of violent criminals and technical wizards into a helicopter defense force assigned to protect a mining station on a remote moon.

Title: Inside Man: Most Wanted
Description: An NYPD hostage negotiator teams up with a federal agent to rescue dozens of tourists held hostage during a 10-hour siege at the U.S. Federal Reserve.

Title: King Kong vs. Godzilla
Description: A UN reporter covers the appearance of a prehistoric monster that emerges from hibernation, while a pharmaceutical company seeks publicity with a monster of their own.

Title: The Million Eyes of Sumuru
Description: Sumuru, a megalomaniacal femme fatale, makes a bid for world domination by eliminating male leaders and replacing them with her sexy female agents.

Title: The Crimson Pirate
Description: During the 1700s, pirate Captain Vallo seizes a British warship and gets involved in various money-making schemes involving Caribbean rebels led by El Libre, British envoy Baron Jose Gruda, and a beautiful courtesan named Consuelo.

Title: Merantau
Description: A young man from the countryside uses his skills in silat martial arts to survive the slave trade.

Title: Python
Description: After a military plane crash near a small American town, a giant man-eating snake sets off on a killing spree. The locals must find a way to eliminate the snake, with the help of a scientist who knows about the snake to kill it.

Title: Seobok
Description: Ex intelligence agent Ki Heon is tasked with safely transporting Seo Bok, the first ever human clone, who holds the secret of eternal life. Several forces try to take control of Seo Bok to serve their own agendas.

Title: Jodhaa Akbar
Description: A sixteenth century love story about a marriage of alliance that gave birth to true love between a great Mughal emperor, Akbar, and a Rajput princess, Jodha.

Title: Hijacked: Flight 285
Description: A convicted murderer is escorted by marshals on a regular flight from Phoenix to Dallas. Shortly after take-off, two of his aides, traveling as ordinary passengers, take control of the flight and free him. He demands 20 million dollars in bonds upon landing. And a sick passenger, bad weather or mechanical problems won't stop him.

Title: What Have They Done to Your Daughters?
Description: A district attorney and two inspectors and discover that a girl's apparent suicide is linked to a teenage prostitution ring which employs a motorcycle-riding killer to tie up loose ends.

Title: Muscle
Description: Plot kept under wraps.

Title: The Sicilian
Description: Egocentric bandit Salvatore Giuliano fights the Church, the Mafia, and the landed gentry while leading a populist movement for Sicilian independence.

Title: Battle Royale II
Description: Three years after the failure of the last BR program, a second act is forged and a class of students is sent to an island with one objective: kill international terrorist Shuya Nanahara.

Title: Dollman
Description: A hard-boiled intergalactic policeman lands on Earth, where he is thirteen inches tall.

Title: The Lady in Red
Description: After being in the wrong place at the wrong time, a naïve farm girl moves to Chicago, where she becomes trapped in a vicious cycle of prostitution and crime abetted by John Dillinger.

Title: Wilderness
Description: Juvenile delinquents are sent to a small British island after a fellow prisoner's death, where they have to fight for survival.

Title: Rogue Elements: A Ryan Drake Story
Description: Ryan Drake, hoping to recover an asset, must infiltrate a fortified base, his every move watched by a shadowy figure. He silently makes his way to the base and rescues the asset. Hell breaks out when the figure makes its presence known.

Title: Fortress: Sniper's Eye
Description: Story revolves around a top-secret resort for retired U.S. intelligence officers.

Title: Memes & Nightmares
Description: NBA Twitter king's quest unravels the fleeting nature of online content and human bonds in the digital era, shaping our ephemeral connections.

Title: MobLand
Description: Bloody Tale Between The Irish Mob and the Italian Mafia Started by the Mexican drug Cartel.

Title: Catch .44
Description: Three women are sent to intercept a major drug deal at a diner at 3 AM and get the money. Simple - save for Murphy's law: anything that can go wrong will go wrong.

Title: Beastmaster 2: Through the Portal of Time
Description: Dar is a warrior who can talk to the beasts. He is forced to travel to Earth to stop his evil brother from stealing an atomic bomb and turning their native land from a desert into, well - a desert.

Title: Emmanuelle 5
Description: Emmanuelle has a streak of bad luck that starts when she is stripped by a mob of adoring fans at the Cannes Film Festival. Her rotten luck continues when the dictator of a banana republic uses the screening of one of her films as a pretext to get her into his country. Our heroine finds herself admitted into his harem as a slave.

Title: Mysterious Island
Description: To escape evils of the Civil War, Cyrus removes his small family and random war prisoners by way of hot air balloon. Once landing on an island, the group finds they are surrounded by danger from giant insects and gold-craving pirates. Turned away by the only safe haven on the island, owned by Captain Nemo, played by Sir Patrick Stewart, the group is forced to find shelter and survive.

Title: Laila
Description: Sonu Model, a renowned beautician from the old city, is forced to disguise himself as Laila, leading to a series of comedic, romantic, and action-packed events. Chaos ensues in this hilarious laugh riot.

Title: The Runner
Description: A high-powered attorney must race through London to save her abducted son while following cryptic commands from a mysterious caller.

Title: Kaabil
Description: A blind dubbing artist seeks revenge against a corrupt politician and his brother, after his wife is raped and killed.

Title: Appleseed Alpha
Description: A tough, cute woman and a cyborg arrive at a depopulated, post WW3 Times Sq. They leave the ruins of NYC with 2 on a secret mission.

Title: Uptown Saturday Night
Description: At Madame Zenobia's illegal nightclub, when Steve Jackson and Wardell Franklin get robbed of their wallets containing a winning lottery ticket, they set out to recover it.

Title: The Patriot
Description: A respected doctor must race against time to find a cure for a lethal virus unleashed by a paramilitary militia leader.

Title: Protector
Description: Former war hero Nikki's peaceful life is shattered when her daughter is kidnapped. Thrust into the criminal underworld while hunted by cops and military, she must fight to rescue her child.

Title: Bigfoot
Description: Two former musicians face off in the hunt for the legendary mountain creature.

Title: Home of the Brave
Description: Three soldiers struggle to readjust to life at home after returning home from a lengthy tour in Iraq.

Title: My Hero Academia: Two Heroes
Description: All Might and Deku accept an invitation to visit an artificial floating island called I-Island, where they fight a villain who takes the city hostage.

Title: Point Blank
Description: An ER nurse and a career criminal are forced into an unlikely partnership in taking down a ring of corrupt cops threatening the lives of both their families.

Title: 12 to Midnight
Description: A detective, despondent after the murder of his wife and forced to resign, is brought back to the force when a serial killer appears to be taunting him and turns out to be superhuman.

Title: Main Hoon Na
Description: An army major goes undercover as a college student. His mission is both professional and personal: to protect his general's daughter from a radical militant, and to find his estranged half-brother.

Title: Herd
Description: When a woman trying to outrun her past ends up trapped between a zombie outbreak and warring militia groups, she must fight to find her way back home.

Title: The Shaft
Description: When the elevators in New York's 102-story Millennium Building start to malfunction, mechanic Mark Newman is sent to find the cause. After a series of gruesome and deadly "accidents" occur, Mark joins forces with spunky reporter Jennifer.

Title: Sahara
Description: After the fall of Tobruk in 1942, during the Allied retreat in the Libyan desert, an American tank picks-up a motley group of survivors but they face advancing Germans and a lack of water.

Title: Primitive War
Description: Vietnam. 1968. A recon unit known as Vulture Squad is sent to an isolated jungle valley to uncover the fate of a missing Green Beret platoon. They soon discover they are not alone.

Title: The Son of No One
Description: A young cop is assigned to a precinct in the working class neighborhood where he grew up, and an old secret threatens to destroy his life and his family.

Title: Knock Off
Description: A fashion designer must join forces with a C.I.A. agent to combat terrorism.

Title: The Godson
Description: Marco is the ambitious godson of a crime boss. His attempt to quickly rise to the top leads to his downfall.

Title: Barbarian Queen II: The Empress Strikes Back
Description: In a final and epic battle in the thrilling sequel to the now classic "Barbarian Queen", Althalia, leads a revolt of peasants and female warriors against the wicked ruler, Arkaris, to regain her throne.

Title: Rurouni Kenshin: The Legend Ends
Description: Shishio has set sail in his ironclad ship to bring down the Meiji government and return Japan to chaos, carrying Kaoru with him. In order to stop him in time, Kenshin trains with his old master to learn his final technique.

Title: The Hunted
Description: An American businessman visiting Nagoya, Japan, meets a woman in a hotel bar. Returning to her room, 3 ninjas kill her and wound him, but he sees the ninja boss' face. Now, he's the prime target of a dangerous ninja cult.

Title: Lazarus
Description: A super powered vigilante fights an organization to free a city from darkness.

Title: Pataakha
Description: Based on Charan Singh Pathik's short story Do Behnein, Pataakha narrates the story of two feuding sisters who realize the true nature of their relationship only after marriage "separates" them.

Title: The Marine 4: Moving Target
Description: Jake Carter is assigned to protect a "high-value package," a beautiful whistleblower trying to expose a corrupt army defense contractor.

Title: Reflet dans un diamant mort
Description: A retired spy suspects his former adversaries have resurfaced when his intriguing neighbor vanishes.

Title: Reprisal
Description: A bank manager haunted by a violent heist that took the life of a coworker teams up with his ex-cop neighbor to bring down the assailant, initiating an explosive counterattack that brings all three men to the breaking point.

Title: Justice League: Gods and Monsters
Description: In an alternate universe, very different versions of DC's Trinity (Superman, Batman and Wonder Woman), who operate outside of the law, are framed for murders of prominent scientist and the government decides to take them out.

Title: Kill Me Three Times
Description: Professional hit-man Charlie Wolfe finds himself in three tales of murder, blackmail and revenge after a botched contract assignment.

Title: Godzilla, Mothra and King Ghidorah: Giant Monsters All-Out Attack
Description: A reporter, notorious for working on pseudo-documentaries, must uncover the legend of the three guardian monsters who must rise to defend Japan from the vengeful spirits within Godzilla.

Title: TC 2000
Description: Somewhere in an apocalyptic future, where the rich live underground and the poor are left to fend for themselves on the surface by forming gangs, corrupt members of an underground security force plot to destroy the surface.

Title: Cut Throat City
Description: Set after Hurricane Katrina, four boyhood friends out of options reluctantly accept an offer to pull off a dangerous heist in the heart of New Orleans.

Title: Phantasm: Ravager
Description: The final installment of the long-running Phantasm series.

Title: Lost Boys: The Thirst
Description: Multi-arrow crossbow? Check. Holy water grenade launcher? Ready. Stake-shooting M134? Got that, too. Edgar Frog is locked and loaded for his bloodiest badass battle yet with the undead.

Title: Vendetta
Description: Detective Mason's wife is murdered by an ex-convict he jailed. He gets arrested intentionally to seek vengeance inside prison, uncovering a criminal conspiracy those involved will kill to protect.

Title: Called to Duty
Description: North Kiyung is threatening U.S with nuclear attacks and missile tests. U.S plans to strike back and train best pilots. However Air force leans on Navy's best fighter Lt. Andrew "Bells". Few hours before attack the drama unfolds.

Title: Chhota Bheem Aur Krishna
Description: Centuries after the end of a conqueror's rule, he is mysteriously back from the dead. It's up to Bheem to save Dholakpur from being taken over.

Title: 3 Days in Malay
Description: A small group must defend an airfield for three days against the Japanese assault during the fight for Malay in World War 2.

Title: Mission: Cross
Description: In the ultimate test of marriage, an agent-turned-househusband gets tangled in a perilous mission with his detective wife, who's clueless about his past.

Title: Versus
Description: There are 666 portals that connect this world to the other side. These are concealed from all human beings. Somewhere in Japan exists the 444th portal.... The forest of resurrection.

Title: The Death of the Incredible Hulk
Description: When Scientist Dr. Ronold Pratt and his wife are kidnapped, David Banner must become The Incredible Hulk for one last time

Title: Roadkill
Description: Vengeance rides the open road when a young woman traveling alone encounters a renegade drifter and ends up in a fight for her life.

Title: Godfather
Description: A political leader's death leads to a power struggle. Amid corruption, greed and deceit, an unlikely opponent steps up.

Title: Mission Stardust
Description: A team of astronauts is sent to the moon to rescue an alien who is seeking help to save her dying race. They are attacked by a force of bandit robots and discover that enemy spies are out to kill the alien.

Title: The King
Description: King Kamehameha fulfills his life-long prophecy of uniting the Hawaiian islands.

Title: Swashbuckler
Description: A pirate and a hot-tempered noblewoman join forces to protect Jamaica from a tyrant.

Title: No Retreat, No Surrender 2
Description: American kickboxer Scott Wylde travels to Cambodia to rescue his Vietnamese girlfriend from Russian and Vietnamese forces.

Title: The Firefighters
Description: After drastic tragedies and changes, firefighters must see themselves helping out the entire world each day, even though in personal life and in work, going against all odds.

Title: Turbulence
Description: After a shootout on a flight transporting prisoners, a flight attendant must outwit a smooth-talking serial killer and land the plane herself.

Title: Supercool
Description: Lifelong friends Neil and Gilbert's undeniable bond is tested to the limits when Neil makes a magical wish that comes true. With the assistance of Neil's charismatic neighbor, Jimmy, and Gilbert's wild ideas, Neil endures one epic night.

Title: Viking
Description: Kievan Rus, late 10th century. After the death of his father, the young Viking prince Vladimir of Novgorod is forced into exile across the frozen sea.

Title: The Moderator
Description: After the murder of her two Scandinavian friends in Morocco, a Russian blogger decides to do her own justice.

Title: Every Last One of Them
Description: A man looking for his missing daughter, but his search uncovers a larger conspiracy involving a Chinatown-derail big capitalism deal over water rights.

Title: Ra.One
Description: A video game company inadvertently creates and lets loose into the real world a single minded villain obsessed with defeating his archnemesis, a young child, in this fast paced sci-fi action thriller.

Title: Jurassic Park: Island Survival
Description: A science team goes missing on Isla Nublar. Masrani Corp sends a security team to find them and retrieve embryos from an abandoned research lab, now overgrown. An escaped dinosaur complicates the mission.

Title: Highlander: The Source
Description: Duncan MacLeod and his fellow Immortals quest to locate the Grail of their world.

Title: Assault on Wall Street
Description: Jim, an average New Yorker, lives with a sick but loving wife. Suddenly, everything changes when the economy crashes and causes him to lose everything. Filled with anger and rage, Jim goes to seek revenge for the life taken from him.

Title: Dragon Ball Z: Resurrection 'F'
Description: Frieza is reborn and achieves the last of his transformations, and it is up to Goku and his warrior friends to join forces to fight the enemy who has returned from the dead.

Title: Cracka
Description: A present day white supremacist gets thrust back in time where the African Americans rule and the whites are the enslaved.

Title: Chick Fight
Description: When Anna Wyncomb is introduced to an underground, all-female fight club in order to turn the mess of her life around, she discovers she is much more personally connected to the history of the club than she could ever imagine.

Title: The Jungle Book
Description: A boy raised by wild animals tries to adapt to human village life.

Title: Sharkansas Women's Prison Massacre
Description: When a fracking environmental accident rips apart the earth's crust, the resulting hole lets out prehistoric sharks from underground that target a group of women and trap them in a cabin.

Title: Shinjuku Incident
Description: A simple Chinese immigrant wages a perilous war against one of the most powerful criminal organizations on the planet.

Title: Waist Deep
Description: An ex-convict (Tyrese) gets tangled up with a gang after his car is hijacked with his son inside.

Title: Battlestar Galactica: Blood & Chrome
Description: The adventures of young William Adama in the First Cylon War.

Title: Lady Terminator
Description: The spirit of an ancient evil queen possesses the body of a young anthropological student, who then goes on a murderous rampage.

Title: Occupation Rainfall: Chapter 2
Description: Continuing on from Occupation Rainfall, Earth's survivors must face the final onslaught of the Alien invaders and band together to save the planet from impending destruction.

Title: Tracers
Description: Wanted by the Chinese mafia, a New York City bike messenger escapes into the world of parkour after meeting a beautiful stranger.

Title: Deathstalker and the Warriors from Hell
Description: The third thrilling saga of Deathstalker pits him against the evil wizard and ruler of the Southland, Troxartes, and his band of undead warriors.

Title: Macross: Do You Remember Love?
Description: Earth braces for an invasion of the Zentradi.

Title: Hollow Man II
Description: A Seattle detective and a biologist are on the run from a dangerous invisible assassin gone rogue.

Title: Day Watch
Description: When Anton, a Warrior of Light, is falsely accused of murdering some vampires, he embarks on a journey to find the real killer and search for an ancient object that has the power to alter destiny.

Title: Escape from the 21st Century
Description: The story follows three friends who discover they have the power to travel back and forth 20 years with a sneeze. However, the future is not as good as they hoped, and they need to take on the responsibility of saving the world.

Title: Electra
Description: Serum gives youth, health, superpowers. Wheelchair-bound billionaire Marcus wants it, sends assassins. Couple tries to escape with serum. Electra also wants serum, which is now transmitted sexually.

Title: Scarlett
Description: A college student must draw upon all the skills her spy-father taught her to protect herself and save her father from weapons dealers.

Title: Superman: Doomsday
Description: When LexCorps accidentally unleash a murderous creature, Doomsday, Superman meets his greatest challenge as a champion. Based on the "The Death of Superman" storyline that appeared in DC Comics' publications in the 1990s.

Title: Red Cliff II
Description: Second and final part of epic tale about a legendary battle that changed the course of China history.

Title: That Time I Got Reincarnated as a Slime the Movie: Scarlet Bond
Description: Corporate worker Mikami is stabbed by a random killer, is reborn to an alternate world. But he is reborn as a slime. He is Thrown into this new world with the name Rimuru, he begins his quest to create a world that's welcoming to all races

Title: Shangri-La Suite
Description: Two young, damaged lovers head to Los Angeles to kill the King of Rock n Roll in the summer of 1974.

Title: Batman vs. Robin
Description: While Damian Wayne struggles to cope with Batman's no-killing rule, he soon starts to believe that his destiny lies within a secret society known as, The Court of Owls.

Title: Endangered Species
Description: Jack Halsey takes his wife, their adult kids, and a friend for a dream vacation in Kenya. But as they venture off alone into a wilderness park, their safari van is flipped over by an angry rhino, leaving them injured and desperate.

Title: The Osiris Child
Description: Set in the future in a time of interplanetary colonization, an unlikely pair race against an impending global crisis and are confronted by the monsters that live inside us all.

Title: Play It Cool
Description: An exploitation sex drama just this side of pinku-eiga with yakuza elements.

Title: UI
Description: UI transcends language barriers as it addresses a global issue.

Title: The Young Savages
Description: A district attorney investigates three white teenagers accused of murdering a blind Puerto Rican kid.

Title: Rise of the Footsoldier 3
Description: Notorious gangster, Pat Tate, rises through the ranks of Essex's criminal underworld. A prequel to the 'Rise of the Footsoldier' franchise.

Title: Death Race
Description: In the North African desert in World War II, a damaged American fighter plane that is unable to take off tries to evade and destroy a pursuing Nazi tank.

Title: Marvel One-Shot: Agent Carter
Description: Frustrated at being marginalized at work, Peggy Carter goes on an unauthorized solo field mission.

Title: Death Race 2050
Description: Five long decades after Death Race 2000 (1975), in the overpopulated United Corporations of America, the annual Death Race is about to begin. This time, Frankenstein is up against no-nonsense challengers. How many points will he score?

Title: Captain America
Description: Superhero Captain America battles the evil forces of the archvillain called The Scarab, who poisons his enemies and steals a secret device capable of destroying buildings by sound vibrations.

Title: Operation Dumbo Drop
Description: To keep the loyalty of a village during the Vietnam war, a U.S. Army officer and his unit struggle to deliver it a live elephant.

Title: Bait
Description: An ex-con is used by police to lure a criminal out of hiding.

Title: Dudes & Dragons
Description: Evil wizard Lord Tensley captures princess Ennogard, releases dragon to destroy love until she accepts him. She sends dragonfly to find Dragon Warrior. Brothers Camilan, Ramicus journey to rescue her, defeat dragon, overthrow Tensley.

Title: Sabata
Description: A master gunfighter sides with a banjo-playing drifter and a Mexican tramp to foil the dignitaries of Daugherty, who want to use stolen army money to buy land that the railroad will cross.

Title: The Bag Man
Description: A criminal bides his time at a seedy motel, waiting for his boss after killing several men and making away with a mystery bag.

Title: Sniper: Reloaded
Description: The son of a renowned sniper decides to track down the sniper who ambushed his squad when they were sent to rescue a white planter in the Congo.

Title: Arena
Description: David Lord finds himself forced into the savage world of a modern gladiatorial arena, where men fight to the death for the entertainment of the online masses.

Title: Commitment
Description: The son of a North Korean spy decides to follow in his father's footsteps to protect his little sister.

Title: The Legend of Johnny Jones
Description: Set in the housing projects of New Jersey. A young man who has known only poverty and abuse all his life suffers a mental breakdown and embarks on a killing spree unlike any other in history.

Title: Neon Genesis Evangelion: Death & Rebirth
Description: A recap of the first 24 episodes of Neon Genesis Evangelion, followed by a 30-minute continuation of the plot that would later form the first third of The End of Evangelion.

Title: Donnybrook
Description: Two men prepare to compete in a legendary bare-knuckle fight where the winner gets a $100,000 prize.

Title: Destroy All Monsters
Description: In 1999, a race of she-aliens, the Kilaaks, brainwash Earth's monsters into attacking major cities, prompting a team of astronauts to stop the invaders while the monsters battle Ghidorah.

Title: Dead Man Running
Description: Nick's borrowed money from Thigo (a loan shark) and he's behind with his payments. Thigo gives him 24-hours to repay the $100,000 he owes and takes his mother hostage as an extra incentive for Nick to come up with the money.

Title: The Warlords
Description: China, 1860s: Having his army slaughtered, General Qingyun joins 2 bandit leaders in raids on rebels and in blood oath. They form a Qing loyal army with eyes on rebel held Suzhou and Nanjing.

Title: Turtles Forever
Description: The Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles meet their match -- Literally! The modern, gritty Ninja Turtles must team up with their classic cartoon counterparts to stop two Shredders and their plans of multi-dimensional scale.

Title: Tremors 4: The Legend Begins
Description: A prequel to Tremors (1990), this movie tells us about how the town of Perfection, Nevada became founded and how they defended it against the Graboids with the help of Burt Gummer's ancestor, Hiram.

Title: Desierto
Description: A group of people trying to cross the border from Mexico into the United States encounter a racist man who has taken border patrol duties into his own hands.

Title: Men in War
Description: During the Korean War, a battle-worn lieutenant and his platoon are behind enemy lines, and have orders to march to Hill 465 for possible relief.

Title: Red Line 7000
Description: The story of three racing drivers and three women, who constantly have to worry for the lives of their boyfriends. Jim Loomis and Mike Marsh drive for Pat Cassarian. Jim expects his fiancée Holly, but before she arrives, he dies in a race. Since she doesn't have the money to travel back, she stays. The young and very ambitious talent Ned Arp joins the team, and immediately starts wooing Pat's sister Julie. Third on the team is womanizer Dan McCall, who brings with him his current girlfriend Gabrielle from Paris. So the basic theme of this movie is, "Whom with whom?"

Title: Fate/stay night [Heaven's Feel] II. lost butterfly
Description: The story focuses on the Holy Grail War and explores the relationship between Shirou Emiya and Sakura Matou, two teenagers participating in this conflict. The story continues immediately from Fate/stay night: Heaven's Feel I. presage flower, following Shirou as he continues to participate in the Holy Grail War even after being eliminated as a master.

Title: Valley of the Dead
Description: Months after bloody combats leave behind thousands of dead in the trenches. Jan Lozano, Captain of the Fifth Brigade has fallen prisoner by an opponent's platoon along with a young driver while carrying out a mission that has been entrusted to him. The possibility of dying executed will soon be overtaken when a new unknown enemy arises. Both rival sides must unite and set their mutual hate aside in order to survive.

Title: Big Legend
Description: An ex-soldier ventures into the Pacific Northwest to uncover the truth behind his fiance's disappearance.

Title: Daphne & Velma
Description: The female future members of Mystery Inc. investigate strange goings-on in their school.

Title: Avenging Force
Description: A senator is targeted by the Pentangle, a right wing paramilitary group. His pal, a former CIA agent and martial artist, tries to help him. The group kidnaps the agent's sister and tries to hunt him down, "The Most Dangerous Game" style.

Title: Bronco Billy
Description: An idealistic, modern-day cowboy struggles to keep his Wild West show afloat in the face of hard luck and waning interest.

Title: Amazon Hot Box
Description: An innocent college student is tossed into a jungle hellhole where she must fight for her life against an evil wardress, psycho inmates, voodoo experiments and the incredible torture machine.

Title: The Shepherd
Description: A former New Orleans cop battles drug cartels and ex-Army Special Forces who are smuggling drugs from Mexico into U.S. through a Texas border town.

Title: The Legend of Conan
Description: The plot is unknown at this time.

Title: Pokémon: Mewtwo Returns
Description: Team Rocket's memories of Mewtwo had been erased, but the Team Rocket scientists' logs have not. After uncovering the logs, they track down Mewtwo and build a Base in a Johto. Ash and company meet Mr. Giovanni for the first time.

Title: Rites of Passage
Description: An anthropology student invites his classmates and professor to his family's abandoned ranch, once a sacred Chumash burial ground, to recreate an ancient ceremony.

Title: Flash Point
Description: A hot-headed inspector takes on a small but powerful Vietnamese-Chinese gang, after a series of crimes and murder attempts committed and putting an undercover cop and his girlfriend in great danger.

Title: The Last Run
Description: A getaway driver comes out of retirement to pull off one last run - one that could send him to an early grave instead.

Title: Off Limits
Description: McGriff and Albaby are probably doing the worst law enforcement job in the world - they are plain clothes U.S. military policemen on duty in war-time Saigon. However, their job becomes even harder when they start investigating the serial killings of local prostitutes. Their prime suspect is high ranking U.S. Army officer which brings their lives in danger.

Title: Cold Eyes
Description: A high-tech police surveillance team attempts to take down a gang of ruthless bank robbers.

Title: Daybreak
Description: This drama, based on Alan Bowne's play "Beirut," takes place in a decrepit New York City of the near future, controlled by a fascist government.

Title: The Flim-Flam Man
Description: A rural con artist and an army deserter cheat the townsfolk and are aided by a rich gal who shields the fleeing duo from the wrath of the pursuing sheriff.

Title: Journey to the West: Conquering the Demons
Description: Tang Sanzang, an aspiring Buddhist hero tries to protect a village from three demons. He develops complex feelings for Miss Duan, the demon hunter who repeatedly helps him, and finally quests to meet the legendary Monkey King.

Title: Taxi 4
Description: Daniel, the driver of a very special taxi in Marseille, gets a famous soccer player to the stadium in time and later helps his clumsy police friend Émilien catch the dangerous Belgian after he escaped on Émilien's guard.

Title: The Lord of the G-Strings: The Femaleship of the String
Description: A diminutive and seductive Throbbit has been entrusted with the task of destroying the all-powerful G-String that can grant its possessor untold powers.

Title: Superintelligence
Description: When an all-powerful Superintelligence chooses to study average Carol Peters, the fate of the world hangs in the balance. As the A.I. decides to enslave, save or destroy humanity, it's up to Carol to prove that people are worth saving.

Title: Bad Cat
Description: A profane house cat must deal with the arrival of his illegitimate son, an accidental killing, his owner's eviction and more within the course of a day of debauchery and mayhem.

Title: Death Valley
Description: Mercenaries with nothing to lose are hired to rescue a bioengineer imprisoned in a cold war bunker. Upon entering the ominous facility, they find themselves in a fight for their lives when they come under attack from an unknown and deadly creature.

Title: Castle Falls
Description: Rival gangs seek out millions of dollars hidden inside a hospital that's scheduled to be demolished, but first they have to deal with the construction worker who found the loot first.

Title: The Scorpion King: Book of Souls
Description: The Scorpion King teams up with a warrior named Tala, who is the sister of The Nubian King. Together they search for a legendary relic known as The Book of Souls, which will allow them to put an end to an evil warlord.

Title: Bachhala Malli
Description: Spanning various periods in a man's life, this dark, real world drama uses jumps in time to explore the sometimes drastic and shocking consequences of familial and romantic strife

Title: Vampires: Los Muertos
Description: A vampire hunter and a priest fight a band of the walking dead in Mexico.

Title: Maniac Cop 3: Badge of Silence
Description: A priest practicing the Voodoo arts resurrects Matt Cordell, who takes his badge and comes back from the dead to do his bidding.

Title: Wild Oats
Description: Everything changes for Eva when she receives a life insurance check accidentally made out for five million dollars instead of the expected fifty thousand dollars. She and her best friend take the money and head out for the adventure of a lifetime.

Title: Gasoline Alley
Description: A man implicated in the triple homicide of three Hollywood starlets begins his own investigation. Needing assistance, he enlists the two detectives on his tail in order to expose a conspiracy more explosive than any of them imagined.

Title: Grand Theft Auto
Description: A rich girl steals her dad's Rolls Royce and heads off to Las Vegas to get married, but her angry parents, a jealous suitor, and a bunch of reward-seekers are determined to stop her.

Title: Ong Bak 3
Description: Continuing from Ong Bak 2's 1440s, Prince Tien fails to revenge his parents' murder by the evil new ruler. The beaten Tien is rescued. Can he bring peace to the kingdom?

Title: Black Warrant
Description: A semi-retired special ops assassin and a DEA agent cross paths on separate missions to stop a cyber terrorist organization that has built a dangerous machine threatening to attack the power grid and bring catastrophe to the world.

Title: Sugar Hill
Description: A drug dealer tries to get out of the life and start anew with his girlfriend, but the transition is tragically difficult.

Title: Jackdaw
Description: A former motocross champion and army veteran is now caring for his younger brother. Broke, he agrees to do an open water pick up of a mysterious illegal package in the North Sea.

Title: Amsterdamned 2
Description: AMSTERDAMNED 2 is the long-awaited sequel to the movie that is regarded as one of the best action movies coming out of Europe in the eighties. A breathtaking roller coaster from beginning to end in the blood drenched Amsterdam canals.

Title: Hitman 2
Description: After a successful first season, Webtoon "Agent Jun" is about to begin its second season. Out of ideas, Jun uses an anonymous email plot in his Webtoon, only to see real-life terrorist attacks resembling the story unfold.

Title: Project Gutenberg
Description: Hong Kong police are hunting a counterfeiting gang led by a mastermind code-named "Painter". In order to crack this true identity, the police recruit gang member Lee Man to unmask "Painter's" secret identity.

Title: Drum
Description: A mid-19th-century mulatto slave is torn between his success as a pit-fighter and the injustices of white society.

Title: The Seventh Curse
