Description: An adventurer who's been inflicted with a deadly curse during a previous expedition to Thailand goes back to battle an evil sorcerer, his tribal army, and his deadly creatures.

Title: A Force of One
Description: When the detectives of an undercover police unit are being mysteriously killed by a martial artist, a professional kickboxer is hired to assist them.

Title: The Legend of Zelda: A Link to the Past
Description: When an evil long thought gone returns, it is up to Link and Zelda to seek out the Master Sword and stop the dark wizard Agahnim.

Title: A Writer's Odyssey
Description: Six years after the abduction of his daughter, a man is hired to kill the author of a fantasy novel, but the world of the novel seems to intersect with reality.

Title: Justice League: The New Frontier
Description: In the 1950s, a new generation of superheroes must join forces with the community's active veterans and a hostile US government to fight a menace to Earth.

Title: The Protector
Description: Two New York City cops, Billy Wong and Danny Garoni, head to Hong Kong after the daughter of a rich businessman is kidnapped by the drug lord, Mr. Ko.

Title: Agneepath
Description: A young boy's quest for revenge leads him to become a gangster as an adult, and with each day he becomes more and more like his enemies. Can he find vengeance and redemption?

Title: Telefon
Description: A Russian officer is sent to the U.S. to try and stop sleeper agents who will mindlessly attack government entities when they hear certain coded words.

Title: Uncharted: Live Action Fan Film
Description: Treasure hunter Nathan Drake finds himself captured while searching for the lost treasure of the Flor de la Mar.

Title: BloodRayne II: Deliverance
Description: Rayne, the half-human/half-vampire warrior, ventures to America's 1880's Wild West to stop the vampired Billy the Kid and his posse of vampire cowboys.

Title: 'Sheba, Baby'
Description: A Chicago private detective returns back home to Louisville, Kentucky, to help her father fight mobsters.

Title: Unnatural
Description: A morally ambiguous corporation experiments with genetic modification resulting in the creation of a man hunting creature. When it escapes, a group of unsuspecting cabin dwellers become its prey in a horrifying game of cat and mouse.

Title: Run Boy Run
Description: 8-year-old Srulik flees Warsaw ghetto in 1942, survives in forest, lives as Christian orphan Jurek on farm, risks losing Jewish identity. Based on Uri Orlev's bestseller.

Title: Cat Run
Description: When a sexy, high-end escort holds the key evidence to a scandalous government cover-up, two bumbling young detectives become her unlikely protectors from a ruthless assassin hired to silence her.

Title: Convict
Description: Sent to prison because of manslaughter, Ray is challenged both physically and mentally by a sadistic prison boss.

Title: The Hot Rock
Description: Dortmunder and his pals plan to steal a huge diamond from a museum. But this turns out to be only the first time they have to steal it...

Title: Planet of the Dead
Description: A Sequel to Army of the Dead

Title: Adagio
Description: Tangled up with blackmail and crooked cops, the son of a former gangster seeks out his father's old friends, who risk everything to save him.

Title: Extraction
Description: A former CIA operative is kidnapped by a group of terrorists. When his son learns there is no plan for his father to be saved, he launches his own rescue operation.

Title: Bullet Proof
Description: After stealing millions in cash from the drug hiding place of the sadistic mafia boss Temple, a thief finds a stowaway passenger in his getaway car.

Title: Redemption Day
Description: When the love of his life is kidnapped and held for ransom by terrorists, a war hero Brad Paxton races against the clock to rescue her in a daring and deadly operation that pits him against the most powerful and shadowy forces.

Title: Justice League: Throne of Atlantis
Description: When Atlantian troops assault Metropolis as revenge for the death of their king, the Queen seeks help from the Justice League to find her son who has gone missing during the madness.

Title: Zombie Town
Description: When Amy and Mike uncover a centuries-old curse after watching an exclusive film reel, they must quickly track down an infamous filmmaker and navigate a town of hungry zombies before it's too late to break the curse.

Title: Hands of Steel
Description: A cyborg is programmed to kill a scientist who holds the fate of mankind in his hands. He fails and hides in a diner in a desert run by a woman who likes him. The people who sent him are after him and so is the local arm wrestling champ.

Title: Ink
Description: A mysterious creature, known as Ink, steals a child's soul in hopes of using it as a bargaining chip to join the Incubi - the group of supernatural beings responsible for creating nightmares.

Title: The Zero Boys
Description: A group of friends travel to a wilderness area to play a survival game. Soon they unexpectedly find themselves in a real-life survival situation.

Title: Lady Scorpions
Description: A drug enforcement agent teams up with her daughter to save her abducted granddaughter from the powerful head of a criminal organization.

Title: How to Rob a Bank
Description: In this true-crime documentary, a charismatic rebel in 1990s Seattle pulls off an unprecedented string of bank robberies straight out of the movies.

Title: Bionicle: Mask of Light
Description: The island of Mata Nui must face one final threat from the evil Makuta: The Rahkshi. The only hope for the survival of the islanders rests with two Matoran villagers, who must find the seventh Toa and deliver him the Mask of Light.

Title: Out of Death
Description: A corrupt Sheriff's department in a rural mountain town comes undone when an unintended witness throws a wrench into their shady operation.

Title: Best Seller
Description: An ex-hit man wants a police detective/novelist to write his biography.

Title: Shark Warning
Description: Two decades later, a man returns to his hometown after a shark killed his brother. When the shark resurfaces and claims more victims, he forms alliances to hunt down and eliminate the predator once and for all.

Title: Alien Country
Description: Reeling from the news of an unexpected pregnancy, Jimmy and Everly unknowingly release an alien invasion in their small town and learn to work together in order to save each other, their town and evidently, the entire galaxy.

Title: Battle in Seattle
Description: Activists arrive in Seattle, Washington en masse to protest a meeting of the World Trade Organization. Riots and chaos ensue as demonstrators successfully stop the WTO meetings.

Title: Dying of the Light
Description: When a devastating illness threatens to end Evan Lake's career in the C.I.A., he goes rogue to hunt down a terrorist who tortured him during a mission gone awry years ago.

Title: One Piece: Stampede
Description: Pirates from around the world gather at the Pirates Expo to join the hunt for Gol D. Roger's lost treasure.

Title: The Chronicles of Riddick: Dark Fury
Description: Acting as a bridgepoint between "Pitch Black (2000)" and "The Chronicles of Riddick (2004)", this short film explains why Riddick decides to go into hiding and deliver Jack and Imam Abu al-Walid to New Mecca.

Title: Youngblood
Description: A gang war/drug story set in a Los Angeles ghetto about the coming of age of a 15-year-old black youth.

Title: Escaflowne: The Movie
Description: A grim retelling of the television series "The Vision of Escaflowne".

Title: The Brotherhood of Justice
Description: Keanu Reeves, Kiefer Sutherland, and Billy Zane star as high-school students who start a vigilante group to combat crime in their neighborhood.

Title: Burn Notice: The Fall of Sam Axe
Description: Follows Sam Axe on a mission in Latin America and gives us a glimpse into his military past.
A disaster film set during the 2018 Kerala Floods where people from all walks of life faced catastrophic consequences and put in collective efforts to survive the calamity.

Title: WWII: Operation Phoenix
Description: A small group of Allied commandos must parachute into enemy occupied Europe and recover the information a female spy was carrying, at all costs. They soon realize that this would be the easy part of the mission.

Title: Detective Knight: Redemption
Description: Detective James Knight is in the middle of an escape led by the Christmas Terrorist. Promising to return his badge in exchange for taking down the terrorists, he decides to give mercy to the righteous - and merciless justice to others.

Title: Cut Off
Description: Thriller set in the world of Forensic Pathology. Coroner Paul Herzfeld finds a capsule in the head of a heavily mutilated corpse, containing a phone number and single word: the name of his daughter.

Title: Dark Asset
Description: A charming guy attempts to pick up a woman in a bar by spinning a tale involving spies, implanted microchips and the dangerous military scientist hunting him.

Title: Witching and Bitching
Description: A gang of armed robbers finds a safe haven in a secluded village crammed with witches--only to encounter the bizarre, the unexpected, and the occult. Can they save themselves, and the rest of the world from the next witch apocalypse?

Title: Shakedown
Description: A legal aid attorney and renegade cop team up to stop a corrupt cop.

Title: Dragons Forever
Description: Three successful Hong Kong lawyers are hired by a chemical company of questionable ethics and must eventually make a difficult decision when their employer's motives become clear.

4 girls out on a 3-day trip to 2 cities--if they survive. While Jo is working in a supermarket, her three friends are all out on their adventures. A chance encounter with diamond thieves sends them on a collision course with fate itself.

Title: Zombie 3
Description: When a terrorist's body, infected with a stolen chemical, is cremated by the US military, a virus is unintentionally released into the atmosphere over a small island.

Title: Warlock: The Armageddon
Description: An order of Druids train their children to battle an evil Warlock determined to unleash Satan upon the world by bringing a collection of five mystic rune stones together.

Title: 2012: Doomsday
Description: Four strangers on a journey of faith are drawn to a temple in the heart of Mexico on December 21, 2012. For the Mayans it is the last recorded day. For NASA scientists it is a cataclysmic polar shift. For the rest of us, it is Doomsday.

Title: Mortal Kombat Legends: Cage Match
Description: In 1980s Hollywood, struggling martial arts actor Johnny Cage searches for his missing co-star amidst a Los Angeles filled with bloodthirsty fighters.

Title: Fullmetal Alchemist: The Revenge of Scar
Description: When a mysterious figure starts to target State Alchemists for their sins against God, Alchemist Edward Elric and his brother Alphonse are at their most vulnerable, meanwhile the homunculi begin to unveil themselves once again.

Title: The Bad Guys: Haunted Heist
Description: The Bad Guys' Halloween night of thievery and crime turns into a night of terror when they come across a dangerous enemy of the supernatural kind that gives them a taste of their own medicine.

Title: Varisu
Description: Vijay Rajendran is a happy to-go lucky man. Things change when his father becomes terminally ill, and he is left to manage his business empire.

Title: Khadaan
Description: Shyam comes from the remote areas of Purulia to work as a laborer in the coal mines of the Damodar Valley. The story of Mohan and Shyam will proceed with their rise, reckoning of friendship.

Title: The Marine 6: Close Quarters
Description: Jake Carter and another former Marine, Luke Trapper, join forces to rescue a kidnapped girl from a gang of international criminals.

Title: Avengers Confidential: Black Widow & Punisher
Description: Punisher and Black Widow are sent on a mission to stop Leviathan, a global terrorist organization that plans to sell stolen S.H.I.E.L.D. technology to the highest bidder.

Title: Shank
Description: An action film for the youth generation, set in a decaying future London. A gang set out on a chase to avenge the murder of one of their own.

Title: Batman & Mr. Freeze: SubZero
Description: When Mr. Freeze, desperate to save his dying wife, kidnaps Barbara Gordon (Batgirl) as an involuntary organ donor, Batman and Robin must find her before the operation can begin.

Title: Savage Sisters
Description: Three women of three races join the fundraising part of an island revolution.

Title: Kill Zone 2
Description: While undercover officer Kit is taken prisoner by the syndicate, he befriends his keeper and discovers an organ trafficking ring.

Title: Tokyo Revengers
Description: A middle-aged loser travels in time to his school years and, in order to save the love of his life from future doom, must become the leader of a dreaded school gang.

Title: A Prayer for the Dying
Description: I.R.A. hitman Martin is seen by a Catholic priest while carrying out a hit. He develops a bond with the priest and his niece, but his past and his former employers put all their lives in danger.

Title: The Last Mercenary
Description: A mysterious former secret service agent must urgently return to France when his estranged son is falsely accused of arms and drug trafficking by the government, following a blunder by an overzealous bureaucrat and a mafia operation.

Title: American Siege
Description: An ex-NYPD officer-turned-sheriff of a small rural Georgia town has to contend with a gang of thieves who have taken a wealthy doctor hostage.

Title: Demetrius and the Gladiators
Description: In first-century Rome, Christian slave Demetrius is sent to fight in the gladiatorial arena and Emperor Caligula seeks Jesus' robe for its alleged magical powers.

Title: Martial Law
Description: Two cops who are martial arts experts team up to stop a criminal organization headed by a ruthless boss who's also a martial artist.

Title: Darkland
Description: A successful doctor who loses his little brother in a gang-related assault gives up his privileged life to become a masked warrior and avenge his brother's death.

Title: Darr
Description: Rahul is obsessed with Kiran and stalks her constantly. However, Rahul goes berserk when she gets engaged to Sunil, a navy officer, and he decides to forcefully claim Kiran for himself.

Title: Primal Rage
Description: A newly reunited young couple's drive through the Pacific Northwest turns into a nightmare as they are forced to face nature, unsavory locals, and a monstrous creature, known to the Native Americans as Oh-Mah.

Title: The Adventures of Mark Twain
Description: Tom Sawyer, Becky Thatcher and Huck Finn join Mark Twain on his airship to meet Halley's Comet.

Title: Bad Kids of Crestview Academy
Description: 5 high school students get Saturday detention. One tries to find her sister's killer. When hit by a computer virus, the school goes on lockdown and the killing continues.

Title: End Game
Description: A secret Service agent and a news reporter investigate the conspiracy behind the assassination of the President.

Title: Pickup Alley
Description: International narcotics smuggler Frank McNally is trailed through various European countries by U.S. drug enforcement agent Charles Sturgis.

Title: The Rig
Description: In the midst of a tropical storm, the crew of an offshore oil rig must survive the rampage of a creature after invading its undersea habitat.

Title: Big Ass Spider!
Description: A giant alien spider escapes from a military lab and rampages the city of Los Angeles. When a massive military strike fails, it is up to a team of scientists and one clever exterminator to kill the creature before the city is destroyed.

Title: Saloum
Description: In 2003, a trio of mercenaries escaping a coup in Guinea-Bissau take refuge in a hidden region on the Saloum river of Senegal. But something from beyond the grave awaits them there.

Title: Mercenaries
Description: The President's daughter is captured and imprisoned while touring a war zone, so a team of elite female commandos is assembled to infiltrate a women's prison for a daring rescue.

Title: White Sands
Description: A small southwestern town Sheriff finds a body in the desert with a suitcase and five hundred thousand dollars. He impersonates the man and stumbles into an F.B.I. investigation.

Title: One Piece: Baron Omatsuri and the Secret Island
Description: The Straw Hat Pirates received an advertisement on a recreational island. The offers all looked promising, so they sailed to the island for an opportunity to kick back and relax from their journey across the Grand Line. The site of the resort looks like a dream come true. Only our heroes find themselves greeted by the head of the island: Baron Omatsuri. He asks all 7 of them to compete in a series of contests for their granted relaxation. Luffy accepts the challenge, and they all find this island to be not so average. There is however a mystery shrouded on the recreational paradise. Such as why are the Straw Hat Pirates the only tourists around? And why is Baron hold the only flower of the island?

Title: Winx Club: The Secret of the Lost Kingdom
Description: At Alfea College, Stella, Aisha, Flora, Musa, and Tecna all graduate and become fairy guardians of their home planets. But, Bloom must watch graduation from the sidelines. The Winx try to save Bloom's parents and the planet.

Title: Scott of the Antarctic
Description: The story of British explorer Robert Falcon Scott's 1912 expedition and his quest to be the first to reach the South Pole.

Title: Good People
Description: Discovering a stash of cash in their dead tenant's apartment, a couple in debt take the money and find themselves the target of a deadly adversary - the thief who stole it.

Title: Safety Last!
Description: A boy leaves his small country town and heads to the big city to get a job. As soon as he makes it big his sweetheart will join him and marry him. His enthusiasm to get ahead leads to some interesting adventures.

Title: Bionic
Description: When the progress of robotics makes Paralympic athletes the new sports stars, Maria dreams of competing against her sister. For that, she will have to enter a world of crime and violence.

Title: In the Hell of Kabul: 13 Days, 13 Nights
Description: Afghan troops guard French embassy during Taliban takeover of Kabul. Tasked with evacuating 500 people to airport amid chaos, facing grave risks as they attempt desperate escape from falling city.

Title: Eye of the Tiger
Description: Returning home from prison, a Vietnam War veteran sets out to clean up his hometown which has come under the control of a violent motorcycle gang.

Title: Crying Freeman
Description: A woman sees an assassin outside San Francisco killing yakuza men and later in Vancouver. She's been told that he leaves no witness. Will she be his next victim or...?

Title: Dayi: Bir Adamin Hikayesi 2
Description: After losing his family in what he discovers was no accident, underworld legend Cevahir, feared by drug cartels, pursues revenge but becomes entangled in a larger conspiracy.

Title: Vanquish
Description: A mother, Victoria, is trying to put her dark past as a Russian drug courier behind her, but retired cop Damon forces Victoria to do his bidding by holding her daughter hostage.

Title: Kidnapping Mr. Heineken
Description: The inside story of the planning, execution, rousing aftermath, and ultimate downfall of the kidnappers of beer tycoon Alfred "Freddy" Heineken in 1983, which resulted in the largest ransom ever paid for an individual.

Title: Battle for Incheon: Operation Chromite
Description: A team of spies is sent into Incheon to gain intelligence on North Korean positions ahead of the invasion by UN forces.

Title: Monster Hunter: Legends of the Guild
Description: In a world where humans and fearsome monsters live in an uneasy balance, young hunter Aiden fights to save his village from destruction by a dragon.

Title: Killers
Description: A psychopathic Japanese executive accidentally triggers a journalist's 'dark side'. They begin to connect over the Internet and make a complicated bond.

Title: Death Stranding
Description: Plot is being kept under wraps. Based on the 2019 hit video game by Hideo Kojima.

Title: The Takeover
Description: Framed for murder after uncovering a privacy scandal, an ethical hacker must evade the police while trying to track down the criminals blackmailing her.

Title: Sundown
Description: High school seniors Logan and Blake prepare for an epic Spring Break as they travel to the beautiful and exotic Mexican beach resort of Puerto Vallarta hoping to hook up with their high school crushes.

Title: G.I. Joe: The Movie
Description: The heroic G.I. Joe action force must oppose the ruthless Cobra organization that has secretly allied with a subterranean reptilian people who were their founders.

Title: Day of Anger
Description: A scruffy garbage boy becomes the pupil of a famed gunfighter, and the stage for confrontation is set when the gunman overruns the boy's town through violence and corruption.

Title: Sheroes
Description: When four thick-as-thieves friends arrive in Thailand they quickly find themselves in over their heads. Fighting to stay alive, they employ their unique set of skills and unleash their fierce loyalty in a heart-pumping battle for survival.

Title: The Bouncer
Description: In Romania, fugitive Frank Sharp takes a job as a bouncer. Saving a woman from abuse, he discovers she's trafficked. They escape together but are relentlessly hunted.

Title: Stone
Description: After one of its members witnesses a political assassination, a motorbike gang becomes the target of a string of murders, prompting a cop to join their ranks to determine who is responsible.

Title: All the Devil's Men
Description: A battle-scarred War on Terror bounty hunter is forced to go to London on a manhunt for a disavowed CIA operative, which leads him into a deadly running battle with a former military comrade and his private army.

Title: Snow Ponies
Description: A tough group of men ward off ruthless bandits and brutal obstacles as they travel across a treacherous landscape to deliver a mysterious package.

Title: Jung_E
Description: On an uninhabitable 22nd-century Earth, the outcome of a civil war hinges on cloning the brain of an elite soldier to create a robot mercenary.

Title: New York Ninja
Description: Originally shot in 1984 and not finished until 2021, New York Ninja is about a sound technician for a news station (John Liu) who becomes a vigilante ninja in New York City after his pregnant wife is murdered.

Title: Shimmer Lake
Description: An inventive crime thriller told backwards reversing day by day through a week following a local sheriff's quest to unlock the mystery of three small-town criminals and a bank heist gone wrong.

Title: The Nutcracker: The Untold Story
Description: In 1920s Vienna, a young girl receives a magical doll on Christmas Eve.

Title: The Traveler
Description: A slow, quiet Christmas Eve night at the police station turns into strange horror after a man enters claiming he wants to confess to murder.

Title: El nino
Description: A small-time trafficker working in the Gibraltar Straits.

Title: Sniper: Legacy
Description: A rogue assassin is taking out military leaders, and Brandon gets word that his father is one. He tries to track down the killer, finds out that his father isn't dead and realizes that his superior officers are using him as bait to track the killer.

Title: The Young Master
Description: A talented martial arts student goes after his expelled brother, who get into bad company.

Title: Walking with the Enemy
Description: A young man, separated from his family in World War II, disguises himself as a Nazi S.S. Officer and uncovers more than just his family whereabouts.

Title: Enemy Lines
Description: In the frozen, war torn landscape of occupied Poland during World War II, a team of Allied commandos is sent on a deadly mission behind enemy lines to extract a rocket scientist from the hands of the Germans.

Title: Lone Wolf and Cub: Sword of Vengeance
Description: The story of a Ronin (i.e. a masterless samurai) who wanders the countryside of Japan with his small child, having various adventures.

Title: The Main Event
Description: After discovering a magical mask, an 11-year-old aspiring wrestler enters a competition to become the next WWE superstar.

Title: Vanishing Point
Description: An ex race car driver hurries 1200 miles home in a 1970 Challenger when his wife has labor problems. Cops in several states try to stop him - initially for speeding.

Title: Kingdom
Description: In ancient China, a young boy dreams of becoming the greatest general of the Qin Kingdom.

Title: Marighella
Description: Facing a violent military dictatorship and an intimidated opposition, writer-turned-politician Carlos Marighella articulates a resistance all the while ousting heinous crimes of torture and the infamous censorship instituted by the regime.

Title: Battle Queen 2020
Description: After a civilization is all but wiped out by a comet, evil forces take advantage of the weak. A powerful woman fights back for the sake of the vulnerable.

Title: The Foreigner
Description: A freelance agent must transport a package for a mysterious employer, leading him into a web of betrayal and deceit.

Title: 38 especial
Description: A Religious fanatic is killing innocent women. A Detective and radio personality psychologist team together to bring him to justice.

Title: Highwaymen
Description: Rennie Cray (Caviezel) embarks on a bloodthirsty rampage to avenge the death of his wife who was struck down by a serial killer - a man who hunts and kills women using his '72 El Dorado.

Title: Restless
Description: After going to extremes to cover up an accident, a corrupt cop's life spirals out of control when he starts receiving threats from a mysterious witness.

Title: Truth or Consequences, N.M.
Description: A group of crooks, an ex con, his friend and a gun crazy gangster plan a drug heist, but not everything goes as planned.

Title: Strategic Air Command
Description: An ex-pilot and current baseballer is recalled into the U.S. Air Force and assumes an increasingly important role in Cold War deterrence.

Title: Mother Mafia
Description: A family run by their mafia mother will show her dark desires.

Title: Assassination
Description: While Korea is occupied by the Japanese Army in 1933, the resistance plans to kill the Japanese Commander. But their plan is threatened by a traitor within their group and also the enemies' forces are hunting them down.

Title: Atlantic Rim
Description: When giant monsters crawl out of the Atlantic Ocean and attack the Eastern Seaboard the US Government is forced to trust a trio of mischievous soldiers, specialized in piloting gigantic robots, to defend America.

Title: Bullet in the Head
Description: When three close friends escape from Hong Kong to war-time Saigon to start a criminal's life, they all go through a harrowing experience which totally shatters their lives and their friendship forever.

Title: The Nude Bomb
Description: Maxwell Smart is recalled to duty to help fight a villian who threatens to detonate a weapon that destroys clothing.

Title: Beau Geste
Description: Three adopted English brothers join the French Foreign Legion in North Africa after one of them steals their adoptive family's famous heirloom sapphire.

Title: Echelon Conspiracy
Description: At first, the strange phone messages promised great wealth. Soon, though, government agents pursue the young engineer receiving them around the world.

Title: Game of Death II
Description: After Billy Lo is killed while seeking the murderers of his friend, his brother Bobby goes all out to bring the perpetrators to justice.

Title: Hoagie
Description: A mysterious egg contains an impish creature who can grant great power. Brendan Bean finds himself face to face with the bizarre creature, and before long a friendship for the ages develops.

Title: First Love
Description: A young boxer and a call girl get caught up in a drug-smuggling scheme over the course of one night in Tokyo.

Title: Ed, Edd n Eddy's Big Picture Show
Description: When a scam goes horribly wrong and leaves the neighborhood kids furious, the Eds embark on a journey to find Eddy's brother to save them from their consequences in the "Ed, Edd, n Eddy" series finale.

Title: Dynamic Duo
Description: It explores the early friendship between Dick Grayson and Jason Todd, the Robins, as they navigate their dreams and differing visions for the future, leading to the emergence of a new Dynamic Duo amidst challenges to their bond.

Title: Speedy
Description: Harold "Speedy" Swift, a fan of Babe Ruth and the New York Yankees, saves from extinction the city's last horse-drawn trolley, operated by his girlfriend's grandfather.

Title: The Resistance Fighter
Description: Film about the lead up to the Polish uprising against German occupation at the end of the Second World War.

Title: Flashpoint
Description: Two U.S. border patrolmen find a buried 20+ year old jeep in the desert with a skeleton, rifle and $800,000. They keep the money. Suddenly, the FBI shows a lot of interest in the car.

Title: Texas Rangers
Description: A ragtag group of youngsters band together after the American Civil War to form the Texas Rangers, a group charged with the dangerous, ruthless duty of cleaning up the West.

Title: Bucktown
Description: After being hassled by The Man in a southern town, a cool operator asks some violent friends for help. After all, if you can't trust another brother, who can you trust?

Title: Taxi 2
Description: Police inspector Emilien and his taxi-driver pal Daniel are back, this time on the tail of a group of Japanese yakuza.

Title: Flight Crew
Description: Aircraft crew members must put off their differences when a natural disaster threatens to death hundreds of tourists.

Title: Kung Fu Deadly
Description: Danny and Frank, two bumbling pest exterminators, cross paths with the enigmatic Lien, a Taoist guardian hunting an ancient Chinese jiangshi in Dublin. Together they set out deal with this menace the only way they know how: extermination.

Title: Braddock: Missing in Action III
Description: Braddock mounts a one-man assault to free his wife and son who are still being held in a Vietnam prison camp.

Title: Sniper 2
Description: Sgt. Beckett's last mission sends him to a remote war-torn wasteland between Eastern Europe and Asia to assassinate a repressive terrorist leader. Once the job is done, Beckett and his spotter find escaping more difficult than anticipated.

Title: Brave Citizen
Description: Follows a former female boxing champion that now works as a substitute high school teacher and how after witnessing intolerable violence, she decides to take justice on her own fists.

Title: Bhoomi
Description: A single father battles injustice after his daughter is raped and the perpetrators are found not guilty.

Title: Savage Dawn
Description: A vicious biker gang is intent on destroying a small town in Arizona. A war veteran visiting an old friend and a few locals with nothing to lose go to war with the gang's ruthless leader.

Title: Ground Zero
Description: L.A. is struck by a series of minor earthquakes. The experts don't know what's happening since their advanced systems didn't detect any seismic activities. Kimberly Stevenson is sent to investigate the epicenter in a remote mountainous forest, and she is surprised to discover she's not alone. Somebody knows the real secret about the "earthquakes".

Title: Rapture
Description: When an apocalyptic event strikes, a group of people caught on the outside of civilization must take a perilous journey to find refuge.

Title: Jarhead 2: Field of Fire
Description: Without tanks or air support, a corporal and his team must muster all the courage and firepower they can to fight their way across war-torn Afghanistan and shepherd an important anti-Taliban woman to safety.

Title: The Monkey King: Havoc in Heaven's Palace
Description: A monkey born from heavenly stone acquires supernatural powers and must battle the armies of both gods and demons to find his place in the heavens.

Title: Fright Night 2
Description: "Fright Night 2" - In Romania, Charley and his friends discover that their alluring art professor is a real-life vampire, hell-bent on completing an ancient ritual with Amy's blood.

Title: 2012: Ice Age
Description: A volcanic eruption in Iceland sends a glacier towards North America, causing everything in it's path to freeze. A family man struggles to escape the onslaught of the coming ice age.

Title: Welcome to the Jungle
Description: A company retreat on a tropical island goes terribly awry.

Title: Mobile Suit Gundam: Char's Counterattack
Description: Amuro Ray and Char Aznable settle their rivalry once and for all during the Second Neo Zeon War.

Title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The Movie
Description: Underneath the sands of Egypt, Anubis, an ancient evil spirit, has awakened. It's up to Yugi, who defeated Anubis centuries ago, to use his skill and determination to rid the world of evil once again.

Title: Darkman II: The Return of Durant
Description: Darkman and Durant return and they hate each other as much as ever. This time, Durant has plans to take over the city's drug trade using high-tech weaponry. Darkman must step in and try to stop Durant once and for all.

Title: Jigarthanda Double X
Description: In 1975, a filmmaker agrees to collaborate on a film with a gangster who wishes to become a famous actor.

Title: Paparazzi
Description: A rising Hollywood actor decides to take personal revenge against a group of four persistent photographers to make them pay for almost causing a personal tragedy involving his wife and son.

Title: Martin
Description: A journey of a man discovering himself, finding love and fighting for his motherland. Can he hold the fort on all three gates?

Title: Extortion
Description: When a Caribbean family vacation takes a disastrous turn, a father finds himself at the mercy of a cold-blooded fisherman, and a desperate race against the clock to save his wife and son.

Title: Asoka
Description: The epic tale of King Asoka's life is recounted.

Title: Sukiyaki Western Django
Description: A nameless gunfighter arrives in a town ripped apart by rival gangs and, though courted by both to join, chooses his own path.

Title: Semper Fi
Description: A police officer who serves in the Marine Corps Reserves is faced with an ethical dilemma when it comes to helping his brother in prison.

Title: To End All Wars
Description: During World War II, four Allied POWs endure harsh treatment from their Japanese captors while being forced to build a railroad through the Burmese jungle.

Title: Godzilla vs. Mechagodzilla
Description: An Okinawan prophecy appears to foretell Earth's destruction at the hands of Godzilla, only for the true Godzilla to reveal his doppelganger as a mechanical alien weapon.

Title: Crack in the World
Description: A dying scientist pushes forward his project to tap through to the Earth's magma layer, with results that threaten to destroy the Earth as we know it.

Title: The Big Bang
Description: A private detective is hired to find a missing stripper. A simple job turns complicated when everyone he questions ends up dead.

Title: Loot 2
Description: The 4 gang members, who were framed in the bank robbery, now escape from the prison. While they look for revenge with Haku Kale, Haku has his own plan of robbing next bank.

Title: Ivy + Bean
Description: Two unlikely friends, the loud and fearless Bean, and the thoughtful and quiet Ivy. Yet the two discover that an adventure can reveal that even seemingly different people can become the best of friends.

Title: Kuang Bao Ju Xi
Description: A young man climbs into the mountains to pick up a meteorite that has fallen there and is killed by something. The "thing" descends to the village and begins to eat the inhabitants one by one, terrorizing the entire island.

Title: Aces High
Description: In World War I, the high casualty rate amongst the rookie pilots of the Royal Flying Corps puts an enormous strain on the survivors.

Title: Viking Quest
Description: A young peasant boy is taken from his home by Viking raiders and raised as one of them. But when a legendary dragon attacks his clan, he discovers that he is the Viking hero destined to stop the dragons from destroying the world.

Title: Hera Pheri
Description: Two tenants and a landlord look for answers to all their money problems - but when their opportunity arrives, will they know what to do with it?

Title: Sector 17
Description: Pargat, son of Gurdit Singh, seeks justice against Tundilaat, who killed his father and stole their land. With the help of Rani and her aunt Balviro, Pargat dismantles Tundilaat's empire, ultimately restoring his family's honor.

Title: The Red Baron
Description: German biopic loosely based on the World War I fighter ace Manfred Von Richthofen, nicknamed the Red Baron by friend and foe alike.

Title: Legion of Super-Heroes
Description: Kara, devastated by the loss of Krypton, struggles to adjust to her new life on Earth. Superman mentors her. Meanwhile, she must contend with a mysterious group called the Dark Circle who searches for a powerful weapon held in the Academy's vault.

Title: Yolo
Description: After an argument with her younger sister, Le Ying moves out on her own. She meets a boxing trainer and starts boxing.

Title: Bade Miyan Chote Miyan
Description: Two elite soldiers with troubled pasts are enlisted for a daring mission when a deadly masked villain threatens India's defenses.

Title: OSS 117: From Africa with Love
Description: The third entry in secret agent OSS 117's parodic spy adventures.

Title: A Hard Place
Description: A group of criminals on the run find themselves caught in the middle of an ancient feud between the monsters that roam the day and the creatures that rule the night.

Title: Strapped
Description: Ex-con attempting to go straight runs accross serious problems. His girlfriend gets arrested for dealing crack to an undercover police officer. In a desperate attempt to get the charges dropped against his woman, he strikes deal with weapons cop(Michael Biehn) to turn in local gun dealers. How ever, the D.A. is not satisfied with the results, resulting in some serious game playing and double crossing.

Title: The Bluff
Description: A Caribbean woman gets her secret past revealed when her island is invaded by vicious buccaneers.

Title: Baby Assassins: Nice Days
Description: Teenage assassins Chisato and Mahiro visit the coastal city of Miyazaki when they unexpectedly cross paths with a bloodthirsty assassin who's looking to add to his personal body count.

Title: Drive
Description: A prototype enhanced human, on the run from Chinese-hired hit men, hooks up with a dread-locked bystander, and the two of them elude their pursuers narrowly each time.

Title: The Twisters
Description: Dozens of deadly tornadoes converge in the Midwest, merging into a mega twister set to obliterate everything for hundreds of miles.

Title: Batman: The Long Halloween, Part Two
Description: The killer known as Holiday continues to stalk the Falcone crime family while a new class of costumed criminal rises in Gotham City. Batman suspects that a former ally might be the serial killer.

Title: Why Don't You Play in Hell?
Description: A renegade film crew becomes embroiled with a yakuza clan feud.

Title: Night of the Sicario
Description: Taylor is forced to hide the young daughter of a Colombian woman in witness protection who will be testifying against a powerful drug cartel in Federal Court, as ruthless sicarios aim to hunt them down.

Title: Do or Die
Description: Hunted down by six teams of assassins hired by a Japanese crime lord, Federal agents Donna and Nicole struggle to survive, with help from their agency friends.

Title: Pokémon: Lucario and the Mystery of Mew
Description: When Pikachu is taken to the Tree of Beginnings by the playful Mew, Ash Ketchum and friends are guided to the tree by Lucario, a time-displaced Pokémon who seeks answers regarding the betrayal of his master.

Title: Bunny the Killer Thing
Description: A group of Finnish and British people get stuck at a cabin when they are attacked by a creature that is a half human, half rabbit.

Title: Descendants: The Royal Wedding
Description: Happily-ever-after continues for Auradon's power couple, Mal and Ben, as they prepare to say "I do" at an epic celebration with their friends and family, but Hades threatens to ruin it all.

Title: Eve of Destruction
Description: A terrorist hunter is hired by a scientist to deactivate her android double, a walking, talking, murderous nuclear bomb which has gone amok in the big city and is about to explode.

Title: Hercules in the Underworld
Description: A woman asks Hercules for his help because a hole leading to the underworld has opened up in her village. Hercules wants to help her, despite knowing that she comes from a group of women notorious for leading men to their doom.

Title: Devil Fish
Description: A marine biologist, a dolphin trainer, a research scientist, and a local sheriff try to hunt down a large sea monster, a shark/octopus hybrid, that is devouring swimmers and fishermen off a south Florida coast.

Title: Godzilla Raids Again
Description: Scout pilots for a fishing company are startled to discover a second Godzilla, whose battle with rival monster Anguirus threatens to destroy Osaka.

Title: Kim Possible: So the Drama
Description: Kim's heart is quickly captured by the new boy, Eric, who soon becomes her boyfriend. Unknown to Kim, her best friend and sidekick, Ron has developed stronger feelings toward her.

Title: Naruto Shippuden the Movie: Blood Prison
Description: Naruto Uzumaki is framed and sent to an inescapable prison where he must escape by any means necessary.

Title: Tekken: Kazuya's Revenge
Description: Suffering from amnesia, a young man trying to discover his true identity is kidnapped by an underground crime organization and turned into a ruthless assassin.

Title: Hattichhap
Description: "Hattichhap" is a Nepali movie directed by Simosh Sunuwar, featuring Dayahang Rai, Saugat Malla, Upasana Singh Thakuri, and Benisha Hamal

Title: Above the Below
Description: A trio of astronauts survive a destructive re-entry to Earth and find that they are cut off from the world.

Title: The Pastor
Description: In a forgotten part of town overrun by a ruthless gang, a community struggles with its faith as they see their neighborhoods torn apart and their youth targeted for gang recruitment. But all that is about to change..

Title: Mr. and Mrs. Smith
Description: Newly relocated to the suburbs, married assassins John and Jane Smith have re-established their respective businesses, though the marital issues that plagued them in the past have returned.

Title: Picasso Trigger
Description: After his brother got eliminated in Hard Ticket to Hawaii (1987), a crime lord triggers a ruthless hunt against all agents responsible, and the remaining agents will have to avenge their fallen comrades.

Title: Wedlock
Description: A male prison escapee heads for his hidden loot electronically attached to a female prisoner.

Title: High Heels and Low Lifes
Description: A nurse eavesdrops with a friend on a cell phone conversation that describes a bank heist. She and the friend then conspire to blackmail the robbers for two million dollars.

Title: Dylan Dog: Dead of Night
Description: The adventures of supernatural private investigator, Dylan Dog, who seeks out the monsters of the Louisiana bayou in his signature red shirt, black jacket, and blue jeans.

Title: Hunting with Tigers
Description: Malik returns from Spain to learn his stepfather Serge was arrested. On trial day lawyer Iris offers Malik a deal, pull off a dangerous heist in exchange for Serge's freedom. Malik agrees and joins ex-partners of Cherif for one last job.

Title: Gadar 2
Description: When Tara Singh goes missing during a skirmish and is believed to be captured in Pakistan, his son Jeetey sets out to rescue him and enters a labyrinth from which they both must escape at all costs.

Title: The Bouncer
Description: A nightclub bouncer in his fifties who's taken punches, literally and figuratively, struggles to raise his 8-year-old daughter.

Title: Tangled: Before Ever After
Description: As Rapunzel prepares for her coronation as Princess of Corona, one unforgettable night will change her hair again!

Title: Kung Fu Slayers
Description: A good-natured vampire must use his powers to defeat an old nemesis, who has kidnapped his son, in Montana.

Title: Cold Comes the Night
Description: A struggling motel owner and her daughter are taken hostage by a nearly blind career criminal to be his eyes as he attempts to retrieve his cash package from a crooked cop.

Title: Skinford: Death Sentence
Description: British con artist, Jimmy 'Skinny' Skinford, uncovers the opportunity of a lifetime--whilst digging his own grave.

Title: Blood Brothers: Bara Naga
Description: A group of close-knit men working in an 'elite security' organization providing protection for powerful men and organized crime leaders is tested when betrayal lurks within the brotherhood.

Title: Escape from Mogadishu
Description: In war-torn Somalia in 1991, the personnel and families of both the South Korean and North Korean embassies share the same goal: to escape from Mogadishu.

Title: Going Places
Description: After covering up a hit and run, three high school graduates face the true test of their friendship when they become entangled in a deadly crime.

Title: Devil's Knight
Description: In the realm of Veroka, an elite group of global monster hunters is summoned by King Samuel to vanquish the ancient Bone Devil, whose reign of terror threatens the Kingdom of Remény.

Title: Superman: Red Son
Description: What if baby Kal-El's rocket landed not in Kansas, but in the Soviet Union? That is the premise of this Elseworld's tale from DC Comics.

Title: Mr. Vampire
Description: The planned reburial of a town elder goes awry as the corpse resurrects into a hopping, bloodthirsty vampire, targeting everyone responsible for digging the grave. A Taoist Priest and his two disciples attempt to stop the terror.

Title: Pathfinder
Description: A young Sámi man witnesses a band of vicious raiders slay his family and flees to a nearby village, where he learns he must become a Pathfinder.

Title: Warriors of the Wasteland
Description: Two mercenaries help wandering caravans fight off an evil and aimless band of white-clad bikers after the nuclear holocaust.

Title: Shadowboxer
Description: When an assassin is diagnosed with terminal cancer, she decides to carry out one final killing, assisted by her lover and stepson, Mikey.

Title: Powerpuff Girls the Revenge of Mojo Jojo
Description: Mojo Jojo, (Jeremiah Tube Gamer) has escaped prison, and now plans to destroy Townsville once again. It's up to Blossom, (Hannah Floto) Bubbles, (Nikki Jay) and Buttercup (TurtleDubVA) to stop Mojo Jojo to finishing his masterplan.

Title: Hotel Tehran
Description: Disillusioned by the end of the war in Afghanistan, a group of disgraced, war torn ex-CIA operators set out to Tehran to take down a life changing score.

Title: Seal Team
Description: Fearless seal Quinn assembles a squad of misfit recruits to stand up to ruthless sharks with razor-sharp teeth and reclaim the open sea.

Title: The Pirates
Description: A band of pirates and a group of bandits fight to catch a gray whale that has swallowed a royal stamp.

Title: Sahara
Description: A tank commander and his men along with a group of assorted stragglers they picked up along the way try to keep a limited supply of water away from the Nazis.

Title: Zombie Plane
Description: Around the world celebrities are seen by day as the faces we know and love, but by night they are saving the world from under-wraps attacks. Led by Commander Chuck Norris, they stand between world peace and humanities' destruction.

Title: The Heroic Trio
Description: While one tough woman with an invisible robe has stolen 18 babies for her powerful master, two other tough women and the cops try to stop her.

Title: Batman: The Long Halloween

Title: Infestation

Title: Eliminators

Title: The Fortress

Title: Hard Target 2

Title: Maude v Maude

Title: Arisaka
Description: Follows a policewoman who has to retrace the route of the Bataan Death March to escape her captors.

Title: The Suspect

Title: Original Gangstas
Description: When a gang shoots his father, Bookman (Fred Williamson) returns to his hometown, rounds up some of his own people and begins an all-out war to restore the neighborhood to its rightful sense of justice.

Title: Godzilla 1985

Title: Rob N Roll
Description: Decadent Murong Hui teams up with violent bandits after a botched robbery. A female detective pursues them as they scheme to steal a bag of money, leading to chaotic events due to betrayals and twists under the "I rob, you rob me" code.

Title: Freelancers
Description: The son of a slain NYPD officer joins the force, where he falls in with his father's former partner and a team of rogue cops.

Title: Green Snake

Title: War 2

Title: Pahat pojat

Title: Reptilicus

Title: Killers Anonymous

Title: Chino

Title: World-Breaker

Title: Hell Dogs

Title: Cleanskin

Title: Maximum Conviction

Torn from the crime lords who were her only family, Shion must choose between a life of killing and a life on the run.

Title: Violent City

Title: G.I. Joe: Ever Vigilant

Title: Bloody Daddy

Title: The Moon

Title: Star Wars: Rogue Squadron

Title: Firecracker

Title: Phantom of the Megaplex

Title: Abelar: Tales of an Ancient Empire

Title: Bloodsport 2

Title: The Gateway

Title: Marvel One-Shot: Item 47

Title: Fullmetal Alchemist the Movie: Conqueror of Shamballa

Title: Hell Behind the Bars

He returns from living a jet-set life in Europe to lead a revolution against the government, only to find out that things aren't quite as black and white as he had assumed.

Title: Desert Dawn

Title: The Magnificent Seven Ride!

Title: Godzilla vs. Megalon
Description: An inventor creates a robot that is seized by an undersea kingdom to guide their monster god in attacking the surface as retaliation for the nuclear tests that have devastated their society.

Title: Toofan
Description: Follows a born killer who rises to power and becomes the biggest toofan

Title: Black Creek
Description: A sheriff's sister seeks revenge against the terrifying leader of a group of outlaws after discovering he brutally murdered her brother, his wife, and other family members in a gritty southwestern town.

Title: The Last Survivors
Description: A teenage girl fights to protect the last working well in a drought-stricken valley from a greedy water baron.

Title: Ben 10: Destroy All Aliens

Title: Delta Farce

Title: Reign of the Supermen
Description: After the death of Superman, several new people present themselves as possible successors.

Title: Blackbird

Title: Stiletto

Title: Circle of Iron
Description: A young martial artist embarks on an adventure, encountering other martial artists in battle until one day he meets an aging blind man who will show him the true meaning of martial arts and life.

Title: OSS 117: Lost in Rio

Title: Buzz Lightyear of Star Command: The Adventure Begins

Title: Flu

Title: Kisi Ka Bhai Kisi Ki Jaan
Description: The eldest brother refuses to marry since he believes it may create disharmony in his big family. His brothers, who've already found partners, come together to find a match for him.

Title: Delhi Belly

Title: Massacre in Dinosaur Valley
Description: A small plane carrying fossil hunters crashes in the Amazon jungle, and the survivors must battle their way through cannibals, wild animals, and slave traders.

Title: Sgt. Kabukiman N.Y.P.D.

Title: Once Upon a Texas Train

Title: Stratton

Title: Arsenal
Description: A Southern businessman attempts to rescue his kidnapped mobster brother.

Title: A Bullet for the General

Title: Les Vampires

Title: Fire on the Amazon

Title: Fatal Beauty

Title: Infernal Affairs II

Title: Kill Switch

Title: Citizen of a Kind

Title: Mojave

Title: Lassiter

Title: Diamonds of Kilimandjaro

Title: UFO Sweden
Description: A rebellious teen placed in foster care suspects her father is not dead but has been abducted. She is determined to find out the truth with help from a UFO association.

Title: Double Threat
Description: Pretty girl with great assets skims money from the mob. The crime boss' son takes it personally and seeks to settle the score. Meanwhile a man on a quest to scatter his brother's ashes becomes entangled in this tawdry affair.

Title: Godzilla vs. Megaguirus
Description: Japan creates an artificial black hole device to trap Godzilla forever, but a test of the device creates new foes for Godzilla, car-sized dragonflies called meganula and their queen, Megaguirus.

Title: Legacy of Lies
Description: An ex-MI6 agent is thrown back into the world of espionage and high stakes to uncover the shocking truth about operations conducted by unknown secret services.

Title: Dragon Fist
Description: Tong Huo-wan seeks redress from the man responsible for his master's death, but becomes entangled in a feud between a local clan and gangsters.

Title: Honor and Glory
Description: FBI agent Tracy Pride is on a mission to capture businessman Jason Slade, who is involved in extortion and murder. Teaming up with her is her sister Joyce, a news reporter; Dragon, Tracy's partner in Hong Kong, and Jake, a bodyguard who worked for Slade. Can they stop Slade before it's too late?

Title: 100 Million BC
Description: A scientist leads a team of Navy SEALs back in time to the Cretaceous Period to rescue the first team he sent back during the 1940s. Things go wildly when he accidentally brings a giant dinosaur back into Los Angeles.

Title: Mackenna's Gold
Description: A bandit kidnaps a Marshal who has seen a map showing a gold vein on Indian lands, but other groups are looking for it too, while the Apache try to keep the secret location undisturbed.

Title: Revenger
Description: A former police investigator decides to go to a prison island to revenge the brutal killings of his family.

Title: Heat Vision and Jack
Description: Astronaut on the run with special powers and his talking motorcycle must deal with a malevolent artificial life form that's possessing people and turning them into dust, as well as NASA's hitman and real life actor Ron Silver.

Title: Lake Placid: The Final Chapter
Description: Black Lake is now a crocodile sanctuary, surrounded by an electric fence. When the fence is left open, a high-school bus unknowingly enters the park. It's up to Reba and the Sheriff to save the kids from becoming crocodile food.

Title: Guns Up
Description: When a job goes horribly wrong, an ex-cop and family man who moonlights as a mob henchman has one night to get his family out of the city.

Title: The Breath
Description: Story of 40-man Turkish task force who must defend a relay station.

Title: Micmacs
Description: A man and his friends come up with an intricate and original plan to destroy two big weapons manufacturers.

Title: Born to Race
Description: Danny's sent to stay with his estranged dad after yet another illegal street race and arrest. He befriends Jessica at school and has problems with her speed crazy bully ex. There's a drag race with a racing school scholarship as prize.

Title: Fate/stay night [Heaven's Feel] I. presage flower
Description: Movie adaptation of the third route of Fate/Stay Night.

Title: Brat 2
Description: Arriving in Moscow, Danila discovers Konstantin dead and he sets out to avenge his death; a journey that leads him to Chicago and a whole new experience.

Title: Adventures of Don Juan
Description: The great lover Don Juan comes to the assistance of his queen.

Title: Mythica: Stormbound
Description: Years after Szorlok's devastation and the Red Thorns' victory, a new evil will threaten the world and new heroes will rise to fight it.

Title: The Legend of Awesomest Maximus
Description: A clueless Trojan general must meet an unbeatable Greek warrior on the battlefield.

Title: Mikaela
Description: Epiphany Eve. An unprecedented snowstorm ravages Spain. Amidst the chaos of a collapsed highway, a group of robbers takes the opportunity to assault an armored van.

Title: Dragon's Lair: The Movie
Description: Dirk the Daring, a knight who sets out to rescue Princess Daphne from the evil dragon Singe and a wizard named Mordroc.

Title: Fear Is the Key
Description: A man is in radio contact with his family when their airplane is shot down. He wants to find and punish those responsible and becomes a criminal to get a job as a deep-sea diver with those salvaging the plane's cargo.

Title: My Nights with Susan, Olga, Albert, Julie, Piet & Sandra
Description: Anton arrives at Susan's farmhouse in rural Holland to take her away with him. The house and surrounding area is populated by strange characters who duplicitously lust for each other. An opening murder weighs over everything.

Title: Happy New Year
Description: A gang of amateur dancers takes part in a dancing competition to avenge their personal vendetta.

Title: Takht
Description: Vicky Kaushal plays Aurangzeb and Ranveer plays Dara, Aurangzeb's elder brother. It's the story about the enmity between brothers caused for the succession of the Throne.

Title: The House Next Door: Meet the Blacks 2
Description: When best selling author Carl Black moves his family back to his childhood home, he must team up with oddball neighbors to do battle with a pimp, who may or may not be an actual vampire.

Title: Tom Sawyer & Huckleberry Finn
Description: Tom Sawyer and his pal Huckleberry Finn have great adventures on the Mississippi River, pretending to be pirates, attending their own funeral and witnessing a murder.

Title: Opportunity Knocks
Description: Two con men hide out in a house while the owner is away; one of them assumes the identity of the absent house sitter when the owner's relatives come to visit, only for further complications to set in.

Title: Shadow on the Land
Description: Patriotic freedom fighters struggle against a fascist dictatorship in a near-future USA.

Title: Twinkle Twinkle Lucky Stars
Description: 5 HK cops (4 horny males) on vacation in Pattaya, Thailand, are told to contact an informant there but he gets murdered. They return to Hong Kong to contact his girlfriend and protect her. 3 other colleagues are busy fighting criminals.

Title: Ator: The Fighting Eagle
Description: The son of Torren learns of his heritage, goes to avenge the deaths of his fellow villagers, and rescue his sister from the evil Dakkar and his spider cult.

Title: Royal Warriors
Description: Michelle Yip of the Hong Kong police is a mild-mannered Kung Fu expert; Michael Wong, from air security, is happy-go-lucky, stuck on himself, constantly talking, and smitten by her; Yamamoto is quiet, hard-boiled, leaving the Tokyo police to spend time with his wife and daughter. They form an alliance when they foil a hijacking on a plane flying a mob prisoner from Tokyo to Hong Kong. The mobster and his would-be rescuer die, and this sets off two avengers who were their blood brothers. Our three cops become the targets. A high-speed chase, a car bomb, the destruction of a nightclub, a spectacular suicide, dead bystanders, and a flying coffin litter the landscape by the end.

Title: Forty Guns
Description: Showdown in Arizona between the Bonnell brothers, U.S.Marshals, and Jessica Drummond, the iron-fist rancher who controls the territory.

Title: Herbie Goes to Monte Carlo
Description: Herbie, the Volkswagen Beetle with a mind of its own, is racing in the Monte Carlo Rally. Unbeknownst to Herbie's driver, thieves have hidden a stolen diamond in Herbie's gas tank, and are now trying to get it back.

Title: Attack Force Z
Description: A group of Australian commandos launch a secret mission against Japanese forces in World War II.

Title: Inherit the Viper
Description: Crime thriller about three siblings in Appalachia getting by as local opioid dealers, trying not to get caught in the spiral of violence that comes with the territory.

Title: Battle for Terra
Description: The peaceful alien planet Terra faces annihilation, as the homeless remainder of the human race sets its eyes on it. Mala, a rebellious Terrian teenager, will do everything she can to stop it.

Title: Fortress of War
Description: A war drama set during the Nazi invasion of the Soviet Union in June 1941, in which Soviet troops held on to a border stronghold for nine days.

Title: See You Yesterday
Description: Two Brooklyn teenage prodigies, C.J. Walker and Sebastian Thomas, build makeshift time machines to save C.J.'s brother, Calvin, from being wrongfully killed by a police officer.

Title: Zinda
Description: A man, taken and locked up for 14 years without any sane reason, is suddenly released, and has 4 days to figure out why this was done to him.

Title: Thor: Hammer of the Gods
Description: Thor along with his friends travel to a mysterious island seeking glory and fame. Upon arriving they encounter strange creatures and they start searching the island for answers. Meanwhile Thor keeps seeing visions for a mighty warrior and a big hammer and Freyja tells him that his visions are clues so they start searching for the hammer.

Title: iBoy
Description: After being shot, Tom awakens from a coma to discover that fragments of his smartphone have been embedded in his head--and worse, that returning to normal teenage life is impossible because he has developed a strange set of superpowers.

Title: The Substitute: Failure Is Not an Option
Description: Former mercenary Karl Thomasson returns once again as a substitute teacher, this time to infiltrate a military school's faculty to cease the actions of white supremacists.

Title: Doctor Mordrid
Description: An unspeakable evil has come into our dimension and wants to rule over Earth, and only a mysterious sorceror known as Doctor Mordrid can stop him.

Title: Black Scorpion
Description: Darcy is a cop who is also a supehero named Black Scorpion at night who kicks and beats evildoers to a pulp. She soon catches wind of an asthmatic mad scientist who plans on tainting the city's air supply with a toxin. Only Darcy in her superhero garb can stop him with the assistance of a petty thief named Argyle and a really cool car.

Title: Nude Nuns with Big Guns
Description: A left-for-dead nun forced into prostitution embarks on a deadly revenge mission to do the Lord's work, punishing sinners in a strictly personal vigilante Holy War.

Title: Mortal Kombat: Rebirth
Description: Detective Jackson Briggs recruits the assassin Hanzo Hasashi into an undercover mission - enter an illegal tournament and eliminate all its criminal participants.

Title: Sweeney!
Description: When one of his informants is murdered, Detective Inspector Jack Regan is drawn into a deadly political game. He is soon a marked man and, after being framed, is suspended from duty. This doesn't stop him searching for the truth.

Title: Yaksha: Ruthless Operations
Description: Nicknamed after a human-devouring spirit, the ruthless leader of an overseas black ops team takes up a dangerous mission in a city riddled with spies.

Title: Winx Club: The Mystery of the Abyss
Description: The Winx Club is struggling with a terrible mystery that will make your heart beat faster! The archenemies of the Winx Club, the Trix witches, team up with the evil nymph Politea and find out that, to defeat the fairies once and for all and become invincible, it takes very little: a Pearl hidden in the Deep of the Infinite Ocean! As small as powerful, the Pearl of the Depth gives enormous powers to those who possess it! The team of the Dark Magic: Trix, Politea and Tritannus, not bad as group... almost unbeatable! But none of them have come to terms with the true power of the Winx, the power of Love: Bloom is more determined than ever to win the magic Pearl before her enemies and save prince Sky captured by the Trix and imprisoned in the Ocean. For the Winx there is not a minute to waste: how will they stop the plans of their enemies before it's too late? The answer is not simple: with a twist, Politea is preparing to seize power all to herself, betraying allies and polluting the Oceans to regain strength and power. Get ready: the most dangerous mission of the Winx is about to begin!

Title: Survive the Night
Description: A disgraced doctor and his family are held hostage at their home by criminals on the run, when a robbery-gone-awry requires them to seek immediate medical attention.

Title: Cherrybomb
Description: Three teenagers go on a wild weekend of drink, drugs, shop-lifting and stealing cars that quickly spins beyond their control.

Title: Werewolf: The Beast Among Us
Description: Set in a 19th century village, a young man studying under a local doctor joins a team of hunters on the trail of a wolf-like creature.

Title: Balle perdue 3
Description: In southern France, Lino is a getaway driver, ex-convict, and burglar who builds cars for criminal purposes.

Title: Embattled
Description: A son aspires to follow in his famous MMA father's footsteps, but along his journey must figure out how to break the abusive cycle, if possible, that his father has continued.

Title: Hanky Panky
Description: Completely innocent man, Michael Jordon, is drawn into a web of government secrets when a girl carrying a mysterious package gets into a taxi with him. When she's later murdered, Michael becomes the chief suspect and goes on the run.

Title: Witch Mountain
Description: It follows two teens that develop abilities and discover that their suburb may not be as idyllic as it seems.

Title: Beyond Rangoon
Description: An American tourist finds herself in the middle of a political uprising in Burma.

Title: Streetwalkin'
Description: A high school dropout working as a street prostitute spends one night turning tricks and avoiding her emotionally unstable pimp who's starting to turn very violent.

Title: Dragon Wars: D-War
Description: Once in 500 years, ancient mythical creatures come to Earth, wreaking havoc and destruction. This time they must be stopped.

Title: Cold Sweat
Description: With his wife and daughter being held hostage, a seasoned ex-military man is involved in a shady smuggling operation to save his family.

Title: Take Point
Description: On the day of the U.S. presidential election in 2024, Ahab (HA) and his team of elite mercenaries embark on a secret CIA mission to abduct North Korea's Armed Forces Minister in an underground bunker below the Korean Demilitarized Zone (DMZ). However, they get caught in the crossfire which causes tensions to escalate to the brink of World War III.

Title: Dig Me No Grave
Description: Aging hunter Scott, trapped beneath a bear, is rescued by a mysterious stranger. Inside a remote cabin, their survival becomes a tense battle as hidden motives surface, escalating into a gripping fight for their lives and buried secrets.

Title: Sex & Fury
Description: During the Meiji era, a gambler named Ochô takes revenge on the three dignitaries who killed her father, shelters a wanted anarchist, and crosses paths with a British femme fatale.

Title: Shottas
Description: Wayne and Biggs grow up together on the tough and dangerous streets of Kingston, Jamaica. Eventually moving to Miami, they begin a ruthless climb to the top of a criminal enterprise as they aggressively take control of the Jamaican mob.

Title: Tadap
Description: Unforeseen circumstances threaten the passionate relationship between star-crossed lovers.

Title: Ice Twisters
Description: Charlie Price, a former scientist turned science fiction author, starts living one of his novels when the Federal Science Foundation's weather experiments escape control and turn disastrous.

Title: Robopocalypse
Description: A sci-fi story set in the aftermath of a robot uprising.

Title: Skin Trade
Description: After his family is killed by a Serbian gangster with international interests, NYC detective Nick goes to Southeast Asia and teams up with a Thai detective to get revenge and destroy the syndicate's human trafficking network.

Title: Hearts and Armour
Description: Bradamante, a woman wearing an invincible suit of armor, is travelling the countryside at the time of the Crusades. After ending up in the middle of a web of romantic and cultural tangles, she finds herself in love with a Moor prince, while one of the Christian knights has fallen in love with a Moor princess. Others, however, are against the cross-cultural romance, and Bradamante's love is soon forced into a duel to the death. Will she ever be with her true love?

Title: The Big Mouth
Description: On a San Diego beach, Gerald Clamson fishes out of the water a look-alike frog man who gives him a map to a stash of stolen-diamonds coveted by several crime syndicates.

Title: Belly of the Beast
Description: An ex-CIA agent's quest to find his kidnapped daughter leads him on a trail of political intrigue, corruption, danger and betrayal; he will stop at nothing to save her.

Title: Bloodthirst
Description: In a post apocalyptic world run by vampires, only the strong survive. John Shepard, Vampire Hunter, is one of them. John has to track down and eliminate the master vampire before he himself gets turned.

Title: Firepower
Description: A merc is hired by the F.B.I. to track down a powerful recluse criminal. A woman is also trying to track him down for her own personal vendetta.

Title: Knuckledust
Description: A former marine is trapped in an elite underground fight club. When cops swoop in they discover only one man left alive, him. But all is not as it seems. Is he the sole survivor or a mass murderer?

Title: Assassin
Description: Ruthless killer for hire (Danny Dyer) breaks the rules of his profession and falls for a beautiful young woman. Discovering the notorious gangland brothers (Martin & Gary Kemp) had hired him to kill her father, his world breaks down and he must turn against his criminal employers and their gang to save the woman he loves.

Title: You Can't Win 'Em All
Description: During the 1922 Turkish Civil War, two Americans and a group of foreign mercenaries offer their services to a local Turkish governor who hires them as guards for a secret transport.

Title: Pimpinero: Blood and Oil
Description: In the treacherous desert along the Colombia-Venezuela border, gasoline smugglers known as "pimpineros" risk their lives transporting illegal fuel across the harsh landscape.

Title: The Stone Killer
Description: A top New York detective is sent to Los Angeles where he must solve a case involving an old Sicilian Mafia family feud.

Title: Init Ng Laman
Description: While running from his wife, who is trying to kill him, he meets another object of his desire.

Title: The Scythian
Description: These are times when one civilization is replacing another. A new era is about to begin in Central Eurasia. Scythians, the proud warriors, are all but gone. The few of their descendants have become ruthless mercenary assassins, the "waves of Ares." Lutobor, is a soldier with a difficult task at hand. He becomes involved in internecine conflicts and sets off on a perilous journey to save his family. His guide is a captive Scythian by the name of Weasel. Lutobor and Weasel are enemies. They pray to different gods but must embark on this journey together. They brave the wild steppes, moving toward the last haven of the Scythians, to what seems to be their inevitable demise.

Title: Boa vs. Python
Description: After a genetically-altered python escapes, a scientist is enlisted to help kill it by releasing a giant boa constrictor that he owns.

Title: The Numbers Station
Description: A disgraced black ops agent is dispatched to a remote CIA broadcast station to protect a code operator. Soon, they find themselves in a life-or-death struggle to stop a deadly plot before it's too late.

Title: Doc Savage: The Man of Bronze
Description: Doc and the Amazing Five battle Captain Seas and "the green death" for control of a fabulous resource.

Title: Turks & Caicos
Description: Worricker is a retired spy living in the Caribbean. He realizes he is in trouble when four "businessmen" show up. They look like mob bosses, but one actually works for the CIA. He gets help from two former MI5 colleagues back in London.

Title: Awake
Description: A man wakes in a hospital bed with no recollection of who he is, and learns that he's wanted by the police for committing a series of murders.

Title: Cottonmouth
Description: When Ed Dantes is framed and condemned to the tortures of a territorial prison in 1895, he must learn the ways of the outlaw to escape and exact his revenge.

Title: Adipurush
Description: A modern adaptation of the Indian epic Ramayana which follows the exiled prince Raghav's journey to rescue his wife Janaki from the demon king Lankesh.

Title: Sooryavanshi
Description: DCP Veer Sooryavanshi, the chief of the Anti-Terrorism Squad in India, tries to bring down a terrorist organization with which he has a history.

Title: Backdraft 2
Description: The sequel to the 1991 hit, follows an investigator with the Chicago F.D., who has to track down an arms dealer who use deadly fires as a distraction.

Title: Appleseed
Description: In a vast futuristic city, built on the ashes of the third world war, a police officer and her cyborg partner fight terrorism.

Title: Setup
Description: A group of friends become involved in a potentially deadly diamond heist.

Title: Stagecoach
Description: On the stagecoach to Cheyenne, a mixed group of passengers must work together to survive the arduous journey and the Indian attacks.

Title: Dead Bang
Description: A man kills a storekeeper and a cop. LASD homicide detective Jerry Beck gets the case. His murder suspect is connected to a heavily armed white supremacy group.

Title: Batman: Mystery of the Batwoman
Description: The Dark Knight must contend with a mysterious female vigilante who emulates him, but to a more ruthless degree.

Title: Flight 93
Description: Flight 93 is the story of the heroic passengers that took back their plane in an effort to stop a 9-11 terrorist attack.

Title: Steamboat Bill, Jr.
Description: The effete son of a cantankerous riverboat captain comes to join his father's crew.

Title: Infidel
Description: An American man (Jim Caviezel) is kidnapped after a friend invites him to Cairo to speak out about recent militant uprisings. His wife heads to the city after hearing the news, determined to get him back.

Title: Space Adventure Cobra
Description: After two years in hiding, a famed space pirate with a "psychogun" for a left arm joins a bounty huntress on a quest to save her world, only to find himself battling an old enemy.

Title: Need for Speed 2
Description: A follow-up to the 2014 action movie 'Need for Speed'.
A scientist invents a time machine, which leads to a bitter battle between his evil twin brother and his son.

Title: Ground Control
Description: A disgraced former air traffic controller is called back into service when the airport's traffic control system malfunctions.

Title: The Phantom Planet
Description: After an invisible asteroid draws an astronaut and his ship to its surface, he is miniaturized by the phantom planet's exotic atmosphere.

Title: Leonard Part 6
Description: Secret Agent Leonard Parker is called out of retirement to save the world from evil genius Medusa Johnson.

Title: Yamakasi
Description: 7 guys from Paris' suburbs like challenges like climbing tall buildings and doing parkour - especially with cops/flics chasing them. When a kid fan urgently needs a heart the Yamakasis try to find a way.

Title: Confidential Assignment 2: International
Description: The film depicts an unpredictable global cooperative investigation by South Korean, North Korean, and American detectives who have come together for their own purposes.

Title: Shark Side of the Moon
Description: Decades ago, the USSR developed unkillable sharks and launched them to the moon. Today, a team of American astronauts will endure the fight of their lives.

Title: American Hero
Description: Melvin, a reluctant Superhero, lives only for crime, women and drugs - until he realises that the only way he will ever get to see his estranged son is to go straight and fulfil his potential as a crime fighter.

Title: Operation Red Sea
Description: PLA Navy Marine Corps launch a hostage rescue operation in the fictional Republic of Ihwea and undergo a fierce battle with rebellions and terrorism.

Title: Steel
Description: The construction of a steel skyscraper becomes a race against time and challenges the sanity of a building foreman and his crew.

Title: Masterminds
Description: Trapped in a school in which a gang of criminals has seized control, a young troublemaker fights a cat and mouse battle from inside.

Title: Trancers II
Description: 6 years after a time cop returns home from battling future alien zombies, his settled life is turned upside down when a mad scientists creates more.

Title: Nirvana
Description: The main character Solo in Nirvana, a computer game developed by Jimi for release in 3 days, has gained self-awareness after a virus attack. Solo wants to be deleted. Jimi wants to find his ex.

Title: Girl Vs. Monster
Description: A teen girl goes on a mission to recapture a dangerous monster that she accidentally released before it can do harm to her parents.

Title: Raees
Description: A bootlegger sets out to improve his community as a promising leader but falls in a political trap.

Title: Attack on Titan: Part 2
Description: A young boy name Eren Jaeger has to use his gift to know about the mystery of the Titans.

Title: Paper Soldiers
Description: Under guidance from experienced thief Will, rookie burglar Shawn navigates relationships with girlfriend Mo'Nique, bumbling friends Birdie and Johnny, parole officer, and volatile neighborhood sociopath Stu while committing robberies.

Title: The Return of the Musketeers
Description: In France in 1649, the services of the Four Musketeers are needed again, and they run into some old foes from twenty years before.

Title: Hercules and the Amazon Women
Description: Hercules and Iolaus take time out from Iolaus' wedding preparations, to help a distant village under attack from "monsters". When they reach their destination, they find the monsters are in fact Amazonian women who are controlled by Hera.

Title: Shadow Conspiracy
Description: Bishop, trusted advisor to the president, has shots fired at him when Pachenko comes to him about a traitor in highest level of government. He gets away from the cold blooded assassin twice. Will he find the traitor before getting killed?

Title: Return to Halloweentown
Description: Marnie and Dylan are going to follow their dreams to go to college, at Halloweentown University, which is also known as Witch University.

Title: Ka Whawhai Tonu
Description: Set in New Zealand in 1864, follows the story of a crucial conflict of the nation's first land warfare, fought between Maori and colonial soldiers against insurmountable odds.

Title: Tokyo Drifter
Description: After his gang disbands, a yakuza enforcer looks forward to life outside of organized crime but soon must become a drifter after his old rivals attempt to assassinate him.

Title: Detective Chinatown 2
