Description: Tang and Qin team up to solve a murder in New York's Chinatown.

Title: Jane and the Lost City
Description: Jane and the colonel must journey to Africa to the lost city to retrieve the diamonds before the Germans do. Based on the classic adult UK comic strip "Jane," especially popular during World War II for its strong pin-up elements.

Title: Supercop 2
Description: As a crime wave sweeps through Hong Kong, the police call on Jessica Yang, a rising star in their ranks, to help stop a notorious gang of thieves.

Title: Bon Cop Bad Cop
Description: Two Canadian detectives, one from Ontario and the other from Quebec, must work together when a murdered victim is found on the Ontario-Quebec border.

Title: Godzilla vs. SpaceGodzilla
Description: Godzilla is threatened by two new forces: Mogera - another UN built machine; and Space Godzilla - a beast spawned from Godzilla's particles in space.

Title: Monster
Description: When a serial killer murders her sister, rage consumes her completely as she seeks for revenge.

Title: Kingdom 2: Far and Away
Description: It follows a young man who dreams of becoming a general and Ying Zheng, whose goal is unification.

Title: Slaughter
Description: Slaughter, a former Green Beret, avenges the killing of loved ones by the Mob, and in so doing is coerced by the Feds into traveling to Mexico to finish off surviving mobsters.

Title: To Hell and Back
Description: The true WWII story of Audie Murphy, the most decorated soldier in U.S. history. Based on the autobiography of Audie Murphy who stars as himself in the film.

Title: The Amazing Bulk
Description: Henry 'Hank' Howard works as a scientist in a military lab, trying to create a superhuman formula but with little success. He is also in love with the daughter of his boss, a general. In an effort to earn his approval to marry his daughter, Henry tests the formula on himself, inadvertently transforming himself into a purple rage monster and leaving him at the mercy of those who wish to exploit his newfound power.

Title: David and Goliath
Description: This epic movie filmed in North Africa and London follows young shepherd David as he takes on the mighty warrior Goliath against all odds.

Title: Salyut-7
Description: USSR, June 1985. Based on actual events. After contact with the Salyut 7 space station is lost, cosmonauts Vladimir Dzhanibekov and Viktor Savinykh dock with the empty, frozen craft, and bring her back to life.

Title: Rapa Nui
Description: Love between the representatives of two warring tribes changes the balance of power on the whole remote island.

Title: Confidential Assignment
Description: When a crime organization from North Korea crosses borders and enters South Korean soil, a South Korean detective must cooperate with a North Korean detective to investigate their whereabouts.

Title: Timebomb
Description: Eddy is recognized on TV after rescuing two. A group tries to kill the peaceful watchmaker. Why? He sees a cute analyst.

Title: Dushman
Description: A woman goes on a hunt to find her twin sister's rapist and murderer.

Title: Singham
Description: A truly honest police officer is transferred to a town controlled by a gangster he has humiliated. The gangster believes he can use good power to bring down this officer who made him look foolish and weak.

Title: Shot
Description: He thought he knew what life was about. He was dead wrong. Rob's an ambitious photographer who is trying to boost his career. He attempts to document life in the 'hood and hooks up with a gang who shows him what life is like on their turf, with their rules. Rob realizes he is in too deep as the bodies start to drop. Will he make it out alive?

Title: Ransomed
Description: A young diplomat is assigned the task of carrying the ransom money to rescue an abducted diplomat in Lebanon, and a local taxi driver accidently gets involved in the mission.

Title: Adventures of Captain Marvel
Description: To protect a magic talisman from being used for evil, a teenage boy named Billy Batson is given the power to become an adult superhero, Captain Marvel, with a single magic word: "Shazam!"

Title: The Italian Connection
Description: A Milanese pimp is pursued by - and then pursues - a pair of New York hitmen and the gangsters who framed him for stealing a shipment of heroin.

Title: Day of the Falcon
Description: Set in the 1930s Arab states at the dawn of the oil boom, the story centers on a young Arab prince torn between allegiance to his conservative father and his modern, liberal father-in-law.

Title: Blood: The Last Vampire
Description: Saya is a Japanese vampire slayer whose next mission is in a high school on a US military base in 1960s Japan, where she poses as a student. She uses a katana/samurai sword to kill vampires.

Title: Godzilla: Planet of the Monsters
Description: A desperate group of refugees attempts to recolonize Earth 20,000 years after Godzilla took over, but one young man wants revenge above all else.

Title: The Assignment
Description: An American naval officer is recruited for an operation to eliminate his lookalike, the infamous terrorist Carlos The Jackal.

Title: One Good Cop
Description: An NYPD Detective and his struggle for justice, while taking care of his late partner's three little girls after he is killed in the line of duty.

Title: Breaker! Breaker!
Description: Truck driver searches for his brother, who has disappeared in a town run by a corrupt judge.

Title: The Black Hole
Description: An atomic research experiment goes awry in St. Louis, Missouri unleashing not only a big black hole, but also a creature from beyond that feeds on electricity through the streets of this Midwest city.

Title: Wake of the Red Witch
Description: During the 1860s in the South Pacific, Capt. Ralls, skipper of the Red Witch, has a series of adventures involving sunken gold bullion, pearls, natives, an unscrupulous ship owner and a giant octopus.

Title: The Misfit Brigade
Description: War story of the 27th Panzers, Hitler's heavy-duty combat regiment composed of prisoners. In 1943, this motley tank crew is sent on a suicide mission behind enemy lines to destroy a Soviet train that's carrying fuel for the Red Army.

Title: WWE Royal Rumble
Description: It will be the 38th annual Royal Rumble and it will take place on Saturday, February 1, 2025, at the Lucas Oil Stadium in Indianapolis, Indiana,

Title: All Through the Night
Description: Runyonesque Broadway gamblers turn patriotic when they stumble onto a cell of Nazi saboteurs.

Title: Shamus
Description: Millions in diamonds are stolen from a safe in NYC and later the burglar is killed. Shamus is paid $10,000 by the owner to find the diamonds or killer.

Title: Night of the Running Man
Description: A Las Vegas cab driver discovers a stolen million dollars, and is tracked by a relentless and cold-blooded assassin sent to retrieve the money.

Title: Age of Heroes
Description: The true story of the formation of Ian Fleming's 30 Commando unit, a precursor for the elite forces in the U.K.

Title: Eye for an Eye 2
Description: A blind swordsman reluctantly mentors an orphan seeking vengeance for his destroyed family, teaching him martial arts skills. The orphan waits for an opportunity to avenge his kin.

Title: Gunday
Description: The lives of Calcutta's most powerful Gunday, Bikram and Bala, changes when Nandita enters it. Then a counter-force takes charge and a thriller unfolds.

Title: 10 Minutes Gone
Description: A crime thriller that centers on a man whose memory has been lost due to a bank heist gone wrong. The character will need to piece together the missing 10 minutes from his memory in order to determine who sabotaged him.

Title: Illang: The Wolf Brigade
Description: Set in the distant future where both North and South Koreas agree to establish a joint government, which has been in preparation for a duration of 7 years, the plot focuses on political uprisings on opposing sides which grow fierce when a special police unit is formed to stop the chaos.

Title: The Friendly
Description: Military medic Curtis gets injured, returns home with dog Friendly who saved him. Curtis and Friendly adjust to civilian life. Curtis falls in love with nurse Sophia, who has a child.

Title: Samrat Prithviraj
Description: A magnum opus recounting the glorious tale of one of India's bravest emperors- Samrat Prithviraj Chauhan. Inspired from the epic poem Prithviraj Raaso and other folklores.

Title: Kizumonogatari Part 3: Reiketsu
Description: Part 3 of Kizumonogatari (Wound Tale) trilogy, based on a light novel by Nisio Isin.

Title: Avengers of Justice: Farce Wars
Description: While trying to remain a good husband and father, Superbat and the Avengers of Justice come out of retirement to stop Dark Jokester and Lisp Luthor from freezing the planet.

Title: Titanic
Description: Third Reich's Nazi propaganda epic about a heroic fictional German officer on board of the RMS Titanic. On its maiden voyage in April 1912, the supposedly unsinkable ship hits an iceberg in the Atlantic Ocean and starts to go down.

Title: The Last Victim
Description: The Last Victim is a Neo Western thriller set in the American southwest, following Sheriff Hickey trying to solve the worst case he has seen in his small town, likely caused by a violent local gang led by a fearsome criminal.

Title: Due Justice
Description: An attorney with a military past hunts down the gang who killed his wife and brother and took his daughter.

Title: Undefeatable
Description: Kristi Jones (Cynthia Rothrock) avenges her sister's death at the hands of a crazed martial arts rapist.

Title: Ludo
Description: From a resurfaced sex tape to a rogue suitcase of money, four wildly different stories overlap at the whims of fate, chance and one eccentric criminal.

Title: The 2nd
Description: An Army Delta Force officer is late picking up his son at college. His son and a Supreme Court Justice's daughter are the last there. A gang of terrorists are there to abduct her and force her dad's hand on a Second Amendment vote.

Title: Screamers: The Hunting
Description: A group of humans arrive on Sirius 6-B to investigate an SOS signal sent out from the planet, which has been supposedly deserted since the destruction of the man-made weapons known as "screamers." Once the squad arrives, they find a group of human survivors eking out an existence in an old military outpost, but more important, they discover that the threat of the screamers has become even more insidious, now that they're able to morph into human form.

Title: Sooryavansham
Description: Heera fails to live up to expectations of his father Thakur Bhanupratap Singh, a powerful and respected man of his community. Despite all odds Heera struggles to keep his father's pride.

Title: Operation Seawolf
Description: In the last days of World War II, Germany, desperate for a last chance to defeat the Allies, gathers its last remaining U-Boats for one last mission: to attack the continental United States.

Title: Hitman
Description: Two hitmen, one a novice and the other a veteran with poor luck, band together to find the "King of Killers" for whom there is a large reward.

Title: Free Ride
Description: A single mom caught up in the Florida drug trade during the late 1970s tries to make a better life for her two girls.

Title: Dark of the Sun
Description: A band of mercenaries led by Captain Curry travel through war-torn Congo across deadly terrain, battling rival armies, to steal $50 million in uncut diamonds. But infighting, sadistic rebels and a time lock jeopardize everything.

Title: Bounty Killer
Description: Bounty killers compete for body count, fame and a fat stack of cash. They're ending the plague of corporate greed and providing the survivors of the apocalypse with retribution. This is the age of the BOUNTY KILLER.

Title: S.T.A.L.K.E.R.: Shadow of the Zone
Description: A seasoned Free Stalker tasked with guiding a band of Mercenaries deep into The Zone to investigate a paranormal radio signal. Based on the S.T.A.L.K.E.R. video-game series by G.S.C. Game World.

Title: Interstelar 2: Operation Terra 2040
Description: 16 years after the events of Interstelar (2014) as food shortage attacks yet again, another brave man goes on a space mission to bring food to Earth.

Title: Unicorn Wars
Description: War-hungry teddy bears journey from bootcamp to the psychedelic terrors of the Magic Forest in this darkly beautiful horror animation.

Title: Hellhound
Description: While hunting down a brutal kingpin, one error sends an elite hitman on a downward spiral that devolves into all-out war on the streets of Thailand.

Title: Fullmetal Alchemist: The Sacred Star of Milos
Description: In the lost holy land of Milos, the Elrics search for the truth behind an unknown form of alchemy. What secrets are hidden in Milos? Riddles must be solved and dangers faced before the truth can be found.

Title: Old Men in New Cars
Description: Fresh out of a Danish prison, Harald bosses his old gang around, into visiting his hospitalized foster dad, who wants to see his bio son before dying. The son's in a Swedish prison. Then there's a money matter - robbing a bank.

Title: Spiders
Description: After a Soviet space station crashes into a New York City subway tunnel, a species of venomous spiders is discovered, and soon they mutate to gigantic proportions and wreak havoc on the city.

Title: No Retreat, No Surrender 3: Blood Brothers
Description: Two feuding brothers (one a policeman, the other a martial arts expert) of different political views, join forces to avenge the death of their father, a retired agent, killed by the mafia.

Title: School of Magical Animals 3
Description: Children with magical animal companions at Winterstein School experience adventures spanning a forest and fashion show, encountering a snobbish cat and vegan crocodile while navigating friendship and first love.

Title: High-Ballin'
Description: Two truck drivers fight off thugs who have been hired to drive them out of business.

Title: The Crocodile Hunter: Collision Course
Description: The Crocodile Hunter mistakes some CIA agents for poachers and sets out to stop them from capturing a wily croc which, unbeknownst to him, has swallowed a tracking drone.

Title: Fat Pizza
Description: The life at a suburban Sydney pizzeria.

Title: Legend of the Eight Samurai
Description: Princess Shizu was born under a terrible curse. Only the eight legendary samurai, hailing from across Japan, can protect her from an ancient supernatural clan to fulfill their destinies as foretold by prophecy.

Title: Believer 2
Description: A determined detective continues his search for the truth behind Asia's largest drug organization and its elusive boss he has unfinished business with.

Title: We Still Steal the Old Way
Description: The Archer Gang are back and doing a daring heist in London. Remanded in prison, they will try to break out their old friend Briggs.

Title: Icebreaker
Description: At the the Killington ski resort something has gone awry. Evil terrorists led by the sinister Greig have taken the resort hostage with a stolen nuclear device. It's up to Ski Patrol bum Matt Foster to save the day - and his fiancé.

Title: Phantasm III: Lord of the Dead
Description: Mike and Reggie continue to hunt the mysterious Tall Man, discovering along the way that the invasion has already begun.

Title: Violent Cop
Description: A violence prone police officer discovers that his colleague is trafficking drugs.

Title: The Return of the Six-Million-Dollar Man and the Bionic Woman
Description: Nine years after his retirement from the government, Colonel Steve Austin must again team up with Jaime Sommers to stop a terrorist group. Complicating matters for Austin are his estranged son Michael, who struggles for his father's acceptance as he graduates from flight school, and Jaime, who must cope with her and Steve's past. When Michael is severely injured in a crash, Steve must make the same decision about fitting him with bionics that he had to make with Jaime years ago after her accident.

Title: McBain
Description: A former Vietnam War lieutenant reforms his old team in order to help a revolutionary's sister overthrow a ruthless dictator.

Title: MFKZ
Description: In Dark Meat City, a young man develops supernatural powers after an otherwise uneventful scooter accident.

Title: Girl Camp 2004: Lesbian Fleshpots
Description: A woman infiltrates a factory producing subservient young women in order to steal from its bank account.

Title: The Unholy Rollers
Description: Behind the scenes of the roller derby circuit. A beautiful young woman joins a roller derby team, but her fierce independence and competitive spirit get her into trouble.

Title: Inside Men
Description: A former political henchman seeks out revenge for being dropped by a ruthless politician while a determined investigator tries to find proof of a connection between the two of them.

Title: Hot Wheels: AcceleRacers - Ignition
Description: After the events of the world race, two racing teams, the Teku and the metal Maniacs, go head to head in new racing realms.

Title: Megalodon
Description: A military vessel on the search for an unidentified submersible finds themselves face to face with a giant shark, forced to use only what they have on board to defend themselves from the monstrous beast.

Title: Fay Grim
Description: Fay Grim heads to Paris in pursuit of her deceased husband's notebooks, which could contain information that compromises the security of the U.S. But she's not the only one who is after them, and she's forced into a life-changing decision.

Title: Blister
Description: Plot kept under wraps. Described as an action drama.

Title: The King of the Kickboxers
Description: A cop goes undercover in Thailand to avenge his brother's death in this martial arts film.

Title: 3-Headed Shark Attack
Description: As a mutated, three-headed, great white shark eats its way from one end of the ship to the next, the passengers have to fight the deadly predator using anything they can find.

Title: Undead
Description: A quaint Australian fishing village is overcome by meteorites that turn its residents into the ravenous undead, leaving a small group of those unharmed to find a way out.

Title: Invincible
Description: Colonel John Taylor enlists billionaire inventor Leor Teska to fund a secret black site, testing Teska's new nano technology for military applications, developed by scientists. When one of the test subjects, Brock Cortez, escapes, Teska's head of security, Cam Devore is given the dangerous task of tracking him down.

Title: Scanners III: The Takeover
Description: A young female scanner turns from a sweet young thing into a murderous, power-crazed villain after she takes an experimental drug developed by her father. Her brother, who is also a scanner, is the only one powerful enough to stop her.

Title: Play Dirty
Description: With Internal affairs on his back, a corrupt cop working for a crime boss must take out the competition if he wants to live long enough to leave town.

Title: Avalon
Description: In a dystopian world, a woman spends her time playing an illegal and dangerous game, hoping to find meaning in her world.

Title: The California Kid
Description: A deranged desert town sheriff has a murderous habit of forcing speeders to their deaths, until a young man with a souped-up hotrod arrives to possibly end it.

Title: The Summertime Killer
Description: After witnessing his father's murder as a child, a man seeks vengeance against the mafia gang responsible, methodically hunting them down while evading law enforcement and the crime boss.

Title: Guyver: Dark Hero
Description: Sean Barker, unwilling host to an alien bio-armor known as the Guyver, must fight the Kronos Corporation again before they discover the secrets of the Guyver's origin.

Title: Beastmaster III: The Eye of Braxus
Description: Before he died, Dar's father gave a mysterious amulet to Tal, Dar's younger brother who is now king. Dar, while wandering with his animal companions, chances to meet and rescue a family who seek the help of King Tal against Lord Agon, a sorcerer who has conquered their land. Dar obtains an audience for them with Tal, who rallies his troops to march against Agon in the morning. Alas, the young king is captured by Agon's crimson warriors during the night. It is the amulet -- the Eye of the imprisoned god Braxus -- that Agon really wants. But Dar now carries half of it, and is nowhere to be found. Will he fall into Lord Agon's clutches when he comes to free his brother?

Title: Immortal Demon Slayer
Description: A giant rebelled against the heavens. It was declared a devil and defeated. The immortal heart evolved into Sun Wukong. The heavens found him, and ravaged his home. He enters the heavenly kingdom, disguised as a human, seeking retribution.

Title: The Lost Patrol
Description: A dozen British soldiers, lost in a Mesopotamian desert during World War I, are menaced by unseen Arab enemies.

Title: Endgame - Bronx lotta finale
Description: A telepathic mutant recruits a post-World War III TV game-show warrior to lead her band of mutants to safety.

Title: Captain America II: Death Too Soon
Description: The star spangled hero must battle a villain's plan to poison America with a chemical that horrifically accelerates the aging process.

Title: Dance of the Dead
Description: On the night of the big High-School Prom, the dead rise to eat the living, and the only people who can stop them are the losers who couldn't get dates to the dance.

Title: Welcome to the Jungle
Description: Police officers Jay Bakshi and Sandhya have been given task to track down notorious criminal Raj Solanki. Things take an unexpected turn when JaY finds out that Raj plays a significant role in his life.

Title: Attack
Description: In 1944, an American Infantry company sets up an artillery observation post, but tensions between Captain Cooney and Lieutenant Costa run high.

Title: Born a Champion
Description: Mickey Kelley, one of the first American black belts in Brazilian jiu-jitsu, gets pulled away from everything he loves and into an unsanctioned MMA tournament.

Title: Dante's Inferno: An Animated Epic
Description: Dante journeys through the nine circles of Hell -- limbo, lust, gluttony, greed, anger, heresy, violence, fraud and treachery -- in search of his true love, Beatrice.

Title: 12 Rounds 3: Lockdown
Description: Upon returning to work after recovering from an injury, a police officer discovers and attempts to turn in incriminating evidence of illegal activities against his fellow cops.

Title: Survive the Game
Description: A man's life on his farm is interrupted when a cop and a pair of dangerous criminals show up.

Title: Bu Feng Zhui Ying
Description: Macau Police brings the tracking expert police officer out of retirement to help catch a dangerous group of professional thieves.

Title: Batman: Return of the Caped Crusaders
Description: Batman and Robin of the 1960s live action series are back in action to take down their fiendish foes united once more against them.

Title: Escape from the Bronx
Description: A rag-tag group of people must fight extermination squads amid their ruined city.

Title: Battle for the Lost Planet
Description: After hijacking a space shuttle, a spy finds that the controls are malfunctioning and sees alien battleships approaching Earth. Many years later, when the arc of his flight path returns to earth, he finds the planet under alien domination.

Title: One Piece: Strong World
Description: Straw Hat Pirates must save their navigator and stop the legendary Pirate, Shiki the Golden Lion from conquering East Blue.

Title: The Commando
Description: A DEA agent returns home with PTSD after a botched mission and must now protect his family from a home invasion when a recently freed convict and his henchmen come after their stash of millions hidden inside of the agent's home.

Title: A Company Man
Description: When a change of heart moves a well-trained hitman to tender his resignation to his employers, no good comes of it for anyone.

Title: R.O.T.O.R.
Description: A prototype crime-fighting robot breaks free from its lab, initiating a relentless rampage as it malfunctions and targets innocents for destruction.

Title: Nate and Hayes
Description: A swashbuckling adventure which takes place in the mid-1800's on the South Pacific islands where bloody raids and battles were once the rule of the day.

Title: El Gringo
Description: A man crossing into Mexico with a satchel of $2,000,000, and a bloody past, finds himself under sudden attack in the sleepy town of El Fronteras.

Title: Stormy Waters
Description: The captain of the tugboat Cyclone, André Laurent, rushes off to save the Mirva. He abandons his sick wife Yvonne and the couple celebrating their marriage. In the early morning, the Cyclone tugs the Mirva ashore with Catherine aboard.

Title: Naruto the Movie 3: Guardians of the Crescent Moon Kingdom
Description: Naruto, Kakashi, Sakura, and Rock Lee are assigned to protect Michiru, the prince of the Land of the Moon, while he travel the world. The prince purchased a tiger Sham and the whole circus, which became the team's protection.

Title: CC2C
Description: A cook from Chandni Chowk gets mistaken for the reincarnation of an ancient peasant warrior by the residents of an oppressed Chinese village.

Title: Largo Winch II
Description: Largo Winch, the newly appointed CEO of the W Group, is accused of crimes against humanity on the very day he announces his intention to sell his corporation and use the proceeds to create a humanitarian foundation.

Title: Foolproof
Description: Kevin, Sam and Rob are founding members of a theoretical group which pulls off heists. Leo, a gangster, blackmails them into pulling off a real multi-million dollar heist. Now it's up to them to get out alive.

Title: The King of Fighters
Description: Live-action feature based on the video game "King of Fighters".

Title: Gumrah
Description: Roshni Chadha, a singer in Bombay, is imprisoned in Hong Kong facing death sentence. Her troubled past involving unknown father's abandonment drives her journey to unravel truth and escape this predicament.

Title: The Wicked City
Description: Lung and his partner Ling is assigned to go after Daishu for selling a drug from the Rapters's world called 'Happiness' which causes people to evaporate, Lung, Ling and Wan-Gei join forces to fight the Rapters.

Title: In the Line of Duty: Ambush in Waco
Description: Religious fanatics are barricaded in a building, and surrounded by police. But they're not going to surrender, they prefer to die.

Title: Eraser: Reborn
Description: It is based on U.S. Marshal Mason Pollard who is specialized in engineering the fake deaths of witnesses that leaves no trace of their existence.

Title: Deadly Prey
Description: A group of sadistic mercenaries kidnap people off the streets and set them loose on the grounds of their secret camp, so the "students" at the camp can learn how to track down and kill their prey.

Title: Steel Rain
Description: A coup in North Korea forces an agent to defect to South with unconscious "Number One". While operatives from North hunt for both of them, the agent has to work with South Koreans to stop the nuclear war.

Title: Dororo
Description: A female warrior who was raised as a man joins a young samurai's quest to recover 48 of his body parts from 48 demons and to avenge her parents death.

Title: Go for It
Description: Two men meet in a strange situation and end up being mistaken first for robbers, then for Secret Service agents.

Title: No Man's Land
Description: When a vigilante border patrol turns fatal, a man flees on horseback to Mexico, seeking forgiveness from the victim's father.

Title: The Martial Arts Kid
Description: When a troubled teen from Cleveland experiences bullying in Cocoa Beach, he soon learns Martial Arts to gain confidence and self-defense skills.

Title: Airwolf
Description: A scientist who created a super-helicopter has defected to Libya, taking the machine with him. A secretive government agency hires an ex-Vietnam War pilot to go to Libya, steal the chopper, and bring it back.

Title: Ponniyin Selvan: Part I
Description: Vandiyathevan crosses the Chola land to deliver a message from the Crown Prince Aditha Karikalan, while Kundavai attempts to establish political peace as vassals and petty chieftains plot against the throne.

Title: Splitting Adam
Description: Adam Baker is the busiest teen ever, but after cloning himself, he will have the best summer ever with Adam 2, Winston, Party Boy, Sensitive, and Perfect. They're hoping to find the girl of his dreams and to crush his archenemy.

Title: Luck-Key
Description: A hapless loser assumes the identity of an amnesia victim without knowing that he is an assassin.

Title: Dadnapped
Description: Melissa has a bad case of sibling rivalry, only her competition is a fictional character in her father's best-selling novel about a teenage super spy. When her father is "dadnapped" by a group of overzealous fans, it's up to Melissa to help him by tapping her inner superhero.

Title: Bad Grandmas
Description: Four grandmothers accidentally kill a con man. When his partner shows up, things go south quickly.

Title: Miraculous
Description: The story of the movie will be based around Ladybug and Cat Noir's origins and how they both fell in love while including more details.

Title: A Gnome Named Gnorm
Description: A Los Angeles police detective partners up with a talking gnome in order to bring down the head of a crime ring.

Title: Paradise
Description: When corrupt officials cover up the murder of Ella's father, she cuts a swath through the anachronistic underbelly of her small island town.

Title: Patlabor 2: The Movie
Description: When a terrorist attack is blamed on the Air Force, Special Vehicle Unit 2 gets caught in the middle of a growing political conflict.

Title: The Purple Plain
Description: In World War II Burma, a Canadian bomber pilot becomes reckless after losing his bride in a Luftwaffe air raid.

Title: Spider-Man 4: Fan Film
Description: Spider-Man returns to face his greatest challenge yet as he faces off against The Vulture.

Title: Iron Eagle II
Description: A joint U.S.- Soviet strike force is assembled to wipe out a nuclear base in an outlaw nation that plans to take the world hostage.

Title: Solis
Description: After a space mining operation gone bad, Troy is on an emergency escape vehicle drifting towards the sun. He gets radio contact with possible help but will they get there in time?

Title: Dragonheart: Battle for the Heartfire
Description: A dragon known as Drago tries to end the rivalry between a brother and sister, both having dragon-like powers, who are after the throne of their grandfather, while a new threat steals Drago's source of power.

Title: Eastern Condors
Description: A group of Asian prisoners is recruited, trained, armed and sent to Vietnam to destroy a cache of American weapons left behind after the Vietnam War, before the Vietcong discovers its location.

Title: Dhoom
Description: Dhoom reinvents the classic cops and robbers tale for the 21st century. Fast bikes, big action, and non-stop fun make for a thrilling story.

Title: Miles Morales: A New Spider Man
Description: Miles Morales is a Comic Book Character who has been present in TV Shows, Games, and will Now be brought to life on screen

Title: Plunkett & Macleane
Description: Two robbers are persecuted by the law, whose servants are not much better and even worse.

Title: Circus of the Dead
Description: A sadistic group of clowns kidnap an unsuspecting man and his daughters, forcing him to play a deadly game in order to save his family.

Title: Spy 2
Description: Plot unknown. A follow-up to the 2015 comedy, 'Spy'.

Title: The New Original Wonder Woman
Description: After a dogfight with a German plane, U.S. Army Air Force pilot Steve Trevor crash lands on an uncharted island in the Bermuda Triangle. Paradise Island is inhabited only by women, and their existence has been kept a secret for thousands of years. Learning of the Nazi German threat to humanity, the Amazon princess Diana is chosen to accompany Trevor back to the United States to battle the Third Reich. Garbed in a skimpy red, white, and blue costume and armed with a magic lasso that forces anyone within its grasp to tell the truth, Diana uses her powers as Wonder Woman to battle the forces of evil.

Title: Rampage: President Down
Description: Bill Williamson returns to bring down the president of the United States and his Secret Service detail.

Title: Blizzard of Souls
Description: After losing his mother and his home, Arturs finds some consolation in joining the army. However, war is nothing like he imagined.

Title: Castle Keep
Description: During the Battle of the Bulge, an anachronistic count shelters a ragtag squad of Americans in his remote 10th Century castle hoping a battle there against the advancing Germans will not lead to its destruction and all the heritage within.

Title: Bellbottom
Description: When an Indian commercial airliner is hijacked by terrorists in the mid 1980s, a government agent is tasked with rescuing the 210 hostages.

Title: Secret of the Incas
Description: An adventurer searchers for hidden treasure in the Peruvian jungles.

Title: General Commander
Description: GRS operative Jake Alexander and his team of young recruits go after the most dangerous and notorious criminals with the help of a Hong Kong billionaire.

Title: Gunjan Saxena: The Kargil Girl
Description: Inspired by the life of a fearless young officer who made history by becoming the first Indian female Air Force officer to fly in a combat zone during the 1999 Kargil War

Title: The Batman vs. Dracula
Description: Batman faces off against the original creature of the night, Count Dracula, who has been unintentionally resurrected by the Penguin.

Title: Sharkula
Description: Count Dracula's curse manifests in a bloodthirsty great white shark terrorizing a tourist town. A hunt for this new predatory species uncovers vampires aiding its survival, leading to monstrous encounters and a deadly trail of carnage.

Title: Big Bad Mama II
Description: The evil local land baron forecloses on Angie's place, and she and her two daughters must leave and continue their life of crime. A reporter witnesses their heist of a bank, and helps them become folk legends by writing a story about them.

Title: The Last Outlaw
Description: Left for dead by his bank robbing gang, a marauder joins a posse to seek revenge.

Title: 40 Days and Nights
Description: When a colossal tectonic shift causes the sea level to start rising, a microbiologist gathers the DNA of as many species as she can, while the military creates an "ark" in a desperate attempt to preserve life on Earth.

Title: The Three Musketeers
Description: Joined by an eager recruit to protect the King of France, three loyal swordsmen attempt to defeat an evil royal advisor and a seductive envoy plotting to overthrow the crown.

Title: Attack on Titan: Chronicle
Description: A recap of the popular anime series Shingeki no Kyojin from seasons 1-3.

Title: Sonchiriya
Description: Set in the Chambal valley, the film follows the story of a legion of dreaded, warring dacoits who once terrorized the Indian heartlands.

Title: 120 Bahadur
Description: Recounting the legendary Battle of Rezang La during the Indo-China war, this film portrays the extraordinary valor and sacrifice of Indian soldiers against overwhelming odds.

Title: After Death
Description: A woman goes back to the island where her parents were killed. They had been working on a cure for cancer and accidentally raised the dead by angering a voodoo priest. With the woman is a group of mercenaries and they meet up with some other researchers. They raise the dead again and all hell breaks loose.

Title: Bad Man
Description: In Colt Lake Tennessee, Sam Evans tackles a meth epidemic. He is sidelined on arrival of Bobby Gaines an undercover agent. Despite Evans local ties, Gaines is hailed as hero. Suspicions arise on Gaines which unravels a complex narrative.

Title: The Long Swift Sword of Siegfried
Description: An "adults only" retelling of the legend of Siegfried.

Title: Ultramarines: A Warhammer 40,000 Movie
Description: A squad of Ultramarines answer a distress call from an Imperial Shrine World. A full Company of Imperial Fists was stationed there, but there is no answer from them. The squad investigates to find out what has happened there.

Title: Prince Nezha's Triumph Against Dragon King
Description: Tells the fable from Chinese mythology about the young warrior Nezha who takes on a group of evil dragons.

Title: Happy, Texas
Description: 3 prisoners escape. 2 end up in Happy, Texas, where they're mistaken for a gay couple expected there to help with the small girls beauty pageant. As the 2 are paid $1000, they decide to stay until the heat is gone.

Title: The Specials
Description: The sixth or seventh best superhero team in the world pursue their rightful place in the harshly competitive world of toy tie-ins and fighting evil.

Title: American Ninja 4: The Annihilation
Description: The two American Ninjas, Joe Armstrong and Sean Davidson, team up to do battle against a terrorist and his band of Ninjas.

Title: Under Lock and Key
Description: A drug lord's prison connections make this a dangerous and deadly assignment for undercover FBI agent Danielle Peters.

Title: Godzilla vs. Mechagodzilla II
Description: The United Nations assembles the ultimate weapon to defeat Godzilla, while scientists discover a fresh pteranodon egg on a remote Japanese island.

Title: Zeiram
Description: Bounty hunters Iria and Bob travel to Earth to capture an escaped bio-engineered fighting machine called Zeiramu.

Title: Twist
Description: A Modern take on the classic tale of Oliver Twist.

Title: Sprunki
Description: This plot is unknown for now.

Title: Deadbeat at Dawn
Description: One last job separates the leader of the Ravens gang from an early retirement. When he finds his girlfriend beaten to death by members of a rival gang, he seeks revenge, knowing that he may be dead by dawn. Will more blood bring her back?

Title: Trespass Against Us
Description: A man looks to find a way to escape the criminal ways of his outlaw family.

Title: Green Street 3: Never Back Down
Description: An old firm leader returns to Green Street for revenge after receiving a call that his little brother was killed, but is he able to cope with a new type of hooliganism and can he find his killer?

Title: Greased Lightning
Description: The true life story of Wendell Scott, the first black stock car racing driver to win an upper tier NASCAR race.

Title: Coffee & Kareem
Description: Twelve-year-old Kareem Manning hires a criminal to scare his mom's new boyfriend -police officer James Coffee - but it backfires, forcing Coffee and Kareem to team up in order to save themselves from Detroit's most ruthless drug kingpin.

Title: Wrong Turn at Tahoe
Description: A small-time crime boss kills a drug dealer without realizing that the drug dealer works for the biggest crime boss in the country.

Title: Crime Story
Description: A Special Agent is assigned to protect a wealthy business magnate. However, when the businessman is kidnapped in a daring ambush, he teams up with a seasoned detective to crack the case. But soon he discovers the case isn't that simple.

Title: Flight 666
Description: Passengers and crew on a flight are attacked by unseen forces that threaten all aboard.

Title: Opposing Force
Description: A major avenges a woman officer wronged by a brutal instructor of an escape-and-evasion course.

Title: Pray for Death
Description: After a peace-loving Japanese immigrant and his family become victims of a crime syndicate, a master ninja emerges.

Title: Scorched Earth
Description: A bounty hunter named Attica Gage tracks down criminals in a post-apocalyptic Earth.

Title: Suburban Sasquatch
Description: When a giant blood-thirsty anthropoid goes on a killing spree in a sprawling suburban park area, it's up to a couple of rangers, a reporter and a mystical Native-American warrior to try and stop it.

Title: Avalanche
Description: The vacationers at a winter wonderland struggle to survive after an avalanche of snow crashes into their ski resort. Their holiday then turns into a game of survival.

Title: Down River
Description: Four soldiers trapped behind enemy lines must confront their fears and desires while finding a way back to their battalion.

Title: Batman and Robin
Description: Second serial featuring the comic book character Batman. In it, Batman, together with his sidekick Robin, face off against the Wizard, a hooded villain with an electronic device that remotely controls vehicles.

Title: Derailed
Description: On an out of control train holding hostages and high-tech bio-weapons agent Kristoff (Van Damme) becomes a one man army to derail the terrorists and save the lives of everyone on board!

Title: Repeaters
Description: Three twenty-somethings find themselves in an impossible time loop, where each day they awaken to the same terrifying day as the preceding one.

Title: Girl Blood Sport
Description: Chaos depicts assassins hosting a lethal tournament luring aspiring models. A vengeful woman threatens them as they turn on each other in this blood-soaked nightmare inspired by true events, cautioning about dangers in freelance modeling.

Title: Poseidon Rex
Description: A small, secluded island off the coast of Belize suddenly finds itself terrorized by a deadly predator from the planet's distant past when deep sea divers accidentally awaken an ancient evil.

Title: A Dirty Carnival
Description: A small time thug collecting debts for the local triad is torn between his criminal aspirations and his devotion to family.

Title: Ghidorah: The Three-Headed Monster
Description: A detective protects a princess who prophecies Earth's destruction by a powerful space monster; the world's only hope being if Mothra can persuade Godzilla and Rodan to unite and save the planet.

Title: Prisoners of the Lost Universe
Description: Three people are transported into a parallel reality, where they find they must use modern technology, but medieval weapons, in order to save the citizenry from a murderous warlord.

Title: Those Daring Young Men in Their Jaunty Jalopies
Description: An international car rally across Europe is complicated by smuggling, cheating, love at first sight, etc. etc.

Title: Superman/Batman: Public Enemies
Description: When Lex Luthor gets elected US President, he uses the threat of an oncoming kryptonite meteor striking Earth as a rationale to frame Superman.

Title: Detonator
Description: A train with hostages is stolen in Bremen, Germany. It's heading south through Europe with a nuclear bomb. A UN crime-fighting task force is in charge of stopping it in cooperation with local military and police.

Title: Kennedy
Description: An insomniac ex-cop who dwells in different circumstances looking for redemption. The ex-cop, who is presumed dead for a long time, operates secretly for the corrupt system.

Title: Madha Gaja Raja
Description: Childhood friends gather for a wedding celebration, but their joyous reunion takes an unexpected turn, forcing them to confront a crisis while navigating personal struggles.

Title: Gintama: The Final
Description: The concluding movie to the Gintama anime series.

Title: Big Boobs Buster
Description: A young woman is rejected due to her flat chest, and seeks revenge on all the well endowed girls around her.

Title: Run All Night 2
Description: Jimmy races against time to rescue his estranged son from peril, leading to a high-stakes confrontation with dangerous adversaries.

Title: Standoff
Description: A young girl photographs an assassin killing 4 at a cemetery. He wants no witnesses. Carter, a veteran in a farmhouse, is all standing between him and the girl.

Title: Mindhorn
Description: A has-been actor best known for playing the title character in the 1980s detective series "Mindhorn" must work with the police when a serial killer says that he will only speak with Detective Mindhorn, whom he believes to be a real person.

Title: Decibel
Description: The story unfolds when a bomb that responds to sound is discovered at the center of the city.

Title: Jesus Christ Vampire Hunter
Description: Jesus returns to Earth to judge humanity but first he must team up with a Mexican fighter to combat vampires who walk during the day.

Title: The Hyperions
Description: In 1960, Professor Ruckus invented the Titan badge - a device that enables humans to have a particular superpower. Cut to 1979 when two of the original superheroes are all grown up and want their Titan badges back.

Title: Retro
Description: A gangster tries to avoid violence and lead a peaceful life after vowing to his wife.

Title: Wonder Woman
Description: A modern man's trespass of the island of the Amazons enables an imprisoned war god to escape and Princess Diana wins the responsibility to recapture him.

Title: Double Trouble
Description: Muscle-bound twins try to smash a jewel smuggling ring.

Title: Helga, la louve de Stilberg
Description: Helga moves the action to South America, where she lords over a castle of female political prisoners, who are stripped and tortured at whim.

Title: Year of the Gun
Description: In 1978, a journalist and a photojournalist, both young Americans, had a close encounter with Red Brigades terrorists in Rome.

Title: Little Dixie
Description: Doc, a former special forces operative, facilitates a fragile truce in secrecy between the state governor and a Mexican drug cartel. But when it breaks down, the cartel's hatchet man sets his vengeful sights on Doc's daughter.

Title: Agneepath
Description: A young boy's father is lynched before his eyes; fifteen years later he returns home for revenge.

Title: Blackjack
Description: Dolph Lundgren plays Jack Devlin, a U.S Marshal who protects high-profile clients when it comes to a matter of security.

Title: Tokyo Revengers 2: Bloody Halloween - Decisive Battle
Description: Driven by a single-minded determination to protect his friends and save Hinata, Takemichi Hanagaki enters a gang war with the hope of altering the course of fate and creating a better future for everyone.

Title: In Like Flynn
Description: The adventurous life of young Errol Flynn in Australia before he became a famous Hollywood actor.

Title: The Dinosaur Project
Description: A British expedition formed by the lead researcher Jonathan Marchant, his assistant, a doctor and a TV crew, travels to Congo to seek evidence of a dinosaur.

Title: Real Steel 2
Description: Plot is unknown.

Title: Cyborg 2087
Description: Earth's civilization of the future sends a cyborg back to the 1960s to change the future.

Title: Laser Mission
Description: Action superstar Brandon Lee portrays rebellious government agent Michael Gold who is sent on a desperate mission to a Soviet-controlled African nation in order to uncover a top-secret laser weapons operation and destroy it.

Title: Les Lyonnais
Description: After growing up in a poor gypsy camp, Edmond Vidal, aka Momon, has retained a sense of family, unfailing loyalty and pride in his origins. Most of all, he has remained friends with Serge Suttel, with whom he first discovered prison life - for stealing cherries. The two of them inevitably got involved in organized crime. The team they formed, the Gang Des Lyonnais, made them the most notorious armed robbers of the early 1970s. Their irresistible rise ended in 1974 with a spectacular arrest. Today, as he nears 60, Momon would like to forget that part of his life. He has found peace by retiring from the "business". He tends to his wife Janou, who suffered so in the past, and to his children and grandchildren, all of whom have great respect for this man of simple and universal values, so clear-headed and full of kindness. But then Serge Suttel, who has disowned nothing of his past, comes back into the picture.

Title: Pawn
Description: A petty robbery spirals into a tense hostage situation after three gunmen hold up a diner that's a front for the mob.

Title: Dead Leaves
Description: Two aliens awaken on Earth with no recollection of their past and embark on a devastating crime spree but are sent to an infamous lunar penitentiary named Dead Leaves.

Title: Sugar Hill
Description: When her boyfriend is murdered by mobsters, Sugar Hill decides not to get mad, but BAD. She asks the voodoo priestess Mama Maitresse to summon Baron Samedi, the Lord of the Dead, to help her gain a gruesome revenge. In exchange for Sugar's soul, the Dark Master raises up a zombie army to do her bidding. The bad guys who think they got away clean are about to find out that they are DEAD wrong.

Title: Timerider: The Adventure of Lyle Swann
Description: A maverick motorbike racer wanders into a top-secret time-travel research test site which unintentionally teleports him to the mid-1800s and ends up having to fight violent outlaws for his survival.

Title: When Eight Bells Toll
Description: In a vein similar to the James Bond movies, British Agent Philip Calvert (Sir Anthony Hopkins) is on a mission to determine the whereabouts of a ship that disappeared near the coast of Scotland.

Title: Keluang Man
Description: A psychiatric patient named Borhan transforms into a masked vigilante superhero.

Title: Women in Cellblock 9
Description: Somewhere in the jungles of South America mercenaries stop a truck which has allegedly loaded fruit. The cargo turns out to be six young women. Apprehended and handed over to the custody of the local women's prison.

Title: Artemis
Description: Jazz is a porter and part-time smuggler in the lunar city of Artemis. Trying to make a little extra money, she accepts a less than legal job but ends up involved in a much bigger crime.

Title: The Veil
Description: Wounded warrior dude comes across a minuscule tribe in hiding. War is upon them so they must go out and find it.

Title: Mummy Shark
Description: In an Egyptian pyramid, researchers uncover a mummified alien shark. A mystic revives the creature, unleashing it on the exploration team.

Title: Exterminator 2
Description: The flamethrower-wielding vigilante John Eastland returns to rid New York City of a drug lord and his gang.

Title: Repligator
Description: Army experimentation with transporter devices accidentally turns people into alligators.

Title: The Female Executioner
Description: Martine is a tough female cop trying to solve the kidnapping of a young girl by a gang of pornographers.

Title: The Package
Description: A courier for a local crime lord must deliver a mysterious package while being chased by a horde of unusual gangsters.

Title: The Chaperone
Description: An ex-con on the run from his criminal past hides out from those he ratted on by chaperoning a field trip to New Orleans.

Title: Megamind: The Button of Doom
Description: On Megamind's first day as a hero, his most evil invention comes to life and he must put a stop to it.

Title: Prisoner of War
Description: A British SAS officer during World War II is captured and forced to fight in a Japanese internment camp.

Title: Salting the Battlefield
Description: MI5 officer Johnny Worricker and Margot Tyrell are on the run together across Europe. But Worricker knows his only chance of resolving his problems is to return home and confront his nemesis, the prime minister.

Title: Disorganized Crime
Description: Career criminal Frank plans a bank heist and sends for his buddies to help pull the job. Before his buddies arrive, he's caught, forcing his cohorts to pull the job alone. Frank soon escapes, setting off a search by the bumbling cops.

Title: Van Helsing: The London Assignment
Description: In this animated prequel to Van Helsing (2004), Van Helsing travels to Victorian London to catch the mysterious, inhuman serial killer, Mr. Hyde.

Title: Adiós, Sabata
Description: Sabata helps a band of Mexican revolutionaries steal a wagon-load of gold from the occupying Austrian forces of Emperor Maximilian I.

Title: Climax
Description: Diane and her boyfriend, ignore warnings and venture into a desert, facing treacherous situations. Their search for safety in a town fails as more perils emerge. Their ordeal focuses on uncovering the mastermind and surviving.

Title: Maximum Ride
Description: A flock of winged children mount a rescue plan when wolf-boys abduct their youngest member and return her to the militarized institution that created them all.

Title: The Dirty Dozen: Next Mission
Description: During WW2, American General Worden orders Major Reisman to pick 12 soldiers from the military prison for the dangerous mission of killing a Nazi General.

Title: Day Zero
Description: When society breaks down due to a violent outbreak that turns victims into undead monsters, a former elite soldier breaks out of jail to find his family.

Title: King
Description: Mentor and disciple embark on a perilous journey, pushing their survival skills to the limit against overwhelming odds and unforgiving environments.

Title: The Jurassic Games
Description: In the near future, 10 death row convicts are forced to compete in a virtual reality game that pits them against dinosaurs and each other.

Title: The Point Men
Description: A Korean diplomat is dispatched to Afghanistan when a group of South Korean tourists is taken hostage by the Taliban. When all measures fail and one hostage is killed, he is forced to team up with a special agent to rescue the survivors.

Title: Predator World
Description: Luxurious space-cruiser 'TITAN 1C' is hit by a meteor storm, allowing a deadly alien life-form to board. The plot revolves around the passengers' struggle to survive the extraterrestrial threat onboard the damaged ship.

Title: The Sword of Doom
Description: Through his unconscionable actions against others, a sociopath samurai builds a trail of vendettas that follow him closely.

Title: The Don Is Dead
Description: After his mistress is savagely beaten up a Mafia leader goes after the killer with a bloody vengeance. Soon after the hunt begins, a gang war ensues.

Title: Against the Wall
Description: Based on the true story of the Attica Prison uprising of 1971.

Title: Manhunt
Description: Accused of heinous crimes he didn't commit, a prosecutor sets out on a mission to clear his name.

Title: A Breed Apart
Description: Violet, a rebel seeking abandoned dogs on a remote island, finds herself in a harrowing situation filled with terror and adrenaline-fueled chaos.

Title: Come Out Fighting
Description: Set during World War 2, a squad of American Army soldiers are sent on a mission behind lines to locate their missing commanding officer.

Title: Mistress of Souls
Description: The valuable secret contained in a lost formula pits a beautiful woman against a seemingly unconquerable force. But can she save herself or lose her very soul?

Title: Samurai I: Musashi Miyamoto
Description: Depicts the early life of the legendary warrior Musashi Miyamoto; his years as an aspiring warrior, an outlaw and finally a true samurai.

Title: The Hitman
Description: A Cop goes undercover as a Hitman to bring down a criminal organization.

Title: Space Raiders
Description: A futuristic, sensitive tale of adventure and confrontation when a 10 year old boy is accidentally kidnapped by a spaceship filled with a motley crew of space pirates.

Title: Knight Rider 2010
Description: Loosely based on the popular television series of the 80's, this movie brings the story into an apocalyptic time and a new "KITT".

Title: Rampage: Capital Punishment
Description: A man takes over a TV station and holds a number of hostages as a political platform to awaken humanity, instead of money.

Title: Asura
Description: A shady cop finds himself in over his head when he gets caught between Internal Affairs and the city's corrupt mayor.

Title: Cosmoball
Description: An enormous spaceship hovers over Earth-this is a stadium, which hosts sports events that resemble soccer but at mind-boggling speeds. The name of the game is cosmoball.

Title: Major
Description: Based on the life of Major Sandeep Unnikrishnan, who fought during the November 2008 Mumbai attacks.

Title: Normal
Description: Centers on a temporary small-town sheriff who uncovers dark mysteries after a local bank robbery.

Title: Ultimate Avengers II
Description: When the Chitauri invaders are sighted in the African kingdom of Wakanda, the Avengers covertly enter the advanced nation to investigate.

Title: Junk Head
Description: In a distant future, humanity has lost its ability to reproduce. An expedition is sent to an underground city where artificial humanoids are still fertile.

Title: Catch Me If You Can
Description: A hotshot car racer persuades the class president of a small Minnesota high school to gamble on illegal car races to raise money for their school facing closure.

Title: The Story of Robin Hood and His Merrie Men
Description: When King Richard the Lionheart leaves England to lead a crusade to the Holy Land, his treacherous brother conspires to bring himself to power.

Title: SGT. Will Gardner
Description: A troubled Iraq War veteran struggling to reintegrate into society sets out on a cross-country journey with the hope of reuniting with his young son.

Title: Renaissance
Description: A young gene researcher, Ilona, is kidnapped in a future Paris. Police Captain Karas and his team are in charge of finding her.

Title: Raptor
Description: When Sheriff Jim Tanner investigates a string of unexplained and grisly killings, he uncovers a prehistoric terror.

Title: Dragonheart Vengeance
Description: Lukas, a young farmer whose family is killed by savage raiders in the countryside, sets out on an epic quest for revenge, forming an unlikely trio with a majestic dragon and a swashbuckling, sword-fighting mercenary, Darius.

Title: Enforcement
Description: Jens and Mike, two police officers on routine patrol, find themselves trapped in a maze of buildings when unrest spreads.

Title: Hard Kill
Description: The work of billionaire tech CEO Donovan Chalmers (Willis) is so valuable that he hires mercenaries to protect it, and a terrorist group kidnaps his daughter just to get it.

Title: AmeriGeddon
Description: A family of dedicated patriots living in the United States decide to defend their country against a terrorist organization that shuts down electricity in America and tries to take over the nation.

Title: American Ninja 3: Blood Hunt
Description: A man newly trained in the martial arts must save his trainer from experimentation.

Title: Eat My Dust
Description: Darlene's into going fast and Hoover's into Darlene, but when they both get into a red-hot race car, the reckless fun accelerates into a trunkful of hot pursuits.

Title: Baaghi
Description: A martial artist faces his biggest test when he has to travel to Bangkok to rescue the woman he loves from the clutches of his romantic rival.

Title: 1968 Tunnel Rats
Description: Halfway into the Vietnam War (1959-1975), a special US combat unit is sent to hunt and kill the Viet Cong soldiers in man-to-man combat in the endless tunnels underneath the jungle of Vietnam.

Title: Altered Carbon: Resleeved
Description: On the planet Latimer, reawakened Takeshi Kovacs must protect a teenage tattooist named Holly while investigating the death of a yakuza boss alongside Gina, a strangely familiar no-nonsense CTAC agent.

Title: Shootfighter II
Description: Shingo and the boys (Nick and Ruben) are blackmailed into helping Rawlins infiltrate an underground shootfighting ring in Miami

Title: Love and Bullets
Description: Arizona cop is sent to Switzerland to bring in the girlfriend of a dangerous mobster so she can testify against him. The mobster sends someone too - assassins.

Title: The Human Tornado
Description: Dolemite flees to California, where he helps Queen Bee and her Kung Fu prostitutes battle a local gangster.

Title: The Great Texas Dynamite Chase
Description: Explosive drama and action when two sexy girls go on a bank robbing binge.

Title: Seized
Description: After a former special forces agent's son is kidnapped, he must wipe out three dangerous crime syndicates, if he wants to see his son alive again.

Title: City Hunter
Description: Nicky Larson, the best private investigator in the business, is called for a high-risk mission: to recover the perfume of Cupid, a perfume that would make irresistible the one who uses it.

Title: Bonus Trip
Description: Two FBI agents defy orders while investigating a case. They team up with a translator to rescue her father and expose a global conspiracy. Along the way, they face humorous situations, unexpected twists, and life-threatening dangers.

Title: The Alamo: Thirteen Days to Glory
Description: Against orders and with no help of relief Texas patriots led by William Travis, Jim Bowie and Davy Crockett defend the Alamo against overwhelming Mexican forces.

Title: Sherlock
Description: Early in his crime-solving career, Sherlock Holmes attempts to prevent Moriarty from cornering the heroin market.

Title: Agastya - Chapter 1
Description: Saurya is haunted by a difficult past and grapples with his troubled mind. After a year, his brother embarks on a quest to find him. A touching story unfolds as Nisan delves into Saurya's history.

Title: Monkey King: Hero Is Back
Description: The all-powerful Monkey King was imprisoned by the Gods for 500 years, but when a child releases him from his curse, the Monkey King must now save an innocent village from the evil Mountain Lord and his monstrous army.

Title: Kahar: Kapla High Council
Description: Set in 2005, Kahar, a socially invisible man, volunteers for Pilihanraya to protect his friend. Initially noble, his actions lead him down a path of malevolence and tyranny, risking his family's legacy.

Title: All-Star Superman
Description: After being poisoned by sun radiation, a dying Superman decides to fulfill his lifelong dreams while Lex Luthor has his own agenda.

Title: Sworn to Justice
Description: After attackers kill her sister and nephew, a female psychologist becomes a defense witness by day and an avenger by night.

Title: Fairytale in New York
Description: Set on Christmas Eve in NYC, a cab driver takes one last ride before reuniting with his estranged son. After an encounter with criminals, he relentlessly pursues retrieving his child's priceless gift.

Title: Righting Wrongs
Description: Yuen Biao plays Jason Chan, a lawyer angry at the way the law seems to protect the bad guys. He decides to take the law into his own hands when a key witness and his entire family are murdered. But Cindy Si is soon on his case and it all spirals into a situation only a few will survive.

Title: The Sea Chase
Description: As World War II begins, German freighter Captain Karl Ehrlich tries to get his ship back to Germany through a gauntlet of Allied warships.

Title: Re:Born
Description: A legend covert soldier with a mysterious past now decides to once again unleash his beast inside of him to stand up for what he cares about.

Title: Eega
Description: Nani loves Bindu but is killed by a jealous Sudeep, who lusts after Bindu. Nani is reincarnated as a fly and decides to avenge his death. He teams up with Bindu to make Sudeep's life a living hell.

Title: Wizards of the Lost Kingdom
Description: When evil screams throughout the world. When all the galaxies converge. When all that's fair and fine seems lost. A Hero will emerge.

Title: Vault
Description: In 1975, a group of small time criminals attempt to pull off the biggest heist in American history: stealing over $30 million from the Mafia in the smallest state in the union, Rhode Island.

Title: Return of the Living Dead: Necropolis
Description: A group of teenagers, in an attempt to rescue their friend from an evil corporation, end up inadvertently releasing a horde of bloodthirsty zombies.

Title: Max 2: White House Hero
Description: Max is assigned to the White House while Charlie, the secret service dog, is on maternity leave. He meets TJ, a 12 year old boy, who is the President's son. Due to his father's high profile, he is trying hard to fit in and lead a normal life. During a state visit by the Russian President and his daughter, Alexandra (Alex), TJ is asked to accompany her, during their stay. TJ befriends Alex, but when they get into trouble, Max comes to the rescue.

Title: Promare
Description: A futuristic firefighting mecha service is created to protect the world.

Title: Project A 2
Description: Dragon is now transferred to be the police head of Sai Wan district, and has to contend with a gangster kingpin, anti-Manchu revolutionaries, some runaway pirates, Manchu Loyalists and a corrupt Police Superintendent.

Title: Almighty Thor
Description: When a demon god steals the Hammer of Invincibility, Thor strikes a mighty blow to get it back.

Title: Breakout
Description: When his stepson, Daniel, is framed and sentenced to 25 years in a foreign country, Reynolds makes a daring jailbreak to save him and must overcome an overzealous prison warden in a race against time to avoid capture and flee the country.

Title: The Day Everything Changed
Description: Mario, used to be a man who had planned a happy future with his wife; until one night, a robbery ends up taking her life. From that moment on, his only objective is now to avenge on those who took away his happiness.

Title: Green Lantern: Beware My Power
Description: Recently discharged Marine sniper John Stewart is at a crossroads in his life, one which is only complicated by receiving an extraterrestrial ring which grants him the powers of the Green Lantern of Earth.

Title: Sharktopus vs. Whalewolf
Description: When a mad scientist hybridizes the genes of a killer whale and a wolf, this creates the whalewolf and, once again, it is up to the sharktopus to stop it.

Title: Enemies Closer
Description: Deep within a forest on the U.S.-Canadian border, two sworn enemies must work together to escape a ruthless drug cartel hell-bent on retrieving a drug shipment which went missing there.

Title: The Spook Who Sat by the Door
Description: A black man plays 'uncle Tom' in order to gain access to CIA training, then uses that knowledge to plot a new American revolt.

Title: Cleopatra Jones
Description: During the 1970s, U.S. Special Agent Cleopatra Jones proves to be an invaluable asset to the local police forces in the war on drugs.

Title: Dragon Ball Z: Wrath of the Dragon
Description: The Z-fighters find themselves in the middle of another extraterrestrial conflict, which includes a sword-wielding warrior named Tapion, a wizard and an enormous monster named Hirudegarn.

Title: James Bond 007 at the Movies
Description: See the sights, sounds and high tech action - See the world's most infamous Villains, See the unbelievable Women and the dashing Roger Moore and Sean Connery playing James Bond 007 with a licence to kill. They dance for him, They yearn for him, They die for him.

Title: Jesse Stone: Benefit of the Doubt
Description: Jesse Stone comes out of involuntary retirement after the new chief who replaced him was blown up, along with another officer in their police car. Jesse is forced to solve the crime on his own since all the other officers have quit.

Title: Sarileru Neekevvaru
Description: An army major sent to Kurnool to give company to his injured colleague's family ends up locking horns with a corrupt minister who is targeting the family.

Title: Justice Society: World War II
Description: The Justice Society of America, a group of heroes aiding the allies in World War 2, acquire an ally from the future who sends them on an adventure that changes history.

Title: Lost Bullet 2: Back for More
Description: After the death of Charras, Lino and Julia took over and form the new narcotic unit. Determined to find the murderers of his brother and his mentor, Lino continues his hunt and won't let anyone get in his way.

Title: In Enemy Hands
Description: When American submarine Swordfish is torpedoed the survivors are picked up by a passing German U-boat but an outbreak of meningitis threatens all aboard.

Title: Nameless Gangster: Rules of the Time
Description: On the verge of being fired, a corrupt customs official finds a haul of drugs and teams up with a vicious gangster to become the most powerful crime partnership in Busan.

Title: Kung Fu Panda: Secrets of the Furious Five
Description: Ordered to teach a martial arts class of rambunctious bunny kittens, Po tells stories of each of the Furious Five's pasts.

Title: Croc!
Description: Deep in the English countryside, Lisa and Charlie prepare for their wedding at a Tudor mansion. But an angry crocodile lies in wait, determined to ruin their big day.

Title: Echo Boomers
Description: Based on a true story, five college graduates decide the best way to get back at the unfair economy and live the life they've always wanted is to steal from Chicago's richest and give to themselves.

Title: Soulcatcher
Description: A military contractor hired to seize a weapon that turns people into savage killers seeks revenge when his brother falls victim to the device.

Title: Crimson Rivers 2: Angels of the Apocalypse
Description: Pierre Niemans faces the threat of the apocalypse while investigating a series of ritual murders.

Title: Superman
Description: Superman comes to Earth as a child and grows up to be his home's first superhero with his first major challenge being to oppose The Spider Lady.

Title: Parallels
Description: A mysterious building is the gateway to infinite parallel Earths.

Title: The Man Who Feels No Pain
Description: It is a story of a young boy Surya who has a rare condition of Congenital Insensitivity to pain meaning he can not feel pain, and he sets out to learn martial arts and hunt down muggers.

Title: Tomcat Angels
Description: Four women graduate the US Navel Top Gun academy. When 2 of them are promptly shot down on their first Gulf assignment, the other 2 and their instructors head out to rescue them. Love and stock navel air footage is had by all.

Title: Sonny and Jed
Description: A vulgar Mexican social bandit reluctantly takes on an aspiring young outlaw as his partner in crime and love, all while the duo is pursued by a vengeful sheriff and bounty hunters.

Title: Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - Mt. Natagumo Arc
Description: Tanjiro teams up with Zenitsu and Inosuke to investigate missing person cases on the mountain Natagumo. They slowly begin to realize the entire mountain is being controlled by a family of Demon spider creatures.

Title: Walker, Texas Ranger: Trial by Fire
Description: Walker investigates a murder connected with a missing government weapon. In addition, he tries to track down a teen on the run from a crime syndicate.

Title: Superman: Unbound
Description: Superman and Supergirl take on the cybernetic Brainiac, who boasts that he possesses "the knowledge and strength of 10,000 worlds."

Title: Jatra
Description: An innocent, poor and hardworking man Phadindra Timsina (Bipin Karki) finds a sack full of 3 Crores Nepalese rupees stolen from a bank. He then consults with his 2 friends Jayas (Rabindra Singh Baniya) and Munna (Rabindra Jha) to make that money white.

Title: Goliathon
Description: A greedy Hong Kong businessman captures a 50-foot-tall ape from the Himalayas and puts it on display, but it escapes and goes on a rampage.

Title: Don
Description: Vijay is recruited by a police officer to masquerade as his lookalike Don, the leader of an international gang of smugglers. Things go wrong when the officer is killed and Vijay is left to fend for himself.

Title: Raging Phoenix
Description: A violent gang is abducting and killing women around Thailand. Sanim and his friends, having had loved ones abducted, have joined together to break the gang of kidnappers. In a botched kidnap attempt, Deu is saved by Sanim's crew. After learning their unique martial arts style, Deu helps lure the gang into an epic battle to save the women across Thailand.

Title: The Survivalist
Description: A year and a half after the fall of civilization due to a viral outbreak, a former FBI agent is forced to protect a young woman immune to the disease from a dangerous gang leader hunting her.

Title: Thirst
Description: When a group of wayward teens arrive at a desert boot camp, with no communication, and nowhere to run to, they realize their only chance for survival is to fight for their lives.

Title: Pimp Bullies
Description: Five suspects holding a piece of the truth behind an unsolved crime.

Title: The Soldier
Description: Terrorists take over a plutonium bomb and threaten to detonate it in a Saudi Arabian oil field. A special anti-terrorist unit is sent in to stop them.

Title: Too Late the Hero
Description: A reluctant hero, American Lieutenant Sam Lawson, is seconded to a motley British unit tasked with destroying a Japanese radio on a Philippine island.

Title: Spare Parts
Description: While travelling on their first American tour, Ms. 45, an all-girl punk band, is drugged and kidnapped. They awaken to find their limbs removed and replaced with crude weaponry, and are forced to fight as Gladiators for a sadistic town.

Title: Hot and Deadly
Description: Carefree electrician Tom Cathral is recruited by The Company, and is quickly offered a full-time promotion to join the Retrievers, an elite squad of crooked secret operatives. His refusal to kill botches his first mission, making Tom The Company's new target.

Title: The Secret Invasion
Description: In 1943, a group of hardened criminals is pardoned on the condition it accepts a mission to free a captive Italian general from the clutches of the Nazis.

Title: Last Passenger
Description: A small group of everyday passengers on a speeding London commuter train battle their warped driver who has a dark plan for everyone on-board.

Title: Off the Grid
Description: A brilliant scientist goes on the run instead of weaponizing his invention

Title: Ramayana: The Legend of Prince Rama
Description: An anime adaptation of the Hindu epic the Ramayana, where Lord Ram combats the wicked king Ravana.

Title: Khuda Haafiz: Chapter 2 - Agni Pariksha
Description: Sameer and Nargis, after overcoming all odds, find a ray of sunshine when little Nandini enters their lives and their family is complete; But their happiness is short-lived. In a bizarre twist of fate, Nandini goes missing.

Title: C.C. & Company
Description: A motorcycle rebel saves a woman from his gang and fights an outlaw guru for supremacy.

Title: Naruto Shippûden: The Movie 3: Inheritors of the Will of Fire
Description: Ninjas with bloodline limits begin disappearing in all the countries and blame points toward the fire nation. By Tsunade's order, Kakashi is sacrificed to prevent an all out war. Naruto fights through friends and foes to prevent his death.

Title: The Lady of Heaven
Description: Two stories separated by 1400 years. After losing his mother in the midst of a war-torn country, an Iraqi child, learns the importance and power of patience by discovering the historical story of Lady Fatima and her suffering.

Title: Liger
Description: A story about martial arts, dreams and star crossed lovers. Liger is an MMA fighter who trains hard and rises up the ranks with one goal in mind, to fight like his idol, world renowned MMA fighter Mark Anderson and get noticed by him.

Title: King of Kotha
Description: In a crime-infested town, Kannan bhai and his gang are the reigning powers. To combat this reign and seek revenge, Inspector Shahul tactfully plots the return of the 'King', leading to a transformative turn of events.

Title: The Myth
Description: Archeologist Jack keeps having reoccurring dreams of a past life, where he is the great general Meng Yi, who is sworn to protect a princess named Ok-Soo. Jack decides to go investigate everything with his friend William.

Title: Air Force
Description: The crew of an Air Force bomber arrives in Pearl Harbor in the aftermath of the Japanese attack on December 7, 1941, and is sent on to Manila to help with the defense of the Philippines.

Title: Bad Girls Dormitory
Description: Inmates at a women's prison run by a corrupt warden and her gang of sadistic guards plan a breakout.

Title: House of the Dead 2
Description: A virus breaks out at a university and people start to become zombies. After 29 days, a team of AMS scientists and soldiers are sent in to deal with the problem. But while they search, things go wrong.

Title: The Navigator: A Medieval Odyssey
Description: Men seeking relief from the Black Death, guided by a boy's vision, dig a tunnel from 14th century England to 20th century New Zealand.

Title: The Blue Knight
Description: Bumper Morgan is a veteran Los Angeles Police Department street cop. He is due to retire after twenty years on the job, but is not letting up on the criminal element on his beat.

Title: Winners & Sinners
Description: Fresh from prison, five friends try to stay crime free but inadvertently find themselves caught in a Triad war.

Title: Aladin
Description: Since he was a child, Aladin Chatterjee has been teased for his fairytale name. As a college student he follows his namesake's footsteps; unleashing genie Genius and wooing exchange student Jasmine. But the evil Ringmaster approaches.

Title: The Blade
Description: A swordsmith trains his friend's orphaned son. The boy seeks revenge for his father's murder but loses an arm rescuing the swordsmith's daughter. A hermit girl nurses him, and he learns swordsmanship with his father's broken sword.

Title: Dangerously Close
Description: A rebel without a cause at an elite uptight High School discovers some of his classmates have formed an even more elite clique hell-bent on ridding the school of what they deem to be its undesirables because of ethnicity, politics, etc.

Title: Extreme Ops
Description: While filming an advertisement, some extreme sports enthusiasts unwittingly stop a group of terrorists.

Title: Metro
Description: Terror strikes the underground train system in Moscow in the form of a flood from a collapsed tunnel.

Title: Deaner '89
Description: A hilarious headbanger finally makes it after struggling for decades, revealing it was all because of a childhood incident when the dark forces of heavy metal reached out from the grave.

Title: No Way Out
Description: A mob hitman wants to retire, but his bosses don't think that's a good idea. Complications and many bloody shootouts ensue.

Title: The Underneath: In Fortune's Shadow
Description: A knight of the underworld has three days to find his adversary and his answer.

Title: Memorial Day
Description: Memorial Day, 1993. When 13-year-old Kyle Vogel discovers the World War II footlocker belonging to his grandfather, Bud, everyone tells Kyle to put it back. Luckily, he ignores them. Although Bud has never talked about the war, he finds himself striking a deal with his grandson: Kyle can pick any three souvenirs, and Bud will tell him the stories behind each one. Memorial Day not only takes us on a journey into Bud's complicated wartime past, but also into Kyle's wartime future. As the two men share parallel experiences in combat, they come to realize how that magical day on the porch shaped both of their lives.

Title: The Land That Time Forgot
