Description: Debt-ridden pacifist Richard Fyre is propositioned to return to his abandoned mercenary ways by flamboyant zealot, Priest, to eliminate his international competition in exchange for a clean slate.

Title: The Berlin File
Description: Jong-seong, a North Korean ghost agent, interrupts an illegal arms sale in Berlin. A notorious North Korean agent tests the loyalties of everyone involved as Jong-Seong prepares to make the ultimate sacrifice.

Title: Crossed
Description: Follows a group of survivors dealing with an apocalyptic pandemic that causes its victims to carry out their most evil thoughts.

Title: Damn the Defiant!
Description: On the H.M.S. Defiant, during the French Revolutionary War, fair Captain Crawford is locked in a battle of wills against his cruel second-in-command Lieutenant Scott-Padget, whose heavy-handed command style pushes the crew to mutiny.

Title: Heroes of the East
Description: A Chinese man marries a Japanese martial artist, and they begin to bicker over which country has the better martial arts. It reaches a point where he has to go against Japanese martial artists in different styles to prove who's the best.

Title: Cats & Dogs 3: Paws Unite
Description: Gwen the Cat and Roger the Dog are secret agents who covertly protect and save the world without humans ever finding out. Their partnership is due to the Great Truce, which has stopped dog and cat hostility for a decade.

Title: Drive
Description: A notorious thief allies with a street racer for a grand heist involving an elaborate game of deceit with authorities, who have their own dirty secrets.

Title: The Ghazi Attack
Description: A Pakistani submarine, Ghazi plans to secretly attack Vizag port. For doing so, it has to get past Indian submarine S21.

Title: Kaho Naa... Pyaar Hai
Description: A young girl meets the doppelganger of her deceased boyfriend and now has a chance to find the people who have murdered him.

Title: Superwho?
Description: A struggling actor who seems doomed to lead the life of a loser. When finally gets a lead role as a superhero named "Badman," he feels like everything is possible but fate strikes again.

Title: Captain Apache
Description: During the presidency of Ulysses S. Grant, the full-blooded Native American Cavalry officer, Captain Apache, finds himself entangled in a well-planned conspiracy, while on a mission to investigate the death of the Indian Commissioner.

Title: Route 666
Description: A federal witness runs away and a team of government agents track him down, but when they take a shortcut on the return trip, they're attacked by zombies.

Title: Tiger on Beat
Description: A seasoned cop and his rookie partner are a pair of mismatched partners in this Hong Kong action-comedy in the style of 'Lethal Weapon'. The wacky twosome are up in arms as they try to solve the murder of a heroin trafficker.

Title: Timecop: The Berlin Decision
Description: A Time Enforcement Commission police officer (Jason Scott Lee) travels back in time to prevent a criminal mastermind from gaining control of the future.

Title: Dragon Inn
Description: When the children of an executed General are pursued in 1457 China, some heroic martial arts swordsmen intervene.

Title: Power Rangers Super Megaforce: The Legendary Battle
Description: The Emperor unleashes another massive attack on Earth and nearly defeats the Rangers, but against all odds, they remain defiant and are rewarded with the help of all the Legendary Rangers from years past.

Title: Shaft in Africa
Description: Private investigator John Shaft is recruited to go undercover to break up a modern slavery ring where young Africans are lured to Paris to do chain-gang work.

Title: Legion
Description: In the year 2036 a special forces team led by Major Agatha Doyle, formed from death-row prisoners, takes on a mission. A former war hero on death row is offered the chance at a pardon if he joins the team to infiltrate an enemy facility.

Title: Assignment K
Description: A British Agent, posing as an executive of a toy company, tangles with East European spies in various European locales.

Title: Death Ring
Description: When ex-Special Forces agent Matt Collins wins a survivalist competition, he becomes "the toughest man alive" - perfect fodder for perverse millionaire Danton Vachs, whose annual manhunt attracts the most vicious killers in the world.

Title: Art of Eight Limbs
Description: A US agent goes undercover at a martial arts training camp which is suspected of being a cover for chemical weapons.

Title: Blood Games
Description: When an all girl baseball team beats a group of rowdy rednecks from a small town, they soon find themselves the prey in a deadly bounty hunt. Now they are playing for their lives. In HD.

Title: A Good Man
Description: A man leaves special forces and hides away as handyman in Bucharest. He befriends two sisters living next door. When the Russian mob threatens them, he takes action.

Title: Darkman III: Die Darkman Die
Description: When he double-crosses a drug kingpin, Darkman must free himself of his remote-control clutches.

Title: Vendetta
Description: A sexy stuntwoman gets herself thrown into prison to avenge the death of her sister.

Title: The Peacekeeper
Description: When a terrorist group steals the US President's personal communications computer for launching the US arsenal in case of war, only a heroic Major has the key to prevent a Presidential assassination or a nuclear holocaust.

Title: Bomber
Description: Bud "Bomber" Graziano (Bud Spencer) retired from boxing as heavyweight champion and has sworn to never fight again. While living his life on a ship he meets Jerry Cala' (Jerry Cala) who finds himself always in trouble due to his being as a Lombard punter. But this time he is in big trouble, setting himself unwittingly against a group of thugs who only obey orders from a new boxing champion who is widely talked about because of winning one fight after the other. When even Bomber later collides later with this big bloke named Rosco, Bomber's passion for boxing suddenly awakens. In fact, Bomber opens a gym for amateurs and begins to train promising young George. After organizing a fight where Rosco, being too strong, knocks out George, Bomber is on the verge of ruining everything he has painstakingly established and eventually decides to face big bloke Rosco in a fight himself.

Title: Paradox
Description: A tough Hong Kong cop's 16 y.o. daughter disappears in Pattaya. He goes to Thailand to find her and must deal with corrupt cops but an honest one helps him track down culprits involved in illegal organ trafficking.

Title: The Cutter
Description: A detective comes to the aid of an aged diamond cutter.

Title: Deathstroke: Knights & Dragons - The Movie
Description: Assassin Slade Wilson leads two lives: a relentless killer known as Deathstroke and a family man. Can he atone for the sins of the past-or will his family pay the ultimate price?

Title: The Yinyang Master
Description: Adaption of the phenomenon-level mobile game "Onmyoji" - film version with the same name that will bring the magnificent oriental fantasy world to life.

Title: The Amazing Screw-On Head
Description: A Civil War-era secret agent with an extraordinary special power serves under president Abraham Lincoln protecting America from supernatural foes. Unsold animated TV pilot adapted from a short comic book from the creator of Hellboy.

Title: Cannon for Cordoba
Description: In 1916, when a Mexican rebel steals cannons from the American army, General Pershing sends out a group of misfits to retrieve the stolen weapons.

Title: The Steel Helmet
Description: A ragtag group of American stragglers battles against superior Communist troops in an abandoned Buddhist temple during the Korean War.

Title: Jurassic Women
Description: A meteor shower causes a spaceship crash on a remote planet populated by beautiful and dangerous women as well as cavemen. All procreation has been forbidden as there is a war between man and woman. But when a woman and a astronaut falls in love, the spaceships jealous captain joins the cavemen and a fight ensues.

Title: Golden Years
Description: Retired couple Arthur and Martha take up bank robbery after their pensions are cut, refusing to accept the injustice of their circumstances.

Title: The Hard Corps
Description: An Army veteran assembles a team of bodyguards to protect a former boxer. Complications arise when the boxer suspects his sister may be romantically involved with the bodyguard.

Title: To Please a Lady
Description: A former war hero and midget car racer meets his match in a feisty reporter who blames his reckless tactics for an accidental racing death.

Title: Raavanan
Description: A bandit leader kidnaps the wife of the policeman who killed his sister, but later falls in love with her.

Title: Best of the Best 4: Without Warning
Description: When a girl fleeing Russian mobsters plants a stolen computer disk on Tommy Lee, the martial arts expert finds himself unwittingly thrust into his most harrowing adventure ever.

Title: Eagle
Description: A journalist uncovers the story of a ruthless assassin when she investigates a government cover up.

Title: Undercover Party Crasher
Description: In order to get evidence for her case and dismantle a criminal organization, an uptight undercover cop crashes a high school graduation trip to a party-heavy beach in Brazil.

Title: The Abductors
Description: Cheerleaders and models are kidnapped & sold by a white slavery ring. Female agent is sent to rescue them.

Title: Black Dawn
Description: Jonathan Cold returns, this time he goes undercover to stop a group of terrorists before they bomb Los Angeles.

Title: Cyber Tracker
Description: This is the future. A secret service agent is framed by his own and becomes the target of the seemingly indestructible Cyborg-Executioners.

Title: Walking the Edge
Description: A Los Angeles taxi driver picks up a woman in his cab, not knowing that she's on a suicidal revenge mission. He manages to escape with her before getting killed, but deranged gangsters are searching for them.

Title: The Front Line
Description: A drama centered on the Korean War's final battle that will determine the border between north and south.

Title: Jallikattu
Description: A portrait of a remote village where a buffalo escapes and causes a frenzy of ecstatic violence.

Title: Sasquatch Mountain
Description: A lonely tow-truck driver gets caught in a deadly struggle between a pair of bank robbers with a beautiful hostage, local cops, and a monster that has come down from the Arizona mountains to eat human flesh.

Title: One in the Chamber
Description: An assassin playing both sides in a Russian gang war becomes the target of an unknown enemy.

Title: Dragon Ball Z: Bardock - The Father of Goku
Description: The tale of Bardock, the father of Goku, and his rebellion against his master the mighty Frieza.

Title: Sarpatta Parambarai
Description: When Sarpatta Parambarai is challenged to a do-or-die match, will Kabilan, a young labourer, put on the gloves himself and lead his clan to victory, or be dissuaded by his disapproving mother and dangerous politics?

Title: Kill Switch
Description: A troubled detective travels to Memphis in order to track down a pair of serial killers.

Title: KA
Description: In a village where the sun sinks below the horizon by 3 PM, darkness creeps in early, bringing with it a chilling wave of inexplicable horrors.

Title: The Amsterdam Kill
Description: Ex-DEA agent Quinlan enters a labyrinth of deception and death as he tries to destroy a powerful Amsterdam-based drug cartel named 'Juliana'.

Title: Legendary Weapons of China
Description: A band of killers from an ailing kung fu and magic society are sent on a manhunt for a former member of the society, whose bad mouthing threatens its existence.

Title: Xtra Credit
Description: A troubled youth (Micah Alberti) has an affair with a seductive woman (Marina Black) whose husband is found murdered.

Title: She Never Died
Description: When a girl goes missing, a woman with a mysterious past tracks down the people responsible.

Title: Zindagi Zindabaad
Description: Full of potential in their youth, a man and his friends develop an addiction to hard drugs that eventually leads to a life of crime.

Title: Easy Money II: Hard to Kill
Description: Three years later, JW gets out of prison, but soon finds himself between the contending parties of his criminal past.

Title: Open Season
Description: Three young men take a young woman and a middleaged man to an isolated cabin, where they are terrorized in different ways.

Title: Baby Assassins: 2 Babies
Description: As teenage assassins Chisato and Mahiro are suspended by their guild due to a rules violation, they are hunted down by two brothers and fellow assassins looking to kill them for a large bounty.

Title: Sohni Mahiwal
Description: After being violently separated from the woman he loves, a young man must disguise himself in order to keep meeting her.

Title: Deadpool Movie in Lego
Description: A shot-for-shot remake of the 2016 movie, Deadpool, created entirely out of Lego.

Title: Duel of the Titans
Description: Twin brothers revolt against tyranny in pre-Roman Italy and then come to a parting of the ways as they lead their people toward the founding of a new city.

Title: The Day the Earth Stopped
Description: Hundreds of massive intergalactic robots appear in all of the world's major capitals with an ultimatum: Prove the value of human civilization or be destroyed.

Title: Iris: The Movie
Description: South Korean National Security Service normally deals with North Korea, but now NSS must deal with IRIS terrorists with a nuke.

Title: Rammbock: Berlin Undead
Description: Just when Michael arrives in Berlin to visit his ex-girlfriend Gabi, a terrible virus starts spreading across the city at a rapid pace, turning people into mindless homicidal maniacs. Much to Michael's concern, Gabi's not home; instead, he meets Harper, a teenage plumber's apprentice at work in her apartment block. Together, they manage to barricade themselves when raging hordes of infected people swarm the building. Surrounded by these thirsty zombies, Michael and Harper have their hands full to survive - and it will take all of their ingenuity to make their way out to try and find Gabi.

Title: Vampiras: The Brides
Description: Dracula's brides must reunite to stop a threats from their past, their sister Mina. With the help of a powerful cartel leader and an army of drug lords under her command, Mina throws Los Angeles into utter chaos, raging for blood.

Title: Rent-a-Cop
Description: Detective Tony is forced to retire and become a store rent-a-cop when his drug sting operation comes to a tragic end by a masked killer. He joins forces with a prostitute, the only one able to identify the killer, to bring him to justice.

Title: Nun of That
Description: Nun of That follows Sister Kelly Wrath as she transforms from a nun with a simple temper problem to a vengeful killer.

Title: The Necro Files
Description: A cannibal rapist rises from the grave as a flesh-eating zombie sex maniac. Two Seattle cops, a satanic cult and a flying demon fetus try to stop the lust-crazed ghoul before he can kill again.

Title: Hostage Radio
Description: A radio star experiences the worst night of his life when stalkers assault the radio station where he's working.

Title: Jurassic Shark
Description: When an oil company unwittingly unleashes a prehistoric shark from its icy prison, the Jurassic killer maroons a group of thieves and beautiful young female college students on an abandoned island.

Title: Mad Dog Morgan
Description: The true story of Irish outlaw Daniel Morgan, who is wanted, dead or alive, in Australia during the 1850s.

Title: Kabaneri of the Iron Fortress: The Battle of Unato
Description: The film chronicles the attempt of the team to take back Unato castle.

Title: Wonder Women
Description: While looking into the disappearance of a jai alai athlete, an insurance investigator is targeted by the sexy all-girl army of rogue transplant surgeon Dr. Tsu.

Title: Untitled Taika Waititi Star Wars Film
Description: The plot is unknown.

Title: Checkmate
Description: Six people are thrown together during an elaborate bank heist where any move can alter the outcome. Is it coincidence, or are they merely pawns in a much bigger game.

Title: The Final Master
Description: A Wing Chun master has to defeat 8 martial arts schools to open his own school, yet he has become a chess piece to the local power dynamics.

Title: Iron Warrior
Description: Ator and his brother are separated as children by the evil witch Phoedra. 18 years later, she takes over the kingdom with the help of a masked warrior. Ator rescues the rightful heir princess Janna, and they struggle to topple the witch.

Title: Tuck Jagadish
Description: In a village with greedy property fights among the families, Jagadish (Nani) carries on his father's legacy to reform all the property issues in his village while trying to reunite his family, which is also split due to property issues.

Title: Operation Cicero
Description: Ilyas Bazna works as a butler in the British Embassy in Turkey during World War II. After Bazna starts working as a German spy he experiences a series of unexpected events.

Title: Figures in a Landscape
Description: Two escapees are on the run in the wilderness of an unspecified country. Wherever they go, they are followed by a menacing black helicopter.

Title: The Pagan King: The Battle of Death
Description: On his deathbed, the reigning king bestows power to an unexpected heir who must find strength within himself to unite his people against the violent crusades which threaten their freedom.

Title: The Fallen
Description: The story of ordinary men during WWII as seen from three different points of View.

Title: Ghost in the Shell: SAC_2045 - Sustainable War
Description: In the year 2045, cybernetic mercenary Motoko Kusanagi returns to Section 9 to face a dangerous new threat: the posthumans. A feature-length recut of the first season of Ghost in the Shell: SAC_2045.

Title: Thunder in Paradise
Description: Terry "Hulk" Hogan stars as R. J. "Hurricane" Spencer who is an ex-Navy S. E. A. L. and confirmed bachelor struggling to make ends meet. In order to save his superboat THUNDER (and ultimately, his business) Spencer is forced into a marriage of convenience with the snobby Megan Whitaker. When Megan gets kidnapped it's up to Spencer and his partner Bru to save the day or risk losing everything.

Title: The Invisible Fight
Description: A guard on the Soviet-Chinese border who, after surviving a deadly attack, decides to become a monk but must continually prove along the way that he's capable of becoming the enlightened man he set out to be.

Title: No Time to Spy: A Loud House Movie
Description: Lincoln and the Louds are ecstatic to welcome their new Gran-Gran, Myrtle, into the family with a tropical wedding celebration, but the festivities are cut short when an old nemesis from Myrtle's secret agent past appears on the island.

Title: Ek Tha Tiger
Description: India's top spy Tiger and his love Zoya battle the dark world of intelligence and espionage that forbids its soldiers from loving the enemy.

Title: Børning
Description: The illegal sports car race "Street legal" goes 2000 kilometers through Norway from Oslo to North Cape, and Roy has been challenged to participate. At the same time, he has to look after his daughter.

Title: Phoenix
Description: Fiona's father has been killed in Florida, but she doesn't believe it was a suicide, and she learns that the prime suspect is a local drug kingpin with an army of mercenaries.

Title: Parava
Description: The story of Parava revolves around pigeon race, a game, which is prominent in Mattancherry, Kochi, Kerala.

Title: Bholaa Shankar
Description: While attempting to build a life in Kolkata with his sister, a taxi driver must confront his dark past as he faces off against the city's underworld.

Title: Pistol Whipped
Description: A tough ex-policeman (S.Seagal) with a gambling and alcohol problem gets offered a job as assassin of bad men. It'll rid him of all gambling debt as well as get him money and a chance of cleaning up his act and be with his daughter.

Title: Nemesis 4: Death Angel
Description: Alex shoots again. She has to kill a man, but shoots the wrong one. A high ransom is set on her, so she is visited by some head hunters. Well, she only could sit and wait and hope for a friend's help.

Title: The Last Man on Planet Earth
Description: In a world ruled and populated only by women, a young female scientist creates a male human being, genetically enhanced to refrain from violence.

Title: Naruto: The Lost Story - Mission: Protect the Waterfall Village
Description: Naruto and his friends must get back a jug of stolen holy water from a band of higher class ninjas.

Title: The Rebels of PT-218
Description: At the height of World War II, the Atlantic Ocean becomes a deadly battleground as an American torpedo boat fights against the constant bombardment of German forces.

Title: Supercar Sinners
Description: Boy with brain disorder inspires privileged supercar owners to transform through kindness and compassion, aided by a dream meeting with WWE's John Cena.

Title: Avarice
Description: A gifted archer must rescue her husband and daughter after they are abducted during a vicious home invasion.

Title: The Doberman Gang
Description: A clever con artist and an animal trainer team up to teach Doberman Pinschers how to rob banks.

Title: The Heart
Description: Centers on Joe and Lucy who, desperate for cash, transport a heart for an illegal buyer. Realizing it's for the black market, they reroute it but face deadly criminals after them.

Title: Mythica: The Godslayer
Description: As the Lich King's zombie legions ravage the world, a cursed young sorceress and her friend Dagen, a self-serving half-elf rogue, embark on a quest to obtain a weapon from the gods.

Title: The Man Who Fell to Earth
Description: An alien lands on Earth and decides that he needs to take a job in order to raise money to build a spaceship so he can get back to his home planet.

Title: Super Vixens
Description: Three stories about women with superhuman powers who battle super villains but get in over their heads and are never the same again.

Title: This City Is a Battlefield
Description: A 35-year-old former fighter and violinist devises a plan to blow up a movie theater, a gathering place for British NICA officials and the Dutch.

Title: Geisha of Death
Description: Nilalang is about an NBI agent who teams up with the heiress to a transnational organized crime syndicate in Japan to put a stop to the centuries-old curse that might be responsible for the spate of serial killings happening in Manila.

Title: Santa Jaws
Description: Trying to survive his family Christmas, Cody makes a wish to be alone, which ends up backfiring when a shark manifests and kills his entire family.

Title: R... Rajkumar
Description: An aimless ruffian starts working for a drug baron and his mission is to kill the rival, whose niece he eventually falls for.

Title: Tarzan and the Leopard Woman
Description: As a spate of leopard attacks causes panic, a sceptical Tarzan joins a hunting expedition, only to face a pagan cult of leopard-god worshippers and their fiendish high priestess. Can he escape the sharp claws of the savage Leopard Woman?

Title: Dawn Rider
Description: After his father is killed, John Mason is willing to turn the world inside out to find the man responsible. What he doesn't know is the killer might be in his own house.

Title: Besharam
Description: A car thief falls in love with a woman whose car he has stolen.

Title: Invader ZIM: Enter the Florpus
Description: ZIM discovers his almighty leaders never had any intention of coming to Earth and he loses confidence in himself for the first time in his life, which is the big break his human nemesis, Dib has been waiting for.

Title: Dear Comrade
Description: A hot-blooded student union leader falls for a state-level cricketer but his anger management issues and violent streak threatens to derail their love story.

Title: Konosuba!: God's Blessing on This Wonderful World! - Legend of Crimson
Description: Kazuma's party is suddenly alerted by an outrageous letter delivered by Yunyun. The letter requested that they come to the Crimson Demon Clan's village, that is facing a threat that could mean it's ending.

Title: Spiritwalker
Description: A fantasy action film that revolves around a man who loses his memory and subsequently wakes up in a new body every twelve hours.

Title: Swamp Shark
Description: An animal smuggling deal goes wrong, resulting in a large shark escaping into the swampy backwoods river.

Title: Tridev
Description: When an exiled police officer, a bandit and the son of a police commissioner are framed by a smuggler, they join forces to teach him a lesson and prove their innocence.

Title: Chhota Bheem Maha Shaitaan Ka Mahayudh
Description: Shaitaan has acquired the powers of all five chakras and has become this ultimate powerful entity that can destroy anything but he can't be too sure of his victory in this universe as a small portion of Chakras went to the chakravees who can destroy Shaitaan so he decides to transport the entire earth into a different dark dimension where Chakravees can't reach. So, Shaitaan sends his four maha villains to create havoc on earth who capture various kingdoms, including Dholakpur.King Inderaverma tells kids that they must travel to Devpur and find Chakrapashus who have the powers of Chakras, with their help Chakras were created in the first place but kids must pass the test to become ultimate Chakra warriors. Kids are on a mission but Zuhu and Damyaan attack them, they somehow manage to reach Devpur, where they meet Kanha disguised as Shamanra who guides them to get their powers form four adbhud Chakra Pashus. In the final face-off kids defeat Shaitaan and save the earth.

Title: Gentleman
Description: Hyeon soo a CEO of a private detective agency visits a pension with a client asking for her dog While waiting outside of pension he is falsely accused of kidnapping the client.

Title: Smoke Signal
Description: A suspected cavalry deserter proves to be resourceful in helping the surviving members of a fort flee Indians along a dangerous river.

Title: Countdown
Description: When a madman kidnaps a young boy and rigs him with explosives, Ray defies his captain and takes matter into his own hands. Now he must beat the clock and save the innocent child.

Title: Judwaa
Description: Twin brothers who are separated soon after birth, meet in adulthood and join forces to defeat their common enemy, a notorious criminal.

Title: The Guardian
Description: An honest cop is made to battle back when the corruption in his department threatens his family

Title: Man, Pride & Vengeance
Description: A stalwart Spanish soldier turns to a life of crime to prove his love for a mysterious and promiscuous gypsy woman.

Title: Kamen Rider 555 20th: Paradise Regained
Description: Orphnochs battle Smart Brain's extermination plans. Masato clashes with enforcer Reina. Takumi resurfaces as next Faiz, assisting Smart Brain. His intentions spark fresh Orphnoch-human tensions as the core conflict.

Title: The Rape of Richard Beck
Description: Seattle veteran cop Richard Beck becomes a sexual assault victim and must deal with the painful aftermath.

Title: Angel of Death
Description: A Jewish commando unit hunting Nazi war criminals tracks down the infamous Dr. Mengele in the jungle, and find that he is torturing nubile young virgins and performing horrible medical experiments on the locals. They prepare to battle their way past Mengele's hordes of fanatic Nazi bodyguards in order to get to him.

Title: Big Rage
Description: THE FIGHT TO RECONCILE ONE'S PAST WHILE NAVIGATING A FUTURE SHAPED BY UNEXPECTED LOVE AND LOYALTIES UNFOLDS IN THE ECOLOGICAL DISASTER KNOWN AS THE SALTON SEA.

Title: Shiri
Description: South Korean agents Ryu and Lee are tracking a female assassin from North Korea who has mysteriously disappeared. With new killings and the theft of a deadly bomb, time is running out to catch her.

Title: The Rise of Kirmada
Description: Bheem and young lord Krishna team up to protect the world against the wicked and powerful Kirmada and his equally dangerous bat army.

Title: Holiday
Description: A military officer attempts to hunt down a terrorist, destroy a terrorist gang and deactivate the sleeper cells under its command.

Title: Haunters
Description: Cho-In can control other people's minds when they are within his field of sight.Except one man.

Title: Guy Manley: Super Spy
Description: Ex-spy Guy Manley is assigned one last mission by his former boss Buck Cash. The mission is to kill Buck's brother Rich Cash to prevent him from being elected as the new mayor, and thereby becoming the most powerful person in the world.

Title: Killing Mary Sue
Description: A corrupt senator arranges for the murder of his biggest liability, his erratic burnout step-daughter, only for her to unwittingly discover her natural talent as an untouchable killer.

Title: Jailbreak
Description: What started as a simple escort mission will soon turn to chaos as the prisoners of Koh Kla take over the prison grounds. A special task force [Jean-Paul Ly, Dara Our, Tharoth Sam] gets trapped in the prison will have to fight their way out for survival, to protect a key witness [Savin Phillip].

Title: Phool Aur Kaante
Description: A young man who despises his father's criminal profession, wants to live a peaceful life away from him but fate has some other plans.

Title: Bodies at Rest
Description: Working in the morgue, a hardworking forensics expert and his assistant are suddenly accosted by masked intruders who demand access to a body involved in a recent crime.

Title: Thundu
Description: A constable aiming for a promotion unexpectedly encounters many problems. Facing the issues with humor and compassion, he works to overcome them.

Title: Kurtlar Vadisi: Filistin
Description: Polat Alemdar and his crew is in Palestine and fight against Israel special agents.

Title: Kuttram 23
Description: ACP Vetrimaaran investigates a series of murders related to the medical industry.

Title: Tom and Jerry Blast Off to Mars!
Description: While carrying on their usual chases, Tom and Jerry inadvertently stow-away on a spaceship bound for Mars.

Title: Golden Job
Description: A group of mercenaries come together to pull of an epic heist.

Title: Behind Enemy Lines: Colombia
Description: Navy SEALS mount an attack on Colombian special forces to clear their names and rescue a hostage.

Title: The Ultimate Weapon
Description: When mercenary "Hardball" Cutter discovers that the team he is working with is actually a group of IRA gunrunners, he decides to put a stop to their plans. Furious with Cutter, the gunrunners target him, his partner, and his family.

Title: Carnosaur 2
Description: A team of scientists go to a nuclear mining facility to investigate a possible meltdown and instead find a large amount of cloned dinosaurs.

Title: Kammara Sambhavam
Description: Kammaran Nambiar is a crooked man whose life story as an unscrupulous Indian peasant is turned into a film where he is glorified as a freedom fighter with much manipulation of history.

Title: Ring of Fire
Description: L.A.'s Chinatown is disrupted by the cross-town rivalry between two kickboxing clubs, as the competitive sport is catapulted from the ring of a gymnasium to a ring of fire.

Title: The Lusty Men
Description: Retired rodeo champion Jeff McCloud agrees to mentor novice rodeo contestant Wes Merritt against the wishes of Merritt's wife who fears the dangers of this rough sport.

Title: Code Name: Wild Geese
Description: Commander Robin Wesley, leader of a group of mercenaries, go to the Golden Triangle in Southeast Asia to overthrow the dictator, who is a major manufacturer and dealer of the world's opium.

Title: Yellow-Faced Tiger
Description: A Chinese-American cop, skilled in martial arts, battles the most powerful criminal gang in San Francisco that is responsible for the death of his partner.

Title: Borrder
Description: Revolves around patriotism and how a military officer runs an anti-terrorist operation.

Title: Before I Self Destruct
Description: A coming of age story about an inner-city youth raised by a hardworking single mother. When his dream of becoming a basketball player fails to materialize, he finds himself employed in a supermarket. After his mother is tragically gunned down, Clarence (played by Jackson) is consumed by revenge and takes up a life of crime in order to support his younger brother.

Title: Babbar
Description: Jorawar, once a mobster, lost his parents as a consequence of the booming crime wave and now wishes to have an easy going life with his brother. But fate turned him into a gang lord Babbar.

Title: FDR: American Badass!
Description: An outrageous, over-the-top spoof, FDR: American Badass is the untold true story of our country's greatest monster-hunting president!

Title: Intent to Kill
Description: A young policewoman relentlessly tries to bring down a ruthless drug kingpin whom plots his own agenda for his drug distribution empire.

Title: Gintama the Movie: The Final Chapter - Be Forever Yorozuya
Description: Gintoki travels into the future and discovers it to be a wasteland with his friends fallen apart. He reunites them to find out what went wrong and how to fix things.

Title: Malyagiri
Description: Parshu, a happy go lucky guy stay's with his family. His father gets ill and a large sum of money is required for his operation. Failing to pay the amount he decides to climb Malyagiri mountain and collect the vedic leafs.

Title: Sleepless Night
Description: A cop with a connection to the criminal underworld finds his secret life exposed when he and his partner are caught stealing cocaine from a powerful drug dealer, a move that puts his son's life in jeopardy.

Title: Shaktimaan
Description: Revolves around the protagonist and also the first Indian superhero Shaktimaan.Who got his power through devotion to God and activated All the chakras, so he could manipulate almost everything in this world.

Title: A Cop Movie
Description: Two professional actors undergo an immersive process to find out what it takes to be a cop in Mexico City.

Title: Drive Hard
Description: A former race car driver is abducted by a mysterious thief and forced to be the wheel-man for a crime that puts them both in the sights of the cops and the mob.

Title: Pitbull
Description: Five troubled lawmen (Marcin Dorocinski, Janusz Gajos, Andrzej Grabowski) pursue a brutal criminal.

Title: Garudan
Description: Sokkan, the trusted confidant of childhood friends Aadhi and Karuna.But when his loyalty and self respect is put into test, which would he choose?

Title: Operation Hadal
Description: The offshore platform Deep Blue 3 in Chinese territorial water has been occupied by mercenaries. The Chinese Navy sets sail then to repel invaders.

Title: Gandhi 3
Description: A local guy named Garry was called Gandhi and some referred to him as Robinhood in Punjab.

Title: Seema Raja
Description: A youngster who belongs to a royal family needs to play saviour to his villagers.

Title: Grizzly Rage
Description: After accidentally killing a bear cub while celebrating graduation in the woods, four teens become the target of a seemingly unstoppable Grizzly.

Title: The Bride with White Hair
Description: Cho Yat-Hang, the unwilling successor to the Wu-Tang clan throne and the unsure commander of the clan's forces in a war against an evil cult, falls in forbidden love with Lien Ni-Chang, a killer for the evil cult.

Title: Kenny Rogers as The Gambler: The Adventure Continues
Description: Brady Hawkes, Billy Montana, and Jeremiah Hawkes are on a train bound for a huge gambling event when the train is taken over by a gang of vicious killers in search of money. As ransom, the gang takes young Jeremiah hostage. Brady and Billy embark on a quest to rescue him and form a small gang of their own along the way.

Title: Night Ambush
Description: Led by British officers, partisans on Crete plan to kidnap the island's German commander and smuggle him to Cairo, Egypt to embarrass the occupiers.

Title: Underclassman
Description: A young detective goes undercover at an elite private school to destroy an international stolen car ring.

Title: Dragon Eyes
Description: In St. Jude, drug dealers and corrupt cops have destroyed an urban neighborhood. But newcomer, Hong, has the fighting skills and moral vision to save this town from itself.

Title: Omerta
Description: A recounting of the story of infamous British-born terrorist Ahmed Omar Saeed Sheikh, who kidnapped and murdered Wall Street Journal reporter Daniel Pearl in 2002.

Title: Kalaga Thalaivan
Description: Thiru, a financial analyst swiftly climbs up the corporate ladder. He soon finds his world turned upside down and is set for a collision with a mysterious deadly group headed by a brutal killer.

Title: Swelter
Description: Ten years after their casino heist, four escaped convicts trace their former partner to a desert town, where he is now a lawman with no memory of his criminal past.

Title: The Demon Detective
Description: Miles Mako is a professional exorcist who takes on a new client after she encounters a demonic presence who may have links to the detective's dark past.

Title: At Home Among Strangers, a Stranger Among His Own
Description: Set during the Civil War between the Reds and the Whites that followed the 1917 revolution in Russia

Title: Empire of the Wolves
Description: A disgraced policeman helps a young detective to hunt down a serial killer who targets Turkish women in Paris.

Title: Airbag
Description: Mamacita's boy Juantxo is engaged. Dragged to the party by his friends Konradin and Paco, he loses his expensive wedding ring inside a prostitute's body. Mafioso whorehouse owner Villambrosa finds the ring. Meanwhile Villambrosa's rival gangster Souza sends "femme fatale" Fatima to check things out. Juantxo and his friends are trying to get the ring back and in the process get involved in the war between gangs..

Title: My Fathers' Daughter
Description: Set in Norway's northern reaches, the story centers on Elvira, a Sami teen. Convinced her mother conceived at a Danish clinic, her life shifts when her true father emerges, forever altering her world.

Title: Mermaids
Description: Mermaid sisters hunt down their father's human killer... and deal with their own personal relationships with the humans.

Title: Hell's Belles
Description: When hot-headed Dan out-drives the thoroughly vicious Tony in a motorcycle race and wins a brand new bike, he sets in motion a chain of events that includes one blazing gas station and a disastrous rock slide.

Title: To Your Last Death
Description: In order to save her siblings, a young woman takes on her father and the powerful entity known as Gamemaster, who ensnares humans into diabolical plots while her species gambles on the outcome.

Title: IB 71
Description: A spy action thriller about the two-front war between Indian intelligence agencies and the Pakistani establishment in 1971.

Title: Caliber 9
Description: A former gangster is forced to resume his old lifestyle when his violent, jealous ex-colleagues and the police believe that he knows the location of a stolen cache of $300,000.

Title: Shaolin
Description: After ambushing and killing his rival, losing everything in the process, dispirited warlord Hou Jie turns to a Shaolin monastery seeking salvation.

Title: Baar Baar Dekho
Description: The highs and lows of a romantic relationship are examined through flashbacks and flash-forwards.

Title: Janbaaz
Description: Rana Vikram Singh (Amrish Puri) has two sons, police officer Rajesh (Feroz Khan) and fun-loving playboy Amar (Anil Kapoor). Rajesh has gone through the traumatic experience of losing the girl he loved (Sridevi), when she succumbed to drug addiction. He vows to fight this menace. An underworld kingpin Raja (Raza Murad) murders Rana's old friend, and his daughter Reshma (Dimple) takes shelter in Rana's house. Amar and Reshma fall in love, but evil Raja pursues her. Meanwhile, Rajesh is on the trail of the drug cartel that victimized his girlfriend.

Title: Shadows
Description: A young low-level drug dealer is reunited with his estranged mom and uncle to protect him when a ruthless drug kingpin puts a hit on him.

Title: Wing Chun
Description: Wing Chun's village is yet again being plundered by bandits. This time she uses kung fu to defeat them. The fighting doesn't end here.

Title: A Chinese Ghost Story II
Description: A Chinese Ghost Story II Chinese 倩女幽魂 II人間道 is a 1990 Hong Kong romantic comedy-horror film directed by Ching Siu-tung and produced by Tsui Hark. It is the sequel to A Chinese Ghost Story and is followed by A Chinese Ghost Story III.

Title: Stryker
Description: The world's water supply has dried up due to some sort of apocalypse. A beautiful woman holds the secret to where one of the last springs being guarded by a group of Amazons. A "Road Warrior" like crew captures her and tries to make her talk through brutal torture. The hero (Styrker) unites with some of the remaining "good guys" and the Amazons and frees the woman. They go on to a "Road Warrior" type of concluding battle with the bad guys.

Title: To Kill a Beaver
Description: Eryk, a soldier of special units fighting in Iraq and Afghanistan, returns to the country and sews up in the old family home. He must regenerate himself in anticipation of the next task. He finds it difficult to find himself in a gray reality. Her thoughts keep coming back to memories from the battlefield. One day he meets a young girl, Bezi who sneaks into his property. The meeting quickly turns into a passionate affair. Can love erase the worst memories? What if the worst memory is another love? However, each of the lovers hides a dark secret, the disclosure of which will have horrifying consequences.

Title: Dsp
Description: A flower seller's son ends up in a tussle with a ruthless rowdy in Dindigul, forcing him to become a policeman and fight the odds.

Title: Control
Description: The decapitated corpses of six women are found near Antwerp. A team of investigators tries to track down the killer to prevent a seventh murder.

Title: Max Payne: Perdition
Description: Max Payne, a former NYPD detective, has avenged his loved ones but now struggles with suicidal thoughts and alcoholism. Hunted by a mysterious figure from his past, Payne has only one night to come to terms with his past and himself.

Title: Kung Fu Panda: Secrets of the Masters
Description: Po and the Furious Five uncover the legend of three of kung fu's greatest heroes: Master Thundering Rhino, Master Storming Ox, and Master Croc.

Title: The Ninja Mission
Description: Swedish scientist named Karl Markov is taken hostage by the KGB. After his daughter Nadia is also kidnapped and brought deep into the heart of Russia, a group of highly trained ninjas, led by American CIA agent Mason, is ordered to get them out.

Title: Street Law
Description: An engineer seeks vigilante justice against the gangsters who took him hostage, and forms an unlikely partnership with a young robber to bring them down.

Title: Hard Cash
Description: Released from prison, an infamous thief and his new crew pull off a brilliant robbery but then become embroiled with a corrupt FBI agent when they discover the money is marked.

Title: Control
Description: A sociopath on death row is given a chance to live if he agrees to take part in a chemical behavioral modification program.

Title: Special Silencers
Description: Large red pills are obtained from a forest dwelling mystic, which aid in meditation. However, if used by the untrained they cause a huge tree to grow in the stomach and burst its way through the skin.

Title: Heroic Trio 2: Executioners
Description: Set some time after the original 'Heroic Trio' the city has been devastated by nuclear attack. An evil deformed villain controls the city's scarce water supply, exerting influence over both a popular leader and a militarist colonel. The trio of Chat the Thief catcher, Ching and Wonder Woman (along with her young daughter) have to avert a military takeover and find clean headwaters to save the city.

Title: Lajja
Description: The lives of four women from different places are the victims of male chauvinism and marital abuse. They decide to fight for their rights and dignity against the social norms and injustice.

Title: Racketeer
Description: Story of a man named Sayan, that had to live through harsh 1990's and make tough decisions.

Title: Witchblade
Description: Witchblade is the story of New York detective, Sara Pezzini, whose search for justice leads her to an arcane weapon that grants her the power to battle Earth's darkest evil forces.

Title: Land Shark
Description: Lucinda Regis, Director of Development at MALCO Oceanic Research, becomes the target of a dangerous killer after unraveling a sinister plot to inject sharks with human DNA.

Title: Butcher Boys
Description: A birthday celebration at a fancy restaurant leads to some friends' encounter with flesh-peddling cannibals.

Title: Deathstalker
Description: A reboot of the cult classic 1983 sword and sorcery film.

Title: Aztec Batman: Clash of Empires
Description: A young Aztec boy experiences tragedy when his father is murdered by Spanish Conquistadors. Yohualli escapes to Tenochtitlan to warn King Moctezuma and his high priest, Yoka, of imminent danger.

Title: Saladin
Description: After Saladin's victory over the King of Jerusalem, a peace treaty is signed between them, but the commander of the Crusader army, Renaud de Chatillon, slaughters a group of pilgrims going to Mecca. Saladin then decides to take revenge.

Title: Karaoglan
Description: Karaoglan is a Turkish historical comic book and drawn by Suat Yalaz.

Title: The Riot
Description: In 1907, the miners in Sulitjelma in Fauske in Nordland made a famous rebellion against greedy mine owners.

Title: Superman and the Mole-Men
Description: When underground beings explore the surface world from a deep oil well and inadvertently cause a panic, only Superman can prevent a tragedy.

Title: Mobile Suit Gundam SEED Freedom
Description: Lacus Clyne becomes president of a peace monitoring organization, but things are not quite what they seem.

Title: The Bamboo House of Dolls
Description: A nurse in a Japanese women's POW camp during World War II masterminds an escapee.

Title: Island of Fire
Description: A cop goes undercover to infiltrate a deadly prison where a team of mercenaries is being assembled.

Title: Ip Man: The Awakening
Description: Adventures of a young Master Ip in Hong Kong.

Title: Free Fall
Description: An employee, working for Gault Capital in L.A, gets targeted by a ruthless assassin and locked in the elevator after she uncovers a chilling secret.

Title: Macross Plus Movie Edition
Description: Two rival test pilots strive to be the best there is at what they do and also to win the heart of the woman behind the AI pop sensation Sharon Apple. Movie compilation of the acclaimed four-chapter OVA with additional scenes.

Title: Line Walker 2: Invisible Spy
Description: After they uncover evidence that there is corruption in the police force, three police officers in Hong Kong try to discover which of them can be trusted.

Title: Enter the Game of Death
Description: WWII looms, China fears German/Japanese invasion. Espionage group hires Bruce Le to retrieve secret document from 6-floor tower's top level by fighting his way up.

Title: The Drunken Prodigy
Description: Lin Yao has loved practicing martial arts since he was a child and thought he was very powerful. After experiencing deception and betrayal, he recognized who he was, regained confidence, practiced drunken boxing, and became a true hero.

Title: The Mean Machine
Description: After a two-year stint in prison, the son of a murdered Mafia boss teams up with a con-woman to get revenge on the drug smuggler who killed his father and stole his girlfriend.

Title: Abducted: Fugitive for Love
Description: [Spoilers ahead!] Jack, a man wrongly convicted of murder is sent to a prison where the unscrupulous warden has political aspirations. The warden manipulates his wife, his political adviser/lover, the prisoners and the voters, all while maintaining a smiling "I'm a great guy" facade. After noticing Jack's interest in his neglected wife Melanie, the warden puts Jack into a no-win situation in an attempt to make Jack do something Jack doesn't want to do. The result has Jack abducting Melanie, followed by the police across the state. Then Jack reveals to Melanie the reason why he abducted her.

Title: Logan's War: Bound by Honor
Description: An Army Ranger infiltrates a mob family by posing as a hit man. In conjunction with his uncle, they are plotting revenge against the killers who murdered his entire family when he was young.

Title: Brass Target
Description: In 1945, General Patton sends Germany's confiscated gold reserves to Frankfurt, but the Army train is robbed by plotters who also hire a Swiss hitman to kill the General.

Title: Gamitan
Description: Cathy, a young and innocent freshman, had a crush on senior hunk, Nick, the campus' basketball star. One day, he came to her and asked her to have dinner and drive her home. One thing led to another until she ended up giving her virginity not knowing that he made a bet with his friends. He dumped her right after he got what he wanted without any explanation. Filled with hatred she seduced Louie, her classmate who had a crush on her, to get back at him - and as a favor she would go to bed with him. Things got out of hand and led to a tragic ending.

Title: Bagman Rising
Description: After forcefully shown the brutal murder of his mom and girlfriend, Bagman sets out for revenge on the killer all the while two detectives are hot on his trail each holding a dark secret of their own.

Title: End of the World
Description: A group of Apocalyptic fanatics must use their knowledge of apocalyptic movies to save the world from a devastating solar flare.

Title: From Beijing with Love
Description: A Chinese spy who's been out of service for ten years whilst making a living as a butcher is sent to Hong Kong to locate a stolen Tyrannosaurus rex skull.

Title: Beast
Description: A jaded former intelligence agent is pulled back into action when an attack at a mall creates a tense hostage situation.

Title: Bharat
Description: At the cusp of India's birth as an Independent nation, a family makes an arduous journey to freedom at a cost. A young boy Bharat, makes a promise to his Father that he will keep his family together no matter what.

Title: Arjun
Description: Arjun Malvankar after his graduation thrives to get job. The corruption and injustice taking place in his community frustrates him to the extent of revolting with the help of some of his friends. This path of his gets him into serious problems with the law and some outrageous gangsters. He is then taken in by a politician named Shivkumar Chowgule; who not only has pity on him but offers him a job and encourages him. Situations take a different turn one morning engulfing Arjun's life into a world of lies, deceit, crime and politics.

Title: Torrente 4: Lethal Crisis
Description: The rude, lewd and crude Spanish ex-police officer Torrente finds himself facing jail time. Can he survive a twisted irony that places him where he has put so many others, both guilty and innocent?

Title: Escape from Brothel
Description: Hung's lover Sam doesn't know that Hung is actually a hooker. He gets involved with a jewelry store robbery and has to hide at Hung's house for a while. Hung tries to hide her profession from Sam, this is where the truth starts unfolding.

Title: Werewolves of the Third Reich
Description: In Germany at the height of World War II, a ragtag group of American soldiers discover Doctor Mengele's diabolical plan to create an unstoppable army of Nazi werewolves.

Title: Ruben Brandt, Collector
Description: Four expert thieves attempt to steal every famous artwork that is haunting their mutual psychotherapist. A detective attempts to find out who the "Collector" is.

Title: Reset
Description: When her son is kidnapped, the inventor of a time machine teams up with multiple versions of her future self to rescue him.

Title: The Magic Carpet
Description: Using a magic flying carpet and a handful of friends, the son of a murdered Caliph must fight the usurper in order to win the throne of the Caliphate.

Title: Witch from Nepal
Description: A Hong Kong man vacations to Nepal where a local tribe imbues him with magical powers which he must use to fight a growing evil.

Title: The Redemption: Kickboxer 5
Description: After David Sloan is murdered, it's up to kick-boxing champ Matt Reeves to avenge him.

Title: American Warships
Description: When a US plane is taken down over seas by an unknown assailant, the army is sure it was North Korea and a new war is about to break out. Even worse, the true attacker is an alien armed force and only one old battleship can stop them.

Title: Dragon's Heaven
Description: In the year 3195, during a war between robots and humans, a sentient combat armor loses his companion in battle and shuts down until his internal systems spot a new human.

Title: Operation Thunderbolt
Description: In July 1976, an Air France flight from Tel-Aviv to Paris via Athens was hijacked and forced to land in Entebbe, Uganda. The Jewish passengers were separated and held hostage in demand to release many terrorists held in Israeli prisons. After much debate, the Israeli government sent an elite commando unit to raid the airfield and release the hostages. This movie is based on the true facts and follows the events since the flight's take-off and until the hostages' return to Israel.

Title: Ozark Sharks
Description: A vacation to the Ozarks turns upside-down when bull sharks somehow infiltrate Arkansas' freshwater lakes and wreak havoc on a town's big fireworks festival.

Title: Expect No Mercy
Description: A maniacal leader trains assassins to become more efficient killing machines through virtual reality. A Federal Service Agent is assigned to infiltrate the mysterious academy.

Title: Family Vanished
Description: A happy family returns from a vacation to find their home invaded by a criminal family and must fight for survival.

Title: Dick Dynamite 1944
Description: In the dying days of World War II, Dick Dynamite and his ragtag team of Nazi-killing commandos must stop a group of depraved German scientists from turning the population of New York into flesh-eating zombies.

Title: Gintama Live Action the Movie
Description: In an era where aliens have invaded and conquered feudal Tokyo, a young samurai seeks work as he can.

Title: Madras Cafe
Description: An Indian intelligence agent journeys to a war-torn coastal island to break a resolute rebel group and meets a passionate journalist.

Title: Live Like a Cop, Die Like a Man
Description: Fred and Tony are members of an elite 'special squad' of police in Rome, Italy, who are licenced-to-kill, undercover cops who thrive on living dangerously.

Title: American Underdog
Description: A man with a troubled past decides to turn his life around after a heroic act by training for a mixed martial arts tournament.

Title: The World in His Arms
Description: In 1850 San Francisco, a Russian Countess runs away from an arranged marriage to a Russian Prince and falls into the arms of an American sea captain who occasionally poaches seals in Russian Alaska.

Title: Third World Cop
Description: A police officer returns to his neighborhood in Kingston, Jamaica to find himself in conflict with his childhood friend who is now the right-hand-man of the local gang-lord in a gun-running racket. Jamaica's highest-grossing film to date.

Title: Oceans Rising
Description: A scientist builds a boat after his warnings of an Earth-destroying flood are ignored. But when it's evident the disaster will occur, those who maligned the scientist now turn to him in desperation.

Title: Sandakozhi 2
Description: Balu and his father have to protect a young man from a woman who has sworn vengeance on his entire clan.

Title: The Last Days of Pompeii
Description: A demobilized centurion returns home to Pompeii to find his father murdered by a gang of black-hooded Christian robbers that terrorizes the city and he decides to investigate the matter while the nearby volcano threatens to erupt.

Title: Akhanda 2
Description: A heartwarming journey explores the connection between children's innocence, the natural world, and spiritual faith as communities strive for progress.

Title: Tokyo Tribe
Description: In an alternate Japan, territorial street gangs form opposing factions collectively known as the Tokyo Tribes. Merra, leader of the Wu-Ronz tribe of Bukuro crosses the line to conquer all of Tokyo. The war begins.

Title: Sayen: The Huntress
Description: Sayen joins a clandestine resistance group with a plan involving Valerie, who will provide needed information in exchange for her freedom. The rescue operation pushes Sayen to extremes limits, leading to a final confrontation.

Title: Minutes to Midnight
Description: On the cusp of New Year's Eve, seven friends and a mysterious backpacker converge at a desolate ski lodge in the mountains when they are systematically hunted down by ruthless masked men with a cryptic agenda.

Title: Hyena
Description: When a chilling terror plot threatens India's major cities-Bangalore, Hyderabad, and Mumbai-an unexpected twist prevents disaster: the bombs fail to detonate. The Intelligence Department quickly traces the terrorists' movements, uncovering the entry points and fragments of their operation. Suspicion grows around a mysterious mastermind who orchestrated the plot. As the National Investigation Squad (NIS) takes charge, a high-stakes pursuit begins. With every clue, the case grows more complex, involving international espionage, covert networks, and betrayals. The Indian Armed Forces, Police, Coast Guard, and Surveillance Alliance unite in a race against time to prevent another attack and uncover the truth. Enter Hyena Squad, an elite team of deadly operatives, brought in to eliminate the mastermind once and for all. But as the hunt intensifies, they discover that not everything is as it seems. Packed with gripping action, strategic warfare, and heart-stopping moments, Hyena: The Deadly Squad is a tribute to the courage and dedication of India's defenders, showing that no enemy is too great when a nation stands united.

Title: My Name Is Modesty: A Modesty Blaise Adventure
Description: When her surrogate father who owns the casino she works in gets murdered, Modesty Blaise takes on those that killed him and are now at the casino to rob it. It turns out she is more than just a modest worker.

Title: Angamaly Diaries
Description: Vincent Pepe who wanted to be a powerful leader of a righteous gang that ruled the city, like his seniors. And then there's the rival clan with the malicious gangsters of Angamaly a locale on which the film is based.

Title: The Amazing Colossal Man
Description: A military officer survives a nuclear blast, only to begin to uncontrollably grow into an increasingly unstable giant.

Title: Camel Spiders
Description: Dozen of large, man-eating camel spiders first attack soldiers in the desert of Iraq, then invades the southwestern areas of the United States.

Title: Winners Take All
Description: The scene is a modern, 1980s arena, where present day gladiators compete in the wild sports extravaganza of Supercross. Winners take all mixes the rivalry and camaraderie of two young men with the thrill of spectacular riding and high stakes competition. Going beyond the drama and excitement of the racing scene. a cast of hot, talented newcomers of young love. No one can feel left out of the thrill of victory on the track and off.

Title: Love You to Debt
Description: Follows Bo, a debt collector who starts to rethink everything after collecting a debt from a beautiful girl.

Title: Bullet Train Down
Description: On its maiden run, the world's fastest bullet train is rigged with a bomb that will explode if it dips below 200 mph.

Title: Destruction Los Angeles
Description: A fatal explosion and sudden earthquake rock Los Angeles, and reporter John Benson seizes his chance to cover the breaking news of increasing seismic activity.

Title: Returner
Description: A young woman from the future forces a local gunman to help her stop an impending alien invasion which will wipe out the human race.

Title: Vaincre ou mourir
Description: The heroic life of Charette, a noble, whom the Vendée peasants came to seek to fight the Republican Revolutionaries, to defend their land, their faith, their sons and their religion.

Title: Minuscule: Valley of the Lost Ants
Description: Somewhere in the forest, a stranded ladybug joins forces with a squad of black ants to retrieve a tin box of delicious sugar cubes to the hive. A battalion of fierce red ants has already set their sights on the loot. Who shall prevail?

Title: Manta, Manta: Legacy
Description: 30 years later, Berti and Uschi are divorced, but their son wants to follow in his father's footsteps and become a racing driver.

Title: Blind Waters
Description: An unrelenting shark turns a couple's dream vacation into a nightmare when they are stranded at sea and forced to fight for their lives.

Title: Assassination Classroom
Description: The Earth's moon is suddenly 70% smaller and permanently crescent shaped by a devastating and unknown force. For the students of E Class, Kunugigaoka Junior High School, the being responsible is known, as their teacher. The strange and very supportive entity has given the Japanese government a challenge to save the Earth from destruction. It wants to be the teacher of the class with the lowest expectations for success, in anything. The students, armed with special weapons that only harm their teacher, must find a way to kill him before the end of the school year. If not, summer break will be canceled by the end of the world.

Title: Kong Island
Description: Eve is a jungle girl brought up by apes. She is captured with a number of apes by a mad scientist, conducting mind control experiments on them. Eventually she is liberated by a young explorer.

Title: Sun, Sand & Romance
Description: Kate reunites with an old friend when her boyfriend spends too much time working during their vacation.

Title: Janatha Garage
Description: An environmental activist comes to Hyderabad to attend a seminar, where an unexpected encounter with a man who runs an organization for the oppressed, changes his purpose in life.

Title: Devil's Playground
Description: London based N-gen tests a performance booster on 30000. A month later, agile zombies plague London, spreading the disease with a bite. One man has 54 hours to find the cure/immune woman.

Title: Revenge of the Green Dragons
Description: Two best friends rise through the ranks of New York's Chinese underworld in the 1980s.

Title: Pittsburgh
Description: Charles 'Pittsburgh' Markham rides roughshod over his friends, his lovers, and his ideals in his trek toward financial success in the Pittsburgh steel industry, only to find himself deserted and lonely at the top. When his crash comes, he finds that fate has dealt him a second chance.

Title: Los canallas
Description: The leader and villain of the movie is called Kadena, a buxom girl, who is the real deal of the gang "Hell's Angels" and whose goal is to kill the Mil Mascaras as sending to jail to his sweetheart consented. What force our hero to fight to bad and bad.

Title: Sky Fighters
Description: An advanced, armed, French Mirage fighter jet is stolen during an air show in UK. 2 other fighter jets locate it. They're forced to shoot it down. Terrorists make another attempt to steal armed Mirages. Why?

Title: Alien Private Eye
Description: An alien from a faraway planet who works as a private investigator on Earth gets involved with a quest to retrieve a powerfully addictive drug that was sent to earth on a black disc.

Title: Malone
Description: A tough as nails private investigator (Malone) squares off with gangsters and their thugs to protect a valuable secret. Malone goes through hell to protect the information but he dishes some hell as well.

Title: Clone Cops
Description: A gang of outlaws defend their hideout until they discover a shocking secret about who they are and what they're up against. Now it's a race against time as they look for a way to escape certain doom at the hands of the Clone Cops.

Title: Five Fingers of Death
Description: As two martial arts schools prepare for an important tournament, one school's master is a dishonorable man, and to ensure his son wins the title, he hires three Japanese samurais, who target the rival school's best fighter.

Title: The Master
Description: A former Chinese Kung Fu master working in L.A. as a medicine man is targeted by an ex-student, and it's up to one of his Hong Kong disciples, who's visiting America, to defend his master's honor.

Title: If You Meet Sartana Pray for Your Death
Description: A gadget-laden gunfighter and gambler interferes with the complex schemes of gangsters and dignitaries hoping to steal a bank's gold and obtain the insurance payout for its theft.

Title: New Fist of Fury
Description: A young man sets out to avenge his grandfather's death and prove his martial arts mastery.

Title: Bridge of Dragons
Description: The tough and cold mercenary Warchild, is working for the man who took care of his war training and upbringing, the greedy General Ruechang. Ruechang is planning to take over the country by marrying Princess Halo. But Halo discovers that Ruechang killed her father to gain more power than he had working for the King, so she decides to run away. Warchild is the one who has to bring her back to Ruechang, but the one thing no one counted on happens... Warchild and Halo falls in love, and together they take on the forces of Ruechang...

Title: Brindaavanam
Description: Indu makes her boyfriend Krishna act like her friend Bhoomi's lover so that her family will stop searching for a groom. However, their lives takes a turn when Bhoomi falls in love with Krishna.

Title: Santhu Straight Forward
Description: Santhu is the typical do-gooder youngster, who is also the angry young hero. He falls for college student Ananya after a series of chance meetings. But, there's also dreaded don Deva in the picture forming the triangle.

Title: Adiós
Description: A con man with freedom supervised starts a bloody path of revenge when his little daughter dies in a car crash after of First Communion's celebration.

Title: One Tough Cop
Description: A detective tries to remain loyal to his partner, and his best friend - a mobster.

Title: Perfect Creature
Description: The vampire myth is given a stylish 1960s treatment, where a human cop partners with a vampire cop to stop a vamp bent on creating a war between the two "separate but equal" races.

Title: 14 Blades
Description: A kung fu thriller set during the Ming Dynasty and centered on a secret service agent (Donnie Yen) in the emperor's court who is betrayed and then hunted by his colleagues.

Title: Wrong Place Wrong Time
Description: Story of an unimaginable nightmare and how a ticket to a new life turns out to be a one way ticket to hell.

Title: Fast Getaway
Description: A lighthearted tale about a gang of bank robbers who fall out and split up. The brains of the gang is a boy who, with his father, successfully continue their crime spree. Annoyed at this, Lilly and her loyal and stupid companion, decide to kidnap the boy, Nelson, and force him to work for them.

Title: Bring Me the Head of the Machine Gun Woman
Description: Timid, video game-loving DJ Santiago seemingly digs his own grave when he agrees to bring a violent criminal kingpin the head of Machine Gun Woman.

Title: Shark Attack 2
Description: The mutant sharks from Dr. Craven's experiments in "Shark Attack 1" are back, this time choosing Cape Town, South Africa as their hunting ground.

Title: Iceman
Description: An imperial guard and his three traitorous childhood friends ordered to hunt him down get accidentally buried and kept frozen in time. 400 years later passes and they are defrosted continuing the battle they left behind.

Title: Jensen & Jensen: Mission - Pacific Force
Description: In a future (2019) dystopian Denmark, the brothers Jensen and Jensen become bounty hunters.

Title: Restart the Earth
Description: In order to combat desertification, humans have developed drugs that promote the accelerated reproduction of plant cells, but they have accidentally liberated the stress system of plants and awakened plant emotions.

Title: Kaavalan
Description: Meera starts calling bhoomi, her bodyguard just to fool him by telling him she loves him. Problems arise when bhoomi falls in love with her not knowing who she is.

Title: Don Seenu
Description: To make himself known as a gang-leader, a man must woo the sister of a dangerous gangster.

Title: For the Sake of Vicious
Description: An overworked nurse returns home to find a maniac hiding out with a bruised and beaten hostage. When an unexpected wave of violent intruders descend upon her home, it becomes a fight for survival.

Title: Revelation Road: The Beginning of the End
Description: Amidst foreboding lighting and tremors, a traveling salesman with a dark past must fight demons, both his own and a murderous biker gang, in his quest to complete his last sale and go home.

Title: M.A.S.K.: Mobile Armored Strike Kommand
Description: Matt Tracker leads a team of elite special agents with a fleet of hidden function vehicles against Miles Mayhem and his terrorist organization known as V.E.N.O.M.

Title: Metal Tornado
Description: An American company inadvertently unleashes a magnetic vortex on an unprepared world.

Title: Guns of Eden
Description: Four weekend campers are hunted by an armed militia.

Title: The Base
Description: In a U.S. army base, a senior army officer leads a group of young men into drug trafficking.

Title: Blue Passion
Description: Six American special agents are sent to an idyllic Greek island to disrupt the operation of an international operation of illegal arms deals and African based terrorists. Three agents are killed - so their team has an infiltrated enemy.

Title: The Hand of Death
Description: A survivor of an attack on a rebel group opposing the Manchu invasion of China creates the Goose Fist fighting technique and tries for revenge on a traitor.

Title: Vikingdom
Description: A forgotten king, Eirick, is tasked with the impossible odds to defeat Thor, the God of Thunder.

Title: Namak Halaal
Description: Brought up by his grandfather, Arjun Singh moves to the city in search of a new job and life. While in the city he meets Bhairon, who helps him find a job as a singer in a 5-star hotel owned by Raja.

Title: The Neptune Factor
Description: When an underwater ocean lab is lost in a earthquake, an advanced submarine is sent down to find it and encounters terrible danger.

Title: Mother's Day
Description: Nina, a secretive ex-NATO Special Operations agent, must use all her lethal skills to save her son who has been kidnapped by ruthless gangsters. Finding Max is a double chance for her. A chance for a new sense of adrenaline and the possibility of returning to life for her son, whom she must have had more .

Title: Galaxis
Description: Legend says that the sacred crystal is the source for all life and was created at the beginning of time. Kyla has sought the crystal to use its powers for himself and he takes the crystal after smashing the defenders on the Planet Sintaria. But there is another identical crystal on Earth and Ladera heads there to get it before the evil Kyla. She finds that Jed has taken the crystal from is hiding place, but Victor and his inexhaustible hit men want it for money they gave to Jed. Ladera easily handles the weak earthlings and saves Jed, but Kyla is also after the crystal. Jed and Ladera must find the crystal before Kyla, the clueless cops or the dimwitted villains.

Title: Litvyak
Description: Lydia Litvyak, a Soviet fighter pilot. Ace. Hero. She holds first place in the women fighter pilots ranking. On the first of August 1943, Litvyak was almost 22 years old. That day her plane took off for the last time.

Title: Bandit: Bandit Bandit
Description: Assigned to deliver a prototype car to a press conference for the Governor, things are complicated by a fraudulent Bandit who ends up stealing Bandit's rig AND the prototype. Now Bandit has to find out who's out to ruin his life and recover the car before the Governor's career is crucified by Big Bob on his radio show and while avoiding a determined Sheriff Buford Enright.

Title: For the Emperor
Description: Lee Hwan is out of professional baseball after being involved in match fixing. He is recruited by gangster boss Jung Sang Ha to work for him as a loan shark. Over time Lee Hwan climbs the ranks of Jung Sang Ha's company as the game becomes one of blood, money and sex.

Title: The Dirty Seven
Description: Emanuelle is trapped in the middle of a brutal war, as both sides set out to claim her. Unfortunately for them, Emanuelle is not only beautiful but quite intelligent and uses her charms to seduce the soldiers to gain an advantage.

Title: Hunting Ava Bravo
Description: Billionaire sportsman Buddy King unwinds by hunting human captives on his remote mountain estate. But his latest victim, Ava Bravo, is no easy target.

Title: The Omicron Killer
Description: Attacked by vicious thugs, left severely wounded and hospitalized, a serial killer known as The Omicron Killer vows vengeance as he embarks on a new reign of terror.

Title: Kaveri
Description: Vikram Simha, a dedicated cop known for his unwavering support for women in trouble, is called to action when Kaveri is brutally assaulted. As she seeks revenge, Vikram must navigate a web of deceit and danger.

Title: Supercollider
Description: When the largest particle collider ever built suffers a catastrophic malfunction, it opens an alternate dimension and causes a series of cataclysmic events that threaten the entire human species.

Title: First Daughter
Description: After an agent saves the US president by not following procedure, she's "demoted" to looking after the teenage first daughter on a wilderness tour with other teenagers. Problems arise.

Title: Yalgaar
Description: Childhood friends became enemies when one Mahendra Ashwini Kumar grows up to be Additional Police Commissioner and the other Raj Pratap Singhal becomes a smuggler. Mahendra have two sons who are also police officers namely Rajesh and Brajesh while on the other hand Singhal is also christened with two sons Vishal who helps develop his dad's business and Vicky who takes up employment in a garage. When Brajesh is killed by one of Mahendra's henchman; Rajesh swears to avenge the death of his brother even if having to take the law into his own hands. After Brajesh's death he leaves behind his widowed wife, Kaushalya and a young daughter, Meghna. On a chance encounter with both Meghna and Vicky both fall in love and the Kumars approve of Vicky as there future son in law unaware of his family background. And then Mahendra is given the post as police Commissioner; unable to bear this Singhal sets up another of his henchman to have Mahendra killed. To escape from the police and public officials Singhal and his family migrates to Dubai further escalating the blood shed between both the families that might continue for years.

Title: Kung Fu Dunk
Description: Fang Shijie is found as a baby in the garbage and raised at a martial arts academy. With the help of a man, he gets into college and is promoted to the basketball championship as he searches for his real parents.

Title: Youth of the Beast
Description: A violent thug plays opposing yakuza bosses against each other.

Title: Dog Day
Description: A fugitive on the run from the law, and carrying several million dollars, hides out in the home of a farm family. The tables turn when the family proves to be even more criminally oriented than he is--and begins to terrorize him instead of the other way around.

Title: Flight of Fury
Description: John is sent in to recover a stolen Stealth Bomber. His trusty sidekick Rojar and ever faithful Jessica fight the rebel forces of Banansistan, led by the vivacious Ellianna.

Title: Pathonpatham Noottandu
Description: Arattupuzha Velayudha Panicker, a 19th century fiery social reformer and his unswerving fight against the dominant caste oppressions by the upper classes.

Title: Double Ismart
Description: A notorious criminal with a terminal brain tumor hires a rogue scientist to transfer his mind into the body of a street-smart renegade with a unique memory transfer port in his brain.

Title: Only 3 Days Left
Description: A Mexican cartel kidnapped Rayane's grandmother and now he has only three days to free her.

Title: Nothing Even Matters
Description: Paroled after five years for a victimless crime, Travis is taken in by Benny, and her mother; their generosity turns into a life of crime and murder.

Title: The Knight of Shadows: Between Yin and Yang
Description: A legendary demon hunter (Jackie Chan), tracking down beasts that enter the human dimension, assisted by a lawman protégé and a motley group of friendly monsters.

Title: Kingdom 3: The Flame of Destiny
Description: It follows Li Xin and Wang Qi as they stand on the battlefield for the first time to fight off an invasion by Zhao, and it also follows Ying Zheng's unknown past.

Title: Justice League x RWBY: Super Heroes and Huntsmen Part Two
Description: After their adventure in Remnant cyberspace, courtesy of Kilg%re, the Justice League returns to Earth. However, they find the Grimm have followed them and are somehow duplicating their powers. Bringing Black Canary up to speed, the League is forced to seek out Team RWBY for help.

Title: ISIS: Enemies of Humanity
Description: "A must watch film to know about the life of terrorists,their ideology and a solution which challenges this violent ideology".

Title: Angel Unchained
Description: Angel is the biker who joins a commune of hippies near a small town. When the town rednecks attack them, Angel calls up some of his bad biker buddies to exact revenge.

Title: Shadow Man
Description: An intelligence operative discovers that no one is what they seem in the shadowy world of espionage.

Title: La Trampa
Description: Uncle and nephew try to recover their lands from a corrupt casino owner. A farmer is pressured to pay his gambling son's huge debt. Both problems have the same source, and will come together.

Title: My Wife Is a Gangster 3
Description: When Aryong, the daughter of a triad boss from Hong Kong is accused of killing the boss of a competing triad, she is goes into hiding in Korea. Upon arriving, she is guided by a nimble but loyal Gi-chul and his motley crew, who are assigned to protect her until her return.

Title: Wolf Hound
